{"type":"message","id":"70e5ae88","parentId":"25c5c6e7","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:03:08.234Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-09 19:50:28 GMT+4] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"2AB2EC31D6FA0197F645\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+971504042000\",\n  \"sender\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant (+971504042000)\",\n  \"id\": \"+971504042000\",\n  \"name\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant\",\n  \"e164\": \"+971504042000\"\n}\n```\n\nNova, perform a complete self-audit and report everything about yourself: \n \n 1. **CONFIG AUDIT** - Read ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json, list all active settings\n (model, memory limits, heartbeat, hooks, plugins, env vars) \n \n 2. **CONNECTION STATUS** - Check WhatsApp connection, verify gateway on port\n 18789, test /health endpoint\n\n 3. **ACCESS & PERMISSIONS** - List your tools (bash, read, write, web),\n workspace dir, elevated mode status\n\n 4. **VOICE CONFIG** - Report TTS provider, STT config, confirm native vs local\n processing\n\n 5. **MEMORY & BRAIN** - List ~/.openclaw/memory/ files, read your persona,\n show brain files, session memory count\n\n 6. **HEARTBEAT & HEALTH** - Show heartbeat interval, last heartbeat, current\n memory usage in MB\n\n 7. **OPTIMIZATIONS** - List applied optimizations, compaction settings,\n context pruning\n\n 8. **PLUGINS & SKILLS** - Enabled plugins, loaded skills, disabled features\n\n Format as structured report. Be thorough."}],"timestamp":1773072188211}}
