, loaded skills, disabled features\\n\\n  Format as structured report. Be thorough.\",\"timestamp\":1773072179000},\"2\":\"inbound message\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.16.0\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"{\\\"module\\\":\\\"web-inbound\\\"}\",\"parentNames\":[\"openclaw\"],\"date\":\"2026-03-09T16:02:58.979Z\",\"logLevelId\":3,\"logLevelName\":\"INFO\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///Users/ahmadabdullah/.bun/install/global/node_modules/openclaw/dist/channel-web-D_BMn4vE.js:777:17\",\"fileName\":\"channel-web-D_BMn4vE.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"channel-web-D_BMn4vE.js:777\",\"fileColumn\":\"17\",\"fileLine\":\"777\",\"filePath\":\"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.bun/install/global/node_modules/openclaw/dist/channel-web-D_BMn4vE.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.bun/install/global/node_modules/openclaw/dist/channel-web-D_BMn4vE.js:777\",\"method\":\"enqueueInboundMessage\"}},\"time\":\"2026-03-09T20:02:58.979+04:00\"}\n{\"0\":\"{\\\"module\\\":\\\"web-auto-reply\\\",\\\"runId\\\":\\\"702641c0-0698-4a53-8097-9c106bfabc8e\\\"}\",\"1\":{\"connectionId\":\"60166a61-41e9-421c-875f-848f86ee6258\",\"correlationId\":\"2AB2EC31D6FA0197F645\",\"from\":\"+971504042000\",\"to\":\"+971504042000\",\"body\":\"[WhatsApp +971504042000 +21m Mon 2026-03-09 20:02 GMT+4] (self): Nova, perform a complete self-audit and report everything about yourself:     \\n  \\n  1. **CONFIG AUDIT** - Read ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json, list all active settings\\n   (model, mвҖҰ (truncated 848 chars)\",\"mediaType\":null,\"mediaPath\":null},\"2\":\"inbound web message\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.16.0\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"{\\\"module\\\":\\\"web-auto-reply\\\",\\\"runId\\\":\\\"702641c0-0698-4a53-8097-9c106bfabc8e\\\"}\",\"parentNames\":[\"openclaw\"],\"date\":\"2026-03-09T16:02:59.006Z\",\"logLevelId\":3,\"logLevelName\":\"INFO\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///Users/ahmadabdullah/.bun/install/global/node_mod