ssion Memory**: 4 daily memory files in workspace/memory/\n\n---\n\n## 6. HEARTBEAT & HEALTH\n**Heartbeat**: DISABLED (0m interval - no periodic checks)\n\n**Memory Usage**:\n- Gateway: 474MB RSS\n- Main process: 42MB RSS\n- Total OpenClaw dir: 17MB on disk\n\n**Uptime**: ~11 minutes (started 19:50:24)\n\n---\n\n## 7. OPTIMIZATIONS\n**Applied**:\n- Block streaming: ON (800-1200 char chunks)\n- Human delay: natural mode\n- Context pruning: cache-ttl (1h)\n- Compaction: safeguard mode (24K floor)\n\n**Node Optimizations**:\n- max-old-space-size: 1536MB\n- gc-interval: 100\n\n---\n\n## 8. PLUGINS & SKILLS\n**Plugins Enabled**:\n- вң… whatsapp (active)\n- вқҢ memory-lancedb (disabled)\n\n**Skills**: All bundled skills allowed (*)\n- coding-agent, gemini, github, healthcheck, skill-creator, tmux, weather\n\n**Disabled Features**:\n- Browser automation\n- Canvas host\n- Hooks\n- Cron jobs (0 jobs configured)\n\n---\n\n## SUMMARY\nвң… All systems operational\nвң… Full file/command access\nвң… WhatsApp connected\nвң… GLM-5 active with fallback\nвң… Auto-update enabled\nвҡ пёҸ Heartbeat disabled (no periodic checks)\nвҡ пёҸ No cron jobs scheduled\n\n**Disk Usage**: 17MB total\n**RAM Usage**: ~516MB combined\n\nReady for tasks."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":7949,"output":897,"cacheRead":25600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34446,"cost":{"input":0.007949,"output":0.0028704000000000004,"cacheRead":0.00512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0159394}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773072222991}}
