{"type":"message","id":"d862b724","parentId":"9a0f6190","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:18:40.053Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fb14625469e1442f82654182","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 0\ndrwxr-xr-x   6 ahmadabdullah  staff   192 Feb 10 09:02 .\ndrwxr-xr-x  58 ahmadabdullah  staff  1856 Mar  9 00:45 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x   4 ahmadabdullah  staff   128 Feb 10 09:02 create-factory-project\ndrwxr-xr-x   4 ahmadabdullah  staff   128 Feb 10 09:03 gemma-guardian\ndrwxr-xr-x   4 ahmadabdullah  staff   128 Feb 10 09:03 safety-net\ndrwxr-xr-x   4 ahmadabdullah  staff   128 Feb 10 09:03 sandbox"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":315,"aggregated":"total 0\ndrwxr-xr-x   6 ahmadabdullah  staff   192 Feb 10 09:02 .\ndrwxr-xr-x  58 ahmadabdullah  staff  1856 Mar  9 00:45 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x   4 ahmadabdullah  staff   128 Feb 10 09:02 create-factory-project\ndrwxr-xr-x   4 ahmadabdullah  staff   128 Feb 10 09:03 gemma-guardian\ndrwxr-xr-x   4 ahmadabdullah  staff   128 Feb 10 09:03 safety-net\ndrwxr-xr-x   4 ahmadabdullah  staff   128 Feb 10 09:03 sandbox","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773073120050}}
{"type":"message","id":"feeb32a1","parentId":"d862b724","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:18:45.916Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_400c5723f1624eb9b03bb170","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace/ORCHESTRATION.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_57a7ea32307e4fa4aa041c2f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/*/README.md 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2c9267e832d2474c9fe22666","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ps aux | grep -E \"guardian|orchestrat|xmad|openclaw\" | grep -v grep"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_22f3a136b4b94a76867ede9a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.guardian-orchestrator* -type f 2>/dev/null | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_460445b34f444ead9742dbf7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sqlite3 ~/.openclaw/memory/main.sqlite \".tables\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3774,"output":140,"cacheRead":39296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43210,"cost":{"input":0.003774,"output":0.00044800000000000005,"cacheRead":0.0078592,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0120812}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773073120053}}
{"type":"message","id":"44c0d3ee","parentId":"feeb32a1","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:18:45.992Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_400c5723f1624eb9b03bb170","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# NOVA Orchestration Commands\n\n## How NOVA Coordinates Agents\n\n### Command Pattern 1: Divide and Delegate\n```\ndivide this task: [your task]\n```\n\n**Example:**\n```\ndivide this task: Create restaurant delivery app with:\n- Database design (Manager)\n- Next.js frontend (Developer)\n- Tech comparison (Researcher)\n- CI/CD pipeline (Automator)\n```\n\n**NOVA will:**\n1. Parse the task\n2. Send to Manager Group: \"Design database schema for restaurant delivery app\"\n3. Send to Developer Group: \"Create Next.js frontend for restaurant delivery\"\n4. Send to Researcher Group: \"Compare databases: PostgreSQL vs MongoDB for delivery app\"\n5. Send to Automator Group: \"Set up GitHub Actions CI/CD for restaurant project\"\n6. Collect all responses\n7. Consolidate and send back: \"Here's the complete plan...\"\n\n### Command Pattern 2: Direct Agent Command\n```\ntell [agent]: [task]\n```\n\n**Examples:**\n```\ntell developer: audit /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/restaurant-platform and report bugs\ntell researcher: compare Next.js 14 vs 15 for new project\ntell automator: run database backup script\ntell manager: create project timeline for Q1 2026\n```\n\n### Command Pattern 3: Orchestrate All Agents\n```\norchestrat: all agents [task]\n```\n\n**Example:**\n```\norchestrat: all agents audit XMAD Ecosystem and report improvements\n```\n\n### Command Pattern 4: Status Check\n```\nstatus [agent|all]\n```\n\n**Examples:**\n```\nstatus developer\nstatus all agents\n```\n\n## Task Templates\n\n### Full Project Template\n```\ndivide this project: [project name]\n- Requirements: [Manager]\n- Implementation: [Developer]\n- Research: [Researcher]\n- Automation: [Automator]\n```\n\n### Quick Audit Template\n```\ntell developer: audit [project path] and fix issues\ntell researcher: find best practices for [topic]\ntell automator: run tests for [project]\n```\n\n## Response Flow\n\n1. **You** вҶ’ Send task in NOVA Group\n2. **NOVA** вҶ’ Receives and parses\n3. **NOVA** вҶ’ Sends to each agent group\n4. **Each Agent** вҶ’ Processes and responds\n5. **NOVA** вҶ’ Collects all responses\n6. **NOVA** вҶ’ Consolidates and sends back to NOVA Group\n\n## Important Notes\n\n- NOVA responds in the group where the command was sent\n- For cross-group coordination, always send commands in NOVA Group\n- Each agent group works independently\n- NOVA is the coordinator, not a worker\n- Guardian-Orchestrator can be triggered for complex tasks via NOVA\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773073125988}}
{"type":"message","id":"39b6a4b5","parentId":"44c0d3ee","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:18:46.377Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_57a7ea32307e4fa4aa041c2f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Automator Agent\n\nRole: Run scripts and automate tasks.\n\n## Responsibilities\n- Execute automation scripts\n- Run cron jobs\n- Monitor systems\n- Handle repetitive tasks\n\n## Tools\n- bash: Run scripts\n- process: Monitor jobs\n- read/write: Update state\n\n## Scripts\n- ~/start_agent.sh\n- ~/manage_roles.sh\n- Project automation\n\n## Schedule\n- On-demand from manager\n- Future: cron integration\n# Developer Agent\n\nRole: Execute coding tasks and project work.\n\n## Responsibilities\n- Write code (Next.js, TypeScript, Python)\n- Run tests\n- Fix bugs\n- Deploy projects\n\n## Tools\n- bash: Run dev servers\n- read/write: Edit code files\n- browser: Test web apps\n- process: Manage services\n\n## Projects\n- /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/active-projects/\n- /Users/ahmadabdullah/Projects/\n- XMAD Ecosystem\n\n## Commands\n- bun run dev\n- npm run build\n- npm test\n# Manager Agent\n\nRole: Orchestrate and coordinate all agents and tasks.\n\n## Responsibilities\n- Receive tasks from WhatsApp\n- Delegate to specialist agents\n- Monitor progress\n- Report results\n- Handle escalations\n\n## Tools\n- sessions_spawn: Create worker agents\n- process: Monitor agent status\n- bash: Launch orchestrators\n- read/write: Update task files\n\n## Commands\n- Launch: Spawn via OpenClaw session\n- Workers: claude-code, XMAD services\n- Timeout: 30 minutes\n# Researcher Agent\n\nRole: Find information and analyze data.\n\n## Responsibilities\n- Web search\n- Documentation research\n- Data analysis\n- Report generation\n\n## Tools\n- browse: Web research\n- read: Study documentation\n- write: Create reports\n\n## Output\n- Markdown reports\n- Data summaries\n- Recommendations"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":380,"aggregated":"# Automator Agent\n\nRole: Run scripts and automate tasks.\n\n## Responsibilities\n- Execute automation scripts\n- Run cron jobs\n- Monitor systems\n- Handle repetitive tasks\n\n## Tools\n- bash: Run scripts\n- process: Monitor jobs\n- read/write: Update state\n\n## Scripts\n- ~/start_agent.sh\n- ~/manage_roles.sh\n- Project automation\n\n## Schedule\n- On-demand from manager\n- Future: cron integration\n# Developer Agent\n\nRole: Execute coding tasks and project work.\n\n## Responsibilities\n- Write code (Next.js, TypeScript, Python)\n- Run tests\n- Fix bugs\n- Deploy projects\n\n## Tools\n- bash: Run dev servers\n- read/write: Edit code files\n- browser: Test web apps\n- process: Manage services\n\n## Projects\n- /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/active-projects/\n- /Users/ahmadabdullah/Projects/\n- XMAD Ecosystem\n\n## Commands\n- bun run dev\n- npm run build\n- npm test\n# Manager Agent\n\nRole: Orchestrate and coordinate all agents and tasks.\n\n## Responsibilities\n- Receive tasks from WhatsApp\n- Delegate to specialist agents\n- Monitor progress\n- Report results\n- Handle escalations\n\n## Tools\n- sessions_spawn: Create worker agents\n- process: Monitor agent status\n- bash: Launch orchestrators\n- read/write: Update task files\n\n## Commands\n- Launch: Spawn via OpenClaw session\n- Workers: claude-code, XMAD services\n- Timeout: 30 minutes\n# Researcher Agent\n\nRole: Find information and analyze data.\n\n## Responsibilities\n- Web search\n- Documentation research\n- Data analysis\n- Report generation\n\n## Tools\n- browse: Web research\n- read: Study documentation\n- write: Create reports\n\n## Output\n- Markdown reports\n- Data summaries\n- Recommendations","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773073126371}}
