{"type":"message","id":"75b4b342","parentId":"17abc9b9","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:18:57.892Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cba52f7302ee47fdb44d8ca6","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Create Factory Project - CLI Tool\n\n## Purpose\nCLI scaffolding tool to generate new projects from templates in the factory monorepo.\n\n## Features (Placeholder)\n- Interactive project setup\n- Template selection (basic, fullstack, ai-agent)\n- Dependency installation\n- Git initialization\n- Workspace registration\n\n## Usage\n```bash\n# From root\npnpm create:project\n\n# Direct usage\nnode tools/create-factory-project/index.js\n```\n\n## Development Status\nрҹҡ§ **PLACEHOLDER** - Structure created, implementation pending\n\n## Next Steps\n- Implement CLI with inquirer/prompts\n- Create template copier logic\n- Add workspace registration\n- Implement git initialization\n- Add dependency installer\n# Gemma Guardian - File Watcher & Validator\n\n## Purpose\nFile watching system that validates changes and prevents destructive operations.\n\n## Features (Placeholder)\n- Real-time file watching\n- Validation rules engine\n- Destructive operation detection\n- Automatic safety checks\n- Alert system for violations\n\n## Usage\n```bash\n# Start guardian\npnpm guardian:start\n\n# Validate changes\npnpm guardian:validate\n```\n\n## Development Status\nрҹҡ§ **PLACEHOLDER** - Structure created, implementation pending\n\n## Next Steps\n- Implement file watcher (chokidar)\n- Create validation rules engine\n- Add destructive pattern detection\n- Implement alert system\n- Create rule configuration format\n# Safety Net - Checkpoint & Rollback System\n\n## Purpose\nGit-based checkpoint and rollback system to safely experiment and revert changes.\n\n## Features (Placeholder)\n- Create named checkpoints\n- List all checkpoints\n- Rollback to any checkpoint\n- Auto-checkpoint before major changes\n- Checkpoint metadata (timestamp, description)\n\n## Usage\n```bash\n# Create checkpoint\npnpm checkpoint:create \"Before big refactor\"\n\n# List checkpoints\npnpm checkpoint:list\n\n# Rollback\npnpm checkpoint:rollback <checkpoint-name>\n```\n\n## Development Status\nрҹҡ§ **PLACEHOLDER** - Structure created, implementation pending\n\n## Next Steps\n- Implement git tag-based checkpoints\n- Create checkpoint metadata storage\n- Add rollback logic\n- Implement auto-checkpoint hooks\n- Add checkpoint diff viewer\n# Sandbox - Agent Isolation Environment\n\n## Purpose\nIsolated execution environment for AI agents to safely run code and experiments.\n\n## Features (Placeholder)\n- Sandboxed code execution\n- Resource limits (CPU, memory, time)\n- File system isolation\n- Network access controls\n- Output capture and logging\n\n## Usage\n```bash\n# Run code in sandbox\npnpm sandbox:run <script>\n\n# Start sandbox server\nnode tools/sandbox/index.js server\n```\n\n## Development Status\nрҹҡ§ **PLACEHOLDER** - Structure created, implementation pending\n\n## Next Steps\n- Implement VM isolation (vm2)\n- Add resource limiters\n- Create file system sandbox\n- Implement network filters\n- Add execution timeout controls"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":325,"aggregated":"# Create Factory Project - CLI Tool\n\n## Purpose\nCLI scaffolding tool to generate new projects from templates in the factory monorepo.\n\n## Features (Placeholder)\n- Interactive project setup\n- Template selection (basic, fullstack, ai-agent)\n- Dependency installation\n- Git initialization\n- Workspace registration\n\n## Usage\n```bash\n# From root\npnpm create:project\n\n# Direct usage\nnode tools/create-factory-project/index.js\n```\n\n## Development Status\nрҹҡ§ **PLACEHOLDER** - Structure created, implementation pending\n\n## Next Steps\n- Implement CLI with inquirer/prompts\n- Create template copier logic\n- Add workspace registration\n- Implement git initialization\n- Add dependency installer\n# Gemma Guardian - File Watcher & Validator\n\n## Purpose\nFile watching system that validates changes and prevents destructive operations.\n\n## Features (Placeholder)\n- Real-time file watching\n- Validation rules engine\n- Destructive operation detection\n- Automatic safety checks\n- Alert system for violations\n\n## Usage\n```bash\n# Start guardian\npnpm guardian:start\n\n# Validate changes\npnpm guardian:validate\n```\n\n## Development Status\nрҹҡ§ **PLACEHOLDER** - Structure created, implementation pending\n\n## Next Steps\n- Implement file watcher (chokidar)\n- Create validation rules engine\n- Add destructive pattern detection\n- Implement alert system\n- Create rule configuration format\n# Safety Net - Checkpoint & Rollback System\n\n## Purpose\nGit-based checkpoint and rollback system to safely experiment and revert changes.\n\n## Features (Placeholder)\n- Create named checkpoints\n- List all checkpoints\n- Rollback to any checkpoint\n- Auto-checkpoint before major changes\n- Checkpoint metadata (timestamp, description)\n\n## Usage\n```bash\n# Create checkpoint\npnpm checkpoint:create \"Before big refactor\"\n\n# List checkpoints\npnpm checkpoint:list\n\n# Rollback\npnpm checkpoint:rollback <checkpoint-name>\n```\n\n## Development Status\nрҹҡ§ **PLACEHOLDER** - Structure created, implementation pending\n\n## Next Steps\n- Implement git tag-based checkpoints\n- Create checkpoint metadata storage\n- Add rollback logic\n- Implement auto-checkpoint hooks\n- Add checkpoint diff viewer\n# Sandbox - Agent Isolation Environment\n\n## Purpose\nIsolated execution environment for AI agents to safely run code and experiments.\n\n## Features (Placeholder)\n- Sandboxed code execution\n- Resource limits (CPU, memory, time)\n- File system isolation\n- Network access controls\n- Output capture and logging\n\n## Usage\n```bash\n# Run code in sandbox\npnpm sandbox:run <script>\n\n# Start sandbox server\nnode tools/sandbox/index.js server\n```\n\n## Development Status\nрҹҡ§ **PLACEHOLDER** - Structure created, implementation pending\n\n## Next Steps\n- Implement VM isolation (vm2)\n- Add resource limiters\n- Create file system sandbox\n- Implement network filters\n- Add execution timeout controls","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773073137888}}
