{"type":"message","id":"8b1f04f6","parentId":"ff77dbe6","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:20:54.364Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\n# рҹ”Қ FULL SYSTEM AUDIT REPORT\n\n---\n\n## 1. ARCHITECTURE MAP\n\n```\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                          USER (Ahmad)                                в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                     WhatsApp / Terminal / Browser                    в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                           в”Ӯ\n        в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n        в”Ӯ                                     в”Ӯ\n        в–ј                                     в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ              в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  рҹ“ұ WhatsApp      в”Ӯ              в”Ӯ  рҹ–ҘпёҸ XMAD Control   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  +971504042000    в”Ӯ              в”Ӯ  Dashboard :8765   в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ              в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n         в”Ӯ                                   в”Ӯ\n         в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                        в–ј\n        в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n        в”Ӯ   рҹҡҖ OpenClaw Gateway         в”Ӯ\n        в”Ӯ   Port 18789 (Local)          в”Ӯ\n        в”Ӯ   Model: GLM-5 (fallback 4.7) в”Ӯ\n        в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                    в”Ӯ\n        в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n        в”Ӯ                        в”Ӯ\n        в–ј                        в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ      в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  рҹӨ– NOVA      в”Ӯ      в”Ӯ  рҹӣЎпёҸ Guardian    в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Main Agent   в”Ӯ      в”Ӯ  Orchestrator   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  (Primary)    в”Ӯ      в”Ӯ  (Inactive)     в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ      в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n        в”Ӯ\n        в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n        в”Ӯ                                    в”Ӯ\n        в–ј                                    в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ             в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  Multi-Agent     в”Ӯ             в”Ӯ  Voice Services  в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  System          в”Ӯ             в”Ӯ  (Inactive)      в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ   в”Ӯ             в”Ӯ  в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў Developer     в”Ӯ             в”Ӯ  вҖў STT SenseVoiceв”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў Manager       в”Ӯ             в”Ӯ  вҖў TTS Chatterboxв”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў Researcher    в”Ӯ             в”Ӯ  вҖў TTS Kokoro    в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў Automator     в”Ӯ             в”Ӯ  вҖў TTS Qwen3     в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ             в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n        в”Ӯ\n        в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  рҹ§  Memory System                   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ                в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў SQLite DB (68KB)                 в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў Markdown Files (MEMORY.md)       в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў Daily Logs (memory/*.md)         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў Persona Files (SOUL.md, etc)     в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n        в”Ӯ\n        в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ  рҹӣ пёҸ Tools & Skills                  в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ                   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў bash, read, write, edit          в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў process, web                     в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  вҖў Skills: coding-agent, github,    в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ    weather, healthcheck, tmux       в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. COMPONENT LIST\n\n### **Core Systems**\n\n| Component | Status | Location | Purpose |\n|-----------|--------|----------|---------|\n| **OpenClaw Gateway** | вң… Active | ~/.openclaw/ | Main AI agent runtime |\n| **NOVA Agent** | вң… Active | workspace/ | Primary AI assistant |\n| **XMAD Control Center** | вң… Active | ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/ | Dashboard & service controller |\n| **Guardian Orchestrator** | вҡ пёҸ Inactive | ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/ | Multi-agent supervisor |\n| **WhatsApp Channel** | вң… Active | Port 18789 | Message interface |\n| **Memory System** | вң… Active | ~/.openclaw/memory/ | Session storage |\n\n### **Active Processes**\n\n| Process | PID | Memory | Port |\n|---------|-----|--------|------|\n| openclaw-gateway | 273 | 428MB | 18789 |\n| openclaw (main) | 271 | 42MB | - |\n| xmad-control-center | 18052 | 40MB | 8765 |\n| claude (3 instances) | - | 1.3GB total | - |\n\n---\n\n## 3. TOOL ANALYSIS\n\n### **Enabled Tools**\nвң… bash - Shell command execution\nвң… process - Background process management\nвң… read - File reading\nвң… write - File creation\nвң… edit - File editing\nвң… web - Web search/fetch\nвң… memory - Memory operations\n\n### **Disabled Tools**\nвқҢ browser - Browser automation\nвқҢ canvas - HTML canvas presentation\nвқҢ nodes - Paired node control\nвқҢ cron - Job scheduling (configured but 0 jobs)\nвқҢ discord - Discord integration\nвқҢ gateway - Gateway management\n\n### **Sandbox Status**\n- **Mode**: OFF (full system access)\n- **Security**: full\n- **Elevated**: Enabled for authorized numbers\n- **Exec Timeout**: 180s\n\n### **Issues Found**\nвҡ пёҸ Tool config warning: `web` and `memory` in allowlist don't match known tools\nвҡ пёҸ No cron jobs scheduled despite cron being available\nвҡ пёҸ Heartbeat disabled (0m interval)\n\n---\n\n## 4. MEMORY ANALYSIS\n\n### **Memory Types**\n\n| Type | Location | Size | Status |\n|------|----------|------|--------|\n| SQLite DB | ~/.openclaw/memory/main.sqlite | 68KB | вң… Active (empty) |\n| Long-term Memory | workspace/MEMORY.md | 9.8KB | вң… Active |\n| Daily Logs | workspace/memory/*.md | ~25KB | вң… Active |\n| Persona Files | workspace/SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md | ~2KB | вң… Active |\n| Session Memory | SQLite tables | 0 chunks | вҡ пёҸ Empty |\n\n### **SQLite Tables**\n- chunks (0 rows)\n- files (0 rows)\n- meta\n- embedding_cache\n- Full-text search tables (chunks_fts*)\n\n### **Memory Issues**\nвҡ пёҸ SQLite memory empty (0 chunks, 0 files)\nвҡ пёҸ LanceDB plugin disabled (vector memory unavailable)\nвҡ пёҸ No semantic search capability\nвҡ пёҸ No knowledge graph\n\n### **Recommendations**\n1. Enable LanceDB for vector memory\n2. Populate SQLite with conversation history\n3. Add semantic recall system\n4. Implement memory consolidation from daily logs\n\n---\n\n## 5. DATABASE ANALYSIS\n\n### **Active Databases**\n| Database | Type | Location | Purpose |\n|----------|------|----------|---------|\n| main.sqlite | SQLite | ~/.openclaw/memory/ | Session memory (empty) |\n| jobs.json | JSON | ~/.openclaw/cron/ | Cron job storage (0 jobs) |\n\n### **Disabled/Inactive**\nвқҢ LanceDB - Vector database (plugin disabled)\nвқҢ Redis - Not installed\nвқҢ PostgreSQL - Not installed\n\n### **Issues**\nвҡ пёҸ No persistent conversation storage\nвҡ пёҸ No vector embeddings\nвҡ пёҸ No semantic search\n\n---\n\n## 6. AGENT SYSTEM\n\n### **Multi-Agent Architecture**\n\n**NOVA (Primary Agent)**\n- Role: Main AI assistant\n- Model: GLM-5 (zai/glm-5)\n- Location: workspace/nova/\n- Status: вң… Active\n\n**Specialist Agents (Inactive)**\n| Agent | Role | Location | Status |\n|-------|------|----------|--------|\n| Developer | Code execution | workspace/developer/ | вҡ пёҸ Config exists, not spawned |\n| Manager | Task coordination | workspace/manager/ | вҡ пёҸ Config exists, not spawned |\n| Researcher | Information gathering | workspace/researcher/ | вҡ пёҸ Config exists, not spawned |\n| Automator | Script execution | workspace/automator/ | вҡ пёҸ Config exists, not spawned |\n\n### **Guardian Orchestrator**\n- Location: ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/\n- Status: вҡ пёҸ Inactive (not running)\n- Purpose: Supervise worker agents\n- Components:\n  - openclaw-bridge.sh\n  - check_guardian.sh\n  - deploy_guardian.sh\n  - coordinator.json\n\n### **Issues**\nвҡ пёҸ Multi-agent system configured but not active\nвҡ пёҸ Guardian orchestrator not running\nвҡ пёҸ No agent spawning currently happening\nвҡ пёҸ Orchestration commands exist but unused\n\n---\n\n## 7. PERFORMANCE ISSUES\n\n### **Memory Usage (8GB Total)**\n- **Used**: 8.1GB (99%!)\n- **Available**: 40MB\n- **Wired**: 1.4GB\n\n### **Top Memory Consumers**\n| Process | Memory | Issue |\n|---------|--------|-------|\n| Claude (3 instances) | 1.3GB | вҡ пёҸ Running multiple Claude instances |\n| Next.js servers (2) | 626MB | вҡ пёҸ Multiple dev servers |\n| OpenClaw Gateway | 428MB | вң… Normal |\n| Ollama | 140MB | вҡ пёҸ Running but unused |\n| XMAD Control | 40MB | вң… Normal |\n\n### **Critical Issues**\nрҹ”ҙ **System nearly out of RAM** (40MB available)\nрҹ”ҙ **3 Claude instances running** (waste of 1GB+)\nрҹ”ҙ **2 Next.js servers** (should be 1 or 0)\nрҹ”ҙ **Ollama running** (140MB, not being used)\n\n### **Recommendations**\n1. Kill unused Claude instances (save 1GB)\n2. Stop inactive Next.js servers (save 600MB)\n3. Stop Ollama if not needed (save 140MB)\n4. **Potential savings: 1.7GB**\n\n---\n\n## 8. SECURITY ISSUES\n\n### **Current Security Posture**\n\n| Setting | Status | Risk |\n|---------|--------|------|\n| Sandbox Mode | OFF | рҹ”ҙ HIGH - Full system access |\n| Exec Security | full | вң… LOW |\n| Elevated Mode | Enabled | вҡ пёҸ MEDIUM - WhatsApp can run elevated |\n| Port Exposure | Localhost only | вң… LOW |\n| API Keys | In config | вҡ пёҸ MEDIUM - Should use env vars |\n\n### **Exposed Ports**\n- 18789 (OpenClaw Gateway) - localhost only вң…\n- 8765 (XMAD Control) - all interfaces вҡ пёҸ\n\n### **Recommendations**\n1. Move API keys to environment variables\n2. Bind XMAD port 8765 to localhost only\n3. Consider enabling sandbox mode\n4. Audit elevated permissions\n\n---\n\n## 9. MISSING FEATURES\n\n### **Compared to Modern Agent Architectures**\n\n| Feature | Status | Priority |\n|---------|--------|----------|\n| Vector Memory | вқҢ Missing | HIGH |\n| Semantic Search | вқҢ Missing | HIGH |\n| Browser Automation | вқҢ Disabled | MEDIUM |\n| Agent Planner | вқҢ Missing | MEDIUM |\n| Task Scheduling | вҡ пёҸ Available but unused | HIGH |\n| Knowledge Graph | вқҢ Missing | LOW |\n| Observability | вҡ пёҸ Basic logging only | MEDIUM |\n| Autonomous Workflows | вқҢ Missing | MEDIUM |\n| Multi-Agent Spawning | вҡ пёҸ Configured but inactive | HIGH |\n| Voice STT/TTS | вҡ пёҸ Available but inactive | LOW |\n\n### **Dead Code / Unused Components**\n- Voice microservices (STT/TTS) - installed but not running\n- Specialist agents - configured but never spawned\n- Guardian orchestrator - installed but inactive\n- Tools (safety-net, gemma-guardian, sandbox) - placeholder code\n- Multiple XMAD hub directories scattered on Desktop\n\n---\n\n## 10. OPTIMIZATION RECOMMENDATIONS\n\n### **IMMEDIATE (Critical)**\n\n1. **Free Up RAM**\n   ```bash\n   # Kill extra Claude instances\n   pkill -f \"claude\" (keep only one)\n   \n   # Stop unused services\n   pkill -f \"next-server\"\n   pkill -f \"ollama\"\n   ```\n   **Savings: 1.7GB RAM**\n\n2. **Enable Heartbeat**\n   - Set to 30m interval\n   - Monitor system health\n   - Check for messages periodically\n\n3. **Fix Tool Config**\n   - Remove `web` and `memory` from allowlist (not valid tools)\n   - Or update to correct tool names\n\n### **SHORT-TERM (This Week)**\n\n4. **Activate Guardian Orchestrator**\n   - Start Guardian service\n   - Enable multi-agent spawning\n   - Test agent coordination\n\n5. **Enable Vector Memory**\n   - Enable LanceDB plugin\n   - Populate with conversation history\n   - Implement semantic search\n\n6. **Set Up Cron Jobs**\n   - Daily backup\n   - Health checks\n   - Memory cleanup\n\n### **MEDIUM-TERM (This Month)**\n\n7. **Consolidate XMAD Directories**\n   - Multiple XMAD versions scattered\n   - Keep only xmad-control-center\n   - Archive old versions\n\n8. **Complete Tool Implementations**\n   - safety-net (checkpoints)\n   - gemma-guardian (file watching)\n   - sandbox (agent isolation)\n\n9. **Security Hardening**\n   - Move API keys to .env\n   - Bind all services to localhost\n   - Enable sandbox mode (optional)\n\n### **LONG-TERM (Future)**\n\n10. **Add Missing Features**\n    - Browser automation\n    - Knowledge graph\n    - Autonomous workflows\n    - Observability stack\n\n---\n\n## 11. PROJECT PURPOSE\n\n### **What This System Does**\n\nThis is a **Multi-Agent AI Command Center** for personal automation and development.\n\n**Primary Goals:**\n1. **Personal AI Assistant** (NOVA) - WhatsApp-based task execution\n2. **Service Controller** (XMAD) - Dashboard for SSH, VPN, services\n3. **Multi-Agent Orchestration** (Guardian) - Coordinate specialist agents\n4. **Voice Services** - STT/TTS capabilities (not yet active)\n\n**How Components Work Together:**\n\n```\nUser вҶ’ WhatsApp вҶ’ NOVA (OpenClaw)\n                  вҶ“\n         Task Analysis & Delegation\n                  вҶ“\n    в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n    вҶ“             вҶ“             вҶ“\nDeveloper    Manager      Researcher\n(executes)   (coordinates) (searches)\n    вҶ“             вҶ“             вҶ“\n         Results collected by NOVA\n                  вҶ“\n         Response to User\n```\n\n**XMAD Role:**\n- Web dashboard for system control\n- Tailscale/SSH management\n- OpenClaw service monitoring\n- Quick actions and scripts\n\n**Guardian Role (when active):**\n- Supervise worker agents\n- Safety checks on code changes\n- Automatic rollback on failures\n- Multi-agent coordination\n\n---\n\n## 12. FINAL SUMMARY\n\n### **System Health: вҡ пёҸ NEEDS ATTENTION**\n\n**Working Well:**\nвң… OpenClaw Gateway stable\nвң… NOVA agent functional\nвң… WhatsApp integration active\nвң… XMAD dashboard operational\nвң… File/command access working\n\n**Critical Issues:**\nрҹ”ҙ **RAM nearly exhausted** (40MB free)\nрҹ”ҙ **Multiple redundant processes** (Claude, Next.js)\nрҹ”ҙ **Guardian orchestrator inactive**\nрҹ”ҙ **Vector memory disabled**\n\n**Quick Wins:**\n1. Kill extra processes вҶ’ Free 1.7GB RAM\n2. Enable heartbeat вҶ’ Proactive monitoring\n3. Activate Guardian вҶ’ Multi-agent capability\n4. Enable LanceDB вҶ’ Semantic memory\n\n**Architecture Status:**\n- Core: вң… Functional\n- Advanced features: вҡ пёҸ Configured but inactive\n- Optimization: рҹ”ҙ Needed (RAM critical)\n\n---\n\n**Audit Complete**\n**Generated**: 2026-03-09 20:04 GMT+4\n**Auditor**: NOVA (рҹҡҖ)"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":706,"output":3492,"cacheRead":48704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52902,"cost":{"input":0.0007059999999999999,"output":0.011174400000000001,"cacheRead":0.0097408,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0216212}},"stopReason":"stop","timestam