{"type":"message","id":"f35bd337","parentId":"6993a9b3","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:04:39.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n# рҹ”Қ NOVA SELF-AUDIT REPORT\n**Generated**: 2026-03-11 17:57 GMT+4\n\n---\n\n## 1. CONFIG AUDIT\n\n**Version**: 2026.3.7  \n**Last Updated**: 2026-03-10\n\n### Model Configuration\n- **Primary**: `zai/glm-4.7` (changed from GLM-5)\n- **Fallback**: `zai/glm-5`\n- **Workspace**: `/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace`\n\n### Memory Limits\n- **Node Options**: Not set (was --max-old-space-size=1536, now removed)\n- **Context Pruning**: cache-ttl mode (1h TTL)\n- **Compaction**: safeguard mode, 24K token floor\n\n### Heartbeat\n- **Interval**: 30m (enabled)\n- **Last Heartbeat**: Unknown\n\n### Hooks\n- **Enabled**: false\n\n### Environment Variables\n- **NODE_ENV**: production\n- **Shell Env**: enabled (30s timeout)\n\n---\n\n## 2. CONNECTION STATUS\n\nвң… **Gateway**: Online (PID 5131)  \nвң… **Port**: 18789 (localhost)  \nвң… **Health**: `{\"ok\":true,\"status\":\"live\"}`  \nвң… **WhatsApp**: Connected (since 17:57:24)  \nвң… **Processes**: 2 active (5131 + 1 child)\n\n---\n\n## 3. ACCESS & PERMISSIONS\n\n### Tools Allowed\nвң… bash - Shell execution  \nвң… process - Process management  \nвң… read - File reading  \nвң… write - File creation  \nвң… edit - File editing  \nвң… web - Web search/fetch  \nвң… memory - Memory operations  \n\n### Tools Denied\nвқҢ browser - Browser automation  \nвқҢ canvas - HTML canvas  \nвқҢ nodes - Remote nodes  \nвқҢ cron - Job scheduling  \nвқҢ discord - Discord integration  \nвқҢ gateway - Gateway management  \n\n### Execution Mode\n- **Host**: node\n- **Security**: full\n- **Sandbox**: OFF\n- **Elevated**: Enabled for WhatsApp (+971504042000, +971502059116, +971562713967)\n- **Timeout**: 180s\n\n---\n\n## 4. VOICE CONFIG\n\n**TTS Provider**: Edge (Microsoft Edge TTS)  \n**TTS Mode**: Auto on inbound messages  \n**STT**: Not configured (uses native device speech-to-text)  \n**Processing**: Local (on Mac mini)\n\n---\n\n## 5. MEMORY & BRAIN\n\n### Memory Files (~/.openclaw/memory/)\n- main.sqlite (68KB) - SQLite database\n- nova-identity.md (1.3KB)\n- openclaw-config-valid-keys-20260226.md (1.1KB)\n- openclaw-shell-exec-fix-20260227.json (1.9KB)\n\n### Persona Files (workspace/)\n- SOUL.md - Defines Nova personality\n- IDENTITY.md - Name, emoji, vibe\n- MEMORY.md - Long-term memory (needs update)\n- USER.md - User info\n\n### Session Memory (workspace/memory/)\n- 2026-02-09.md (7KB)\n- 2026-02-10.md (4.5KB)\n- 2026-02-10-infisical-success.md (3.7KB)\n- 2026-02-11-stage1-attempts.md (9.5KB)\n- 2026-02-11-stage1-tasks.md (5.8KB)\n\n### Database Content\n- **Chunks**: 0\n- **Files**: 0\n- **Status**: Empty (not recording conversations)\n\n---\n\n## 6. HEARTBEAT & HEALTH\n\n**Heartbeat**: Enabled (30m interval)  \n**Last Heartbeat**: Unknown (not logged)  \n**Memory Usage**:  \n- Gateway: 482MB RSS\n- Disk: 20MB total\n\n**System Memory**: 8.1GB used (99%), 34MB free рҹ”ҙ\n\n---\n\n## 7. OPTIMIZATIONS\n\n### Applied\n- **Block Streaming**: ON (3000-4000 char chunks)\n- **Human Delay**: natural mode\n- **Context Pruning**: cache-ttl (1h)\n- **Compaction**: safeguard mode (24K floor)\n- **Chunk Coalescing**: 1500 min chars, 1000ms idle\n\n### Streaming Config\n- Break: text_end\n- Min chunk: 3000 chars\n- Max chunk: 4000 chars\n- Coalesce idle: 1000ms\n\n---\n\n## 8. PLUGINS & SKILLS\n\n### Plugins Enabled\nвң… whatsapp - Active  \nвң… memory-lancedb - Active (vector memory)\n\n### Plugins Disabled\nвқҢ browser - Disabled  \nвқҢ canvasHost - Disabled\n\n### Skills Allowed\n- apple-notes\n- apple-reminders\n- github\n- gog\n- coding-agent\n- weather\n\n### Cron Jobs\n- **Total**: 0\n- **Status**: No scheduled tasks\n\n---\n\n## SUMMARY\n\n**Status**: вң… Operational  \n**Model**: GLM-4.7 primary, GLM-5 fallback  \n**Gateway**: Online, healthy  \n**Memory**: Critical (34MB free system-wide)  \n**WhatsApp**: Connected  \n**Heartbeat**: E