{"type":"message","id":"345c07c9","parentId":"4b758454","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:13:29.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n# рҹ“Ҡ ALL RUNNING APPS & STARTUP ITEMS\n\n## **LOGIN ITEMS (Starting automatically)**\nвҡ пёҸ **These run when you login:**\n\n| App | RAM Impact | Can Disable? |\n|-----|-----------|--------------|\n| **AnyDesk** | ~50MB | вң… Yes (if not using remote) |\n| **Ollama** (3x!) | ~500MB+ | вң… Yes (if not using AI locally) |\n| **Dropbox** | ~100MB+ | вң… Yes (if not syncing) |\n| **Wispr Flow** | ~50MB | вң… Yes (voice app) |\n\n---\n\n## **CURRENTLY RUNNING (by RAM usage)**\n\n### **Big Consumers:**\n| Process | RAM | What is it | Kill? |\n|---------|-----|------------|------|\n| openclaw-gateway | 538MB | **Keep** (me!) | вқҢ NO |\n| mds_stores | 121MB | Spotlight (system) | вқҢ NO |\n| WindowServer | 105MB | Display (system) | вқҢ NO |\n| Finder | 80MB | File manager | вқҢ NO |\n| Terminal | 64MB | Terminal | вҡ пёҸ If not using |\n\n### **Background Apps (Non-System):**\n| Process | RAM | What is it | Kill? |\n|---------|-----|------------|------|\n| **AnyDesk** (2x) | ~80MB | Remote desktop | вң… YES |\n| **Samsung printer** | ~50MB | Printer service | вң… YES |\n| **Spotlight** | ~60MB | Search indexing | вң… YES |\n| CalendarAgent | ~50MB | Calendar sync | вң… YES |\n| NotificationCenter | ~50MB | Notifications | вң… YES |\n\n---\n\n## **рҹҺҜ RECOMMENDATION - Kill These:**\n\n### **Immediate (Safe to kill):**\n```bash\n# Kill AnyDesk (if not using remote desktop)\nkillall AnyDesk\n\n# Kill Ollama (if not running local AI)\nkillall ollama\n\n# Remove Samsung printer service (if not printing)\nkillall \"Samsung_M2070_Series__SEC30CDA73468E4_\"\n```\n\n### **Disable from Startup (Settings):**\n1. **System Settings вҶ’ General вҶ’ Login Items**\n   - вқҢ Remove AnyDesk (if not needed)\n   - вқҢ Remove Ollama (all 3 instances!)\n   - вқҢ Remove Dropbox (if not syncing)\n   - вқҢ Remove Wispr Flow (voice app)\n\n---\n\n## **рҹ’° POTENTIAL SAVINGS:**\n\n| Action | RAM Saved |\n|--------|-----------|\n| Kill AnyDesk | ~80MB |\n| Kill Ollama (3x) | ~500MB |\n| Kill Samsung printer | ~50MB |\n| **Total** | **~630MB** |\n\n**Would give you ~2.1GB free!**\n\nWant me to kill AnyDesk and Samsung printer now?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":79453,"output":635,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81240,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773241994456}}
