{"type":"message","id":"b8a18cc0","parentId":"b19b6468","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:37:01.472Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n# рҹ“Ғ **OPENCLAW INSTALLATION LOCATIONS**\n\n## **Primary Installation**\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/                          вҶҗ MAIN CONFIG DIR (20MB)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw.json                     вҶҗ Config file\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ workspace/                        вҶҗ Nova's workspace (696KB)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ memory/                           вҶҗ SQLite DB (80KB)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ logs/                             вҶҗ Log files (3.3MB)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ credentials/                      вҶҗ 15MB\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ media/                            вҶҗ Inbound media (684KB)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ scripts/                          вҶҗ Utility scripts (24KB)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ skills/                           вҶҗ Custom skills (8KB)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ agents/                           вҶҗ Subagent runs (664KB)\nв””в”Җв”Җ devices/                          вҶҗ Device identities (8KB)\n```\n\n## **Binary Location**\n\n```\n~/.bun/bin/openclaw                   вҶҗ Executable (symlink)\n  вҶ’ Bun global package\n```\n\n## **Launch Agent**\n\n```\n~/Library/LaunchAgents/\nв””в”Җв”Җ com.openclaw.agent.plist          вҶҗ Auto-start script\n```\n\n---\n\n## **рҹ“Ҡ SIZE BREAKDOWN**\n\n| Directory | Size | Purpose |\n|-----------|------|---------|\n| **credentials** | 15MB | API keys, tokens |\n| **logs** | 3.3MB | System logs |\n| **agents** | 664KB | Subagent runs |\n| **media** | 684KB | WhatsApp media |\n| **workspace** | 696KB | Nova's brain |\n| **memory** | 80KB | SQLite DB |\n| **scripts** | 24KB | Utility scripts |\n| **Total** | **20MB** | All OpenClaw data |\n\n---\n\n## **рҹ”Қ OTHER LOCATIONS (Searched)**\n\n- `/usr/local/*openclaw*` вҶ’ Not found\n- `~/Library/*openclaw*` вҶ’ Only launch agent\n- `~/*openclaw*` вҶ’ Only main dir\n\n---\n\n## **вң… CLEAN INSTALLATION**\n\n**OpenClaw is cleanly installed in:**\n- **Config**: `~/.openclaw/`\n- **Binary**: `~/.bun/bin/openclaw`\n- **Launcher**: `~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.openclaw.agent.plist`\n\n**No scattered files!** Very clean setup.\n\n---\n\nWant me to check anything specific in these directories?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":73,"output":507,"cacheRead":86400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86980,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773243413081}}
