{"type":"message","id":"d4f9d402","parentId":"ebe4b560","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:42:27.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n# вң… **YES, OPENCLAW HAS WATCHDOG!**\n\n## **Watchdog Location & Status**\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/scripts/watchdog.sh      вҶҗ Main watchdog script\n~/.openclaw/logs/watchdog.log        вҶҗ Logs (25KB)\n```\n\n---\n\n## **рҹ“Ҡ WATCHDOG CONFIGURATION**\n\n| Setting | Value |\n|---------|-------|\n| **Max Memory** | 1400MB |\n| **Check Interval** | 30 seconds |\n| **Health URL** | http://127.0.0.1:18789/ |\n| **Max Restarts** | 10 per hour |\n| **Reports To** | XMAD Control Center |\n\n---\n\n## **рҹ”Қ WHAT WATCHDOG DOES**\n\n1. **Monitors Memory** - Kills if > 1400MB\n2. **Health Checks** - Tests /health endpoint every 30s\n3. **Crash Detection** - Restarts if process dies\n4. **Freeze Detection** - Checks for UN (I/O hang) state\n5. **Auto-Restart** - Restarts gateway up to 10x/hour\n6. **Reports** - Writes status to XMAD dashboard\n\n---\n\n## **рҹ“Ҳ CURRENT STATUS**\n\n**Watchdog Script**: вң… Exists (`~/.openclaw/scripts/watchdog.sh`)\n\n**Watchdog Process**: вқҢ **NOT RUNNING**\n\n- Last logged: 2026-03-11 01:52:17 (stopped ~18 hours ago)\n- No watchdog process found\n- Not in launchctl\n\n---\n\n## **вҡ пёҸ FINDING**\n\n**Watchdog is configured but NOT active!**\n\nOpenClaw is running without watchdog protection. If it crashes or exceeds memory, nobody will restart it.\n\n---\n\n## **рҹҺҜ RECOMMENDATION**\n\n**Start the watchdog** for protection:\n\n```bash\n# Option 1: Run manually (foreground)\n~/.openclaw/scripts/watchdog.sh\n\n# Option 2: Run in background\nnohup ~/.openclaw/scripts/watchdog.sh &\n\n# Option 3: Create launch agent for auto-start\n# (requires creating plist file)\n```\n\n**Want me to start the watchdog now?**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":89402,"output":464,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89866,"cost":{"input":0,"output