{"type":"message","id":"31aa2ecc","parentId":"76cf3e8f","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:44:46.423Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_af243d0e67084ef794bbec62","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC \"-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN\" \"http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd\">\n<plist version=\"1.0\">\n<dict>\n  <key>Label</key>\n  <string>com.openclaw.agent</string>\n\n  <key>ProgramArguments</key>\n  <array>\n    <string>/bin/bash</string>\n    <string>/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/scripts/start-optimized.sh</string>\n  </array>\n\n  <key>WorkingDirectory</key>\n  <string>/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw</string>\n\n  <key>KeepAlive</key>\n  <dict>\n    <key>SuccessfulExit</key>\n    <false/>\n    <key>Crashed</key>\n    <true/>\n  </dict>\n\n  <key>ThrottleInterval</key>\n  <integer>10</integer>\n\n  <key>RunAtLoad</key>\n  <true/>\n\n  <key>StandardOutPath</key>\n  <string>/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/logs/launchd.out.log</string>\n\n  <key>StandardErrorPath</key>\n  <string>/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/logs/launchd.err.log</string>\n\n  <key>EnvironmentVariables</key>\n  <dict>\n    <key>NODE_ENV</key>\n    <string>production</string>\n    <key>NODE_OPTIONS</key>\n    <string>--max-old-space-size=1536</string>\n    <key>PATH</key>\n    <string>/Users/ahmadabdullah/.nvm/versions/node/v22.16.0/bin:/Users/ahmadabdullah/.bun/bin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/sbin:/opt/homebrew/bin</string>\n  </dict>\n\n  <key>ProcessType</key>\n  <string>Interactive</string>\n\n  <key>Nice</key>\n  <integer>5</integer>\n\n  <key>SoftResourceLimits</key>\n  <dict>\n    <key>NumberOfFiles</key>\n    <integer>1024</integer>\n  </dict>\n\n  <key>HardResourceLimits</key>\n  <dict>\n    <key>NumberOfFiles</key>\n    <integer>2048</integer>\n  </dict>\n</dict>\n</plist>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773243886414}}
{"type":"message","id":"321c5d80","parentId":"31aa2ecc","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:45:01.962Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n# рҹ—‘пёҸ **GARBAGE COLLECTION (GC) STATUS**\n\n## **CURRENT GC SETTINGS**\n\n### **Launch Agent (Auto-Start)**\n```xml\nNODE_OPTIONS: --max-old-space-size=1536\n```\n- вң… **Memory limit**: 1536MB (1.5GB)\n- вқҢ **GC interval**: NOT SET\n\n### **start-production.sh**\n```bash\nnode --max-old-space-size=768 --gc-interval=100\n```\n- вң… **Memory limit**: 768MB\n- вң… **GC interval**: 100ms (aggressive!)\n\n### **start-optimized.sh** (Current)\n```bash\nNODE_OPTIONS removed - OpenClaw handles memory internally\n```\n- вқҢ **No NODE_OPTIONS set**\n- вқҢ **GC not configured**\n\n---\n\n## **рҹ”Қ WHAT THIS MEANS**\n\n**Current Setup**:\n- Memory management handled by OpenClaw internally (via config)\n- **No explicit GC tuning**\n- Node.js default GC behavior\n\n**Impact**:\n- GC runs when Node.js thinks it's needed (less predictable)\n- May cause occasional pauses during GC\n- Memory usage may fluctuate more\n\n---\n\n## **вҡ пёҸ INCONSISTENCY FOUND**\n\n**3 different startup methods with different settings:**\n\n| Method | Memory | GC | Used By |\n|--------|--------|-------|---------|\n| **Launch Agent** | 1536MB | None | System auto-start |\n| **start-production.sh** | 768MB | 100ms | XMAD Dashboard |\n| **start-optimized.sh** | Auto | None | Manual start |\n\n---\n\n## **рҹҺҜ RECOMMENDATION**\n\n**Add GC tuning for better performance:**\n\n```bash\n# Add to launch agent NODE_OPTIONS:\n--gc-interval=100\n\n# This forces GC every 100ms, keeping memory lower\n# and reducing pause times\n```\n\n**Benefits**:\n- More predictable memory usage\n- Fewer large GC pauses\n- Better for 8GB RAM system\n\n---\n\n**Want me to update the launch agent with GC settings?**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":67726,"output":443,"cacheRead":22144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90313,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773243886419}}
