{"type":"message","id":"6854fd36","parentId":"884060e9","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:00:14.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me start the systematic unification myself. First, let me create the master plan and start Phase 1:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7ff5027ff50c42ecba750291","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/UNIFICATION_MASTER_PLAN.md","content":"# рҹ”§ OpenClaw/Nova Complete Unification Project\n**Date**: 2026-03-11\n**Goal**: SSOT - Single Source of Truth for entire system\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ӣ PROJECT PHASES\n\n### вң… Phase 1: Discovery & Mapping\n**Status**: IN PROGRESS\n\n**Tasks**:\n- [ ] Find all OpenClaw files (~/.openclaw/, Desktop, Documents)\n- [ ] Find all Nova brain/memory/persona files\n- [ ] Find all startup scripts (watchdog, start-optimized, start-production)\n- [ ] Find all Guardian files\n- [ ] Map duplicates and versions\n- [ ] Identify best/most recent versions\n\n**Locations to Search**:\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/openclaw/\n~/Desktop/KEEP/\n~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/\n~/Library/LaunchAgents/\n```\n\n---\n\n### рҹ”„ Phase 2: Unification & Optimization\n**Status**: PENDING\n\n**Tasks**:\n- [ ] **Configs**: Merge openclaw.json (keep best settings)\n- [ ] **Memory**: Unify MEMORY.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md\n- [ ] **Brain**: Consolidate workspace/memory/ files\n- [ ] **Scripts**: Create one optimized startup script with:\n  - GC: --gc-interval=100\n  - Memory: --max-old-space-size=768\n  - Watchdog: Auto-restart\n  - Memory spike detection\n  - Auto-cleanup on crash\n- [ ] **TTS/STT**: Keep Edge TTS (lightest), document setup\n- [ ] **Launch Agent**: Update with unified settings\n\n**Optimized Settings for 8GB RAM**:\n```json\n{\n  \"max-old-space-size\": 768,\n  \"gc-interval\": 100,\n  \"watchdog\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"max_mem\": 900,\n    \"check_interval\": 30\n  },\n  \"heartbeat\": \"30m\",\n  \"context_pruning\": \"aggressive\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### рҹ–ҘпёҸ Phase 3: XMAD Dashboard Integration\n**Status**: PENDING\n\n**New Pages/Features**:\n- [ ] OpenClaw Status Page\n  - PID, Memory, Health\n  - Config display\n  - Active tools\n  - Heartbeat status\n\n- [ ] Memory & Brain Viewer\n  - Persona files (SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md)\n  - Long-term memory (MEMORY.md)\n  - Session logs\n  - Edit capability\n\n- [ ] PC Optimization Script\n  - Add boost-machine.sh to dashboard\n  - One-click optimization\n  - Show before/after RAM\n\n- [ ] Backup & Restore\n  - Backup button\n  - Restore from backup\n  - Auto-backup schedule\n\n---\n\n### рҹ—‘пёҸ Phase 4: Cleanup & Protection\n**Status**: PENDING\n\n**Tasks**:\n- [ ] Remove all duplicate files\n- [ ] Archive old versions to ~/Desktop/xmad-backups/\n- [ ] Lock critical files with chmod 444\n- [ ] Create SSOT documentation\n- [ ] Verify only one source of truth exists\n\n**Files to Lock**:\n```bash\nchmod 444 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nchmod 444 ~/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md\nchmod 444 ~/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md\nchmod 444 ~/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n```\n\n---\n\n### рҹ“ҡ Phase 5: Documentation & Safety\n**Status**: PENDING\n\n**Documentation**:\n- [ ] SSOT_LOCATION.md - Where everything lives\n- [ ] BACKUP_RESTORE.md - How to backup/restore\n- [ ] TROUBLESHOOTING.md - Common issues\n- [ ] ARCHITECTURE.md - System overview\n- [ ] FILE_PERMISSIONS.md - What's locked and why\n\n**Backup System**:\n```bash\n# Auto-backup script\n# Daily: ~/.openclaw/backup/daily/\n# Weekly: ~/.openclaw/backup/weekly/\n# Keep: 7 days daily, 4 weeks weekly\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҜ SUCCESS CRITERIA\n\nвң… Only ONE openclaw.json (no duplicates)\nвң… Only ONE set of persona files\nвң… Only ONE startup script (optimized)\nвң… Watchdog running and protecting\nвң… GC tuned for 8GB RAM\nвң… Dashboard can view/control everything\nвң… All duplicates archived or deleted\nвң… Critical files password-protected\nвң… Full documentation in XMAD\n\n---\n\n#