{"type":"message","id":"2e36346a","parentId":"2f70fd08","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:01:50.443Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good! Now let me map all directories systematically:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ebbdd1eb05714d7fbb3b253b","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/DISCOVERY_RESULTS.md","content":"# рҹ”Қ OpenClaw Discovery Results\n**Date**: 2026-03-11 20:00\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ғ PRIMARY LOCATIONS\n\n### 1. Main Installation\n```\n~/.openclaw/                          вҶҗ SSOT (PRIMARY)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw.json                     вҶҗ Config\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ workspace/                        вҶҗ Nova's brain\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ SOUL.md\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ IDENTITY.md\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ MEMORY.md\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ USER.md\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ memory/                       вҶҗ Daily logs\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ scripts/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ watchdog.sh                  вҶҗ Watchdog\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ start-optimized.sh           вҶҗ Startup\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ start-production.sh          вҶҗ Alternative\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ memory/                           вҶҗ SQLite DB\nв””в”Җв”Җ logs/                             вҶҗ All logs\n```\n\n### 2. XMAD Control Center\n```\n~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw/                         вҶҗ DASHBOARD FILES ONLY\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ logs/                        вҶҗ Empty\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ watchdog/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ watchdog.log             вҶҗ Copy of main log?\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ status.json              вҶҗ Watchdog status\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ nova-self-audit-prompt.md\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ server.js                         вҶҗ Dashboard server\nв””в”Җв”Җ index.html                        вҶҗ Dashboard UI\n```\n\n### 3. Guardian Orchestrator\n```\n~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/         вҶҗ MULTI-AGENT SYSTEM\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw-bridge.sh                вҶҗ Bridge to OpenClaw\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ check_guardian.sh\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ install.sh\nв””в”Җв”Җ logs/                             вҶҗ Guardian logs\n```\n\n### 4. Old Guardian\n```\n~/.guardian-orchestrator/              вҶҗ OLD VERSION\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ logs/\nв””в”Җв”Җ jobs/\n```\n\n### 5. XMAD Hub\n```\n~/Desktop/xmad-hub/                    вҶҗ ANOTHER XMAD VERSION\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ (duplicate of xmad-control-center?)\nв””в”Җв”Җ Needs investigation\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”Қ DUPLICATES FOUND\n\n| File Type | Primary | Duplicates | Action |\n|-----------|---------|------------|--------|\n| **Config** | ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | None | вң… Keep |\n| **Persona** | ~/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md | None | вң… Keep |\n| **Watchdog** | ~/.openclaw/scripts/watchdog.sh | XMAD copy | рҹ—‘пёҸ Delete XMAD copy |\n| **Logs** | ~/.openclaw/logs/ | XMAD/openclaw/logs/ | рҹ—‘пёҸ Delete XMAD copy |\n\n---\n\n## вҡ пёҸ ISSUES FOUND\n\n1. **Multiple XMAD versions**:\n   - ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/ (current)\n   - ~/Desktop/xmad-hub/ (old?)\n\n2. **Multiple Guardian versions**:\n   - ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/ (current)\n   - ~/.guardian-orchestrator/ (old)\n\n3. **Watchdog logs duplicated**:\n   - Main: ~/.openclaw/logs/watchdog.log\n   - Copy: XMAD/openclaw/logs/watchdog.log\n\n4. **Emergency backup on Desktop**:\n   - ~/Desktop/openclaw_emergency_backup_1773158481.tar.gz\n   - Should be archived elsewhere\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ҡ SIZE ANALYSIS\n\n| Location | Size | Status |\n|----------|------|--------|\n| ~/.openclaw/ | 20MB | вң… Primary |\n| XMAD/openclaw/ | <1MB | вҡ пёҸ Duplicate |\n| .guardian-orchestrator-2026/ | 460KB | вң… Keep |\n| .guardian-orchestrator/ | 20KB | вҡ пёҸ Old |\n| xmad-hub/ | ? | вҡ пёҸ Investigate |\n\n---\n\n## вң… NEXT STEPS\n\n1. **Investigate xmad-hub/** - What's in there?\n2. **Backup everything** - Before cleanup\n3. **Delete duplicates** - XMAD/openclaw/ copies\n4. **Archive old Guardian** - .guardian-orchestrator/\n5. **Unify configs** - One openclaw.json\n6. **Update XMAD** - Point to primary locations\n\n---\n\n**Status**: Discovery 80% complete\n**Pending**: Investigate xmad-hub, verify XMAD usage\n"