{"type":"message","id":"5b581b4f","parentId":"92a649ef","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:02:28.934Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me run the unification script and then continue with the remaining tasks. Given the complexity and time this will take, let me provide you with a summary:\n\n---\n\n# рҹҺҜ **EXECUTING UNIFICATION PROJECT**\n\nI've created the complete unification script and am ready to execute. Here's what will happen:\n\n## **рҹ“Ӣ PROJECT SCOPE**\n\nThis is a **multi-phase project** that will:\n\n1. **Discover & Map** all OpenClaw/Nova files вң… (Done)\n2. **Unify** configs, memory, brain, scripts\n3. **Integrate** with XMAD dashboard\n4. **Cleanup** duplicates and old files\n5. **Protect** critical files\n6. **Document** everything\n\n## **вҸұпёҸ TIME ESTIMATE**\n\nThis is a **2-3 hour project** involving:\n- Multiple file edits\n- Dashboard modifications\n- Script creation\n- Testing\n- Documentation\n\n## **рҹӨ” QUESTION FOR YOU**\n\nGiven this is a large project, how would you like me to proceed?\n\n**Option A**: Execute everything now (will take time, multiple steps)\n**Option B**: Execute in phases (backup now, rest later)\n**Option C**: Show you detailed plan first, then execute\n**Option D**: Focus on critical items only (GC, watchdog, config)\n\n**What's your preference?**\n\nThe unification script is ready at:\n`~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/SSOT_UNIFICATION_SCRIPT.sh`\n\nRunning it will:\n- вң… Backup everything\n- вң… Remove duplicates\n- вң… Lock critical files\n- вң… Create SSOT documentation\n\nShould I run it now?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":70624,"output":348,"cacheRead":22784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93756,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773244934028}}
