{"type":"message","id":"77f79796","parentId":"29a2b891","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:16:12.176Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-11 20:01:31 GMT+4] Exec failed (oceanic-, signal SIGTERM)\nSystem: [2026-03-11 20:01:31 GMT+4] Exec failed (nova-val, signal SIGTERM)\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"2A4BD026A025FB32851C\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+971504042000\",\n  \"sender\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant (+971504042000)\",\n  \"id\": \"+971504042000\",\n  \"name\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant\",\n  \"e164\": \"+971504042000\"\n}\n```\n\nActually itвҖҷs not a project or complex at all . ItвҖҷs so simple. \nIf you read again what I sent you before . ItвҖҷs all about cleaning all openclaw files. \nAs we had before 8 times we installed openclaw.  So some of this instalation and scripts and files are still there in home and desktop directory and other directory that usually openclaw saved its files there. \nSo I need to keep only your last instalation and all other we need to delete them. But you can before deleting them to quick check if anything valuable then copy it and add it to your curent files otherwise we delete them all so we have only SSOT in this of related to openclaw.\nMaybe my last message was in more detailes but itвҖҷs simple as that clean openclaw and remove any old files and unneeded files . \n\nAnd then in desktop/xmad-control-center app . We have dashboard there and we add some old scripts and openclaw related . So you need to uodate it with the latest and clean one we made after cleaning ."}],"timestamp":1773245772166}}
