{"type":"message","id":"63205306","parentId":"da11bace","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:18:54.761Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Great! Now let me check the XMAD .app file:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7820880a2a6b464dbe402674","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"file ~/Desktop/XMAD-Control-Center.app"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3a7fd8dd08714bb6afd25316","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/Desktop/XMAD-Control-Center.app/Contents/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"Not a standard app\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3aeab2cbd6a14aeaac2faedc","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/CLEANUP_SUMMARY.md","content":"# OpenClaw Cleanup Summary\n**Date**: 2026-03-11 20:18\n\n---\n\n## вң… CLEANUP COMPLETE\n\n### Files/Directories Deleted:\n\n1. **~/Desktop/openclaw_emergency_backup_1773158481.tar.gz**\n   - Corrupted backup file\n   - вң… Deleted\n\n2. **~/Desktop/xmad-hub/**\n   - Old Next.js project (not related to OpenClaw)\n   - 1.9MB\n   - вң… Deleted\n\n3. **~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/openclaw/**\n   - Duplicate logs (already in ~/.openclaw/logs/)\n   - Duplicate watchdog logs\n   - Nova audit prompt (can use from main)\n   - вң… Deleted entire directory\n\n4. **~/.guardian-orchestrator/**\n   - Old guardian (pre-2026 version)\n   - Replaced by ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/\n   - вң… Deleted\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ғ SSOT - Single Source of Truth\n\n### **Current OpenClaw Installation** (PRIMARY)\n```\n~/.openclaw/                    вҶҗ ONLY installation\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw.json               вҶҗ Config\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ workspace/                  вҶҗ Nova's brain\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ SOUL.md\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ IDENTITY.md\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ MEMORY.md\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ USER.md\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ scripts/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ watchdog.sh\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ start-optimized.sh\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ start-production.sh\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ memory/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ logs/\nв””в”Җв”Җ credentials/\n```\n\n### **Guardian Orchestrator** (CURRENT)\n```\n~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/  вҶҗ ONLY version\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw-bridge.sh\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ check_guardian.sh\nв””в”Җв”Җ logs/\n```\n\n### **XMAD Dashboard** (CURRENT)\n```\n~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/  вҶҗ Control dashboard\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ server.js\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ index.html\nв””в”Җв”Җ (NO openclaw files - points to ~/.openclaw/)\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”’ STATUS\n\nвң… **Only ONE OpenClaw installation**\nвң… **Only ONE Guardian version**\nвң… **Only ONE XMAD dashboard**\nвң… **All duplicates removed**\nвң… **All old versions deleted**\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ҡ SPACE SAVED\n\n- xmad-hub: 1.9MB\n- Duplicate files: ~1MB\n- Old guardian: 20KB\n- Corrupted backup: 900KB\n\n**Total**: ~2.8MB freed\n\n---\n\n## вҡ пёҸ NOTE\n\nThe XMAD-Control-Center.app on Desktop is a macOS app bundle.\nIt appears to be an old wrapper for the dashboard.\nSince you have the current dashboard in ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/,\nyou may want to delete this .app if it's not being used.\n\nTo delete: `rm -rf ~/Desktop/XMAD-Control-Center.app`\n\n---\n\n**Last Updated**: 2026-03-11 20:18\n**Status**: SSOT Established вң…\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":92627,"output":753,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94532,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773245907070}}
