{"type":"message","id":"fd3b56f9","parentId":"093e4d53","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:19:36.727Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! The XMAD server already points to the correct location (`~/.openclaw`). Now let me add the optimization script endpoint to the dashboard:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a315670746a24fd48b6cc067","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/server.js","offset":400,"limit":100}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_574b0a65edbb455493bc5889","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/README_OPENCLAW.md","content":"# OpenClaw - Single Source of Truth (SSOT)\n\n## рҹ“Қ Installation Location\n\n**Primary**: `~/.openclaw/`\n\nThis is the ONLY OpenClaw installation on this system.\n\n---\n\n## рҹ—ӮпёҸ Directory Structure\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw.json                 вҶҗ Main configuration file\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ workspace/                    вҶҗ Nova's brain\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ SOUL.md                   вҶҗ Personality & rules\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ IDENTITY.md               вҶҗ Name, emoji, vibe\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ MEMORY.md                 вҶҗ Long-term memory\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ USER.md                   вҶҗ User information\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ memory/                   вҶҗ Daily session logs\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ scripts/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ watchdog.sh               вҶҗ Auto-restart protection\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ start-optimized.sh        вҶҗ Main startup script\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ start-production.sh       вҶҗ Alternative startup\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ memory/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ main.sqlite               вҶҗ Session database\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ logs/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw.log              вҶҗ Main log\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ gateway.log               вҶҗ Gateway log\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ watchdog.log              вҶҗ Watchdog log\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ credentials/                  вҶҗ API keys (locked)\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ devices/                      вҶҗ Device identities\nв””в”Җв”Җ agents/                       вҶҗ Subagent runs\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹҡҖ Startup Process\n\n### Automatic (Recommended)\nOpenClaw starts automatically via LaunchAgent:\n```bash\n~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.openclaw.agent.plist\n```\n\n### Manual\n```bash\n# Start OpenClaw\n~/.openclaw/scripts/start-optimized.sh\n\n# Start with watchdog\n~/.openclaw/scripts/watchdog.sh &\n\n# Stop\npkill -f openclaw-gateway\n```\n\n---\n\n## вҡҷпёҸ Configuration\n\n### Current Settings (Optimized for 8GB RAM)\n```json\n{\n  \"model\": {\n    \"primary\": \"zai/glm-5\",\n    \"fallbacks\": [\"zai/glm-4.7\"]\n  },\n  \"heartbeat\": \"30m\",\n  \"max-old-space-size\": \"768MB\",\n  \"gc-interval\": \"100ms\",\n  \"watchdog\": {\n    \"max_mem\": 900,\n    \"check_interval\": 30\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Launch Agent Settings\n```xml\nNODE_OPTIONS: --max-old-space-size=768 --gc-interval=100\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹӣЎпёҸ Protection\n\n### Locked Files (Read-Only)\n- `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md`\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md`\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md`\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md`\n\n### To Edit Locked Files\n```bash\n# Temporarily unlock\nchmod 644 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\n# Edit file\nnano ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\n# Re-lock\nchmod 444 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹҗ• Watchdog\n\nThe watchdog monitors and protects OpenClaw:\n\n**Location**: `~/.openclaw/scripts/watchdog.sh`\n\n**What it does**:\n- Checks memory every 30 seconds\n- Restarts if memory exceeds 900MB\n- Restarts if process crashes\n- Restarts if health check fails\n- Reports status to XMAD Dashboard\n\n**Start Watchdog**:\n```bash\n~/.openclaw/scripts/watchdog.sh &\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ҡ Monitoring\n\n### XMAD Dashboard\nAccess at: http://localhost:8765\n\nShows:\n- OpenClaw status (online/offline)\n- Memory usage\n- PID\n- Health status\n- Watchdog status\n\n### Health Check\n```bash\ncurl http://localhost:18789/health\n```\n\n### View Logs\n```bash\n# Main log\ntail -f ~/.openclaw/logs/openclaw.log\n\n# Gateway log\ntail -f ~/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log\n\n# Watchdog log\ntail -f ~/.openclaw/logs/watchdog.log\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”§ Troubleshooting\n\n### OpenClaw Not Running\n```bash\n# Check if process exists\npgrep -f openclaw-gateway\n\n# Check port\nlsof -i :18789\n\n# Restart\n~/.openclaw/scripts/start-optimized.sh\n```\n\n### High Memory Usage\n```bash\n# Check memory\nps aux | grep openclaw-gateway\n\n# If > 900MB, watchdog will auto-restart\n# Manual restart:\npkill -f openclaw-gateway\nsleep 2\n~/.openclaw/scripts/start-optimized.sh\n```\n\n### WhatsApp Not Connected\n```bash\n# Check WhatsApp process\npgrep -f whatsapp\n\n# Restart OpenClaw\npkill -f openclaw-gateway\nsleep 2\n~/.openclaw/scripts/start-optimized.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“қ Backup & Restore\n\n### Backup\n```bash\n# Create backup\ncd ~/.openclaw\ntar -czf ~/Desktop/openclaw-backup-$(date +%Y%m%d).tar.gz .\n\n# Or use built-in backup\n~/.openclaw/scripts/backup.sh\n```\n\n### Restore\n```bash\n# Stop OpenClaw\npkill -f openclaw-gateway\n\n# Extract backup\ncd ~/\ntar -xzf ~/Desktop/openclaw-backup-YYYYMMDD.tar.gz\n\n# Restart\n~/.openclaw/scripts/start-optimized.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҜ Best Practices\n\n1. **Don't edit locked files** unless necessary\n2. **Let watchdog handle crashes** - don't manually restart constantly\n3. **Check XMAD dashboard** for status before making changes\n4. **Keep backups** before major changes\n5. **Monitor memory usage** - should stay under 768MB\n6. **Don't run multiple instances** - only one openclaw-gateway\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“ұ Related Systems\n\n### Guardian Orchestrator\n**Location**: `~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/`\n\nMulti-agent system that works with OpenClaw.\n\n### XMAD Dashboard\n**Location**: `~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/`\n\nControl and monitoring dashboard for OpenClaw.\n\n---\n\n**Last Updated**: 2026-03-11\n**Version**: OpenClaw 2026.3.8\n**Status**: SSOT Established вң…\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":62969,"output":1482,"cacheRead":31104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95555,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773245955464}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef66b278","parentId":"fd3b56f9","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:19:36.732Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a315670746a24fd48b6cc067","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        });\n    }\n};\n\n// Docs handler\nconst docsHandler = {\n    list: () => {\n        const locations = [IMPORTANT_DOCS_DIR, XMAD_DIR, GUARDIAN_DIR];\n        const docs = [];\n\n        for (const loc of locations) {\n            if (fs.existsSync(loc)) {\n                try {\n                    fs.readdirSync(loc)\n                        .filter(f => f.endsWith('.md'))\n                        .forEach(f => docs.push({ name: f.replace('.md', ''), location: loc }));\n                } catch {}\n            }\n        }\n        return { ok: true, docs };\n    },\n    read: (name) => {\n        // Security: sanitize name to prevent path traversal\n        const safeName = name.replace(/[\\/\\\\\\.]/g, '');\n        const locations = [\n            path.join(IMPORTANT_DOCS_DIR, `${safeName}.md`),\n            path.join(XMAD_DIR, `${safeName}.md`),\n            path.join(GUARDIAN_DIR, `${safeName}.md`)\n        ];\n\n        for (const loc of locations) {\n            if (fs.existsSync(loc)) {\n                return { ok: true, content: fs.readFileSync(loc, 'utf8'), path: loc };\n            }\n        }\n        return { ok: false, content: '(Document not found)', searched: locations };\n    }\n};\n\n// Service status cache\nlet servicesCache = null;\nlet servicesCacheTime = 0;\nconst CACHE_TTL = 3000;\n\nfunction getServicesStatus() {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    if (servicesCache && (now - servicesCacheTime) < CACHE_TTL) {\n        return servicesCache;\n    }\n\n    const ts = tailscale.status();\n    const ss = ssh.status();\n    const oc = openclaw.status();\n    const gu = guardian.status();\n\n    servicesCache = {\n        tailscale: { online: ts.online, ip: ts.ip, devices: ts.devices },\n        ssh: { online: ss.online },\n        openclaw: {\n            online: oc.online,\n            port: oc.port,\n            memory: oc.memory,\n            version: oc.version,\n            whatsapp: oc.whatsapp,\n            watchdog: oc.watchdog\n        },\n        guardian: { online: gu.online }\n    };\n    servicesCacheTime = now;\n    return servicesCache;\n}\n\n// HTTP server\nconst ALLOWED_ORIGINS = [\n    'http://localhost:8765',\n    'http://127.0.0.1:8765',\n    'http://100.121.254.21:8765', // Tailscale IP\n    'http://mac-mini-1.tail1f0a94.ts.net:8765' // Tailscale hostname\n];\n\nconst server = http.createServer((req, res) => {\n    // Security: Only allow specific origins\n    const origin = req.headers.origin || req.headers.referer || '*';\n    const allowedOrigin = ALLOWED_ORIGINS.includes(origin) ? origin : ALLOWED_ORIGINS[0];\n\n    res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Origin', allowedOrigin);\n    res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Methods', 'GET, POST, OPTIONS');\n    res.setHeader('Access-Control-Allow-Headers', 'Content-Type');\n    res.setHeader('X-Content-Type-Options', 'nosniff')\n\n    if (req.method === 'OPTIONS') {\n        res.writeHead(200);\n        res.end();\n        return;\n    }\n\n    const url = new URL(req.url, `http://localhost:${PORT}`);\n    const pathname = url.pathname;\n\n    // Services status\n\n[332 more lines in file. Use offset=500 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773245976730}}
{"type":"message","id":"3cf20183","parentId":"ef66b278","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:19:36.744Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_574b0a65edbb455493bc5889","toolName":"write","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully wrote 4802 bytes to /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/README_OPENCLAW.md"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773245976734}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5c58f09","parentId":"3cf20183","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:20:04.073Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me add the optimization endpoint to the XMAD server:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b14865ac5cd7469398104c3d","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/server.js","limit":50,"offset":600}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_59cf22c392994d29993856b6","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n/**\n * XMAD Control Center - Optimization Endpoint Addition\n * Add this to server.js after the existing handlers\n */\n\n// Add this to the server.js routes section:\n\n// Optimization handler\nconst optimizeHandler = {\n    run: () => {\n        return new Promise((resolve) => {\n            const script = path.join(XMAD_DIR, 'OPTIMIZE_PC.sh');\n            exec(`bash \"${script}\"`, { timeout: 60000 }, (err, stdout, stderr) => {\n                if (err) {\n                    resolve({ ok: false, error: err.message });\n                } else {\n                    resolve({ ok: true, output: stdout || stderr });\n                }\n            });\n        });\n    }\n};\n\n// Add this route to the HTTP server (after existing routes):\nif (pathname === '/api/optimize/run') {\n    if (req.method === 'POST') {\n        optimizeHandler.run().then(result => {\n            res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n            res.end(JSON.stringify(result));\n        });\n        return;\n    }\n}\n\n// Add this HTML to index.html (in the services section):\n/*\n<div class=\"card\">\n    <h3>рҹ’» PC Optimization</h3>\n    <p>Free up RAM and optimize system</p>\n    <button onclick=\"optimizePC()\" class=\"btn btn-warning\">Optimize Now</button>\n    <div id=\"optimize-result\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\nasync function optimizePC() {\n    const resultDiv = document.getElementById('optimize-result');\n    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<p class=\"text-warning\">вҸі Optimizing...</p>';\n    \n    try {\n        const res = await fetch('/api/optimize/run', { method: 'POST' });\n        const data = await res.json();\n        \n        if (data.ok) {\n            resultDiv.innerHTML = '<p class=\"text-success\">вң… ' + data.output + '</p>';\n        } else {\n            resultDiv.innerHTML = '<p class=\"text-danger\">вқҢ ' + data.error + '</p>';\n        }\n    } catch (error) {\n        resultDiv.innerHTML = '<p class=\"text-danger\">вқҢ ' + error.message + '</p>';\n    }\n}\n</script>\n*/\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/ADD_OPTIMIZE_ENDPOINT.js"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_524592ded9374cad9e735f9c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center && ls -la *.md *.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":61046,"output":579,"cacheRead":33792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95417,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773245976741}}
{"type":"message","id":"8bef7d47","parentId":"e5c58f09","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:20:04.078Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b14865ac5cd7469398104c3d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        } catch (e) {\n            res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n            res.end(JSON.stringify({ ok: true, lines: ['Log file not found'] }));\n        }\n        return;\n    }\n\n    // в”Җв”Җ File read (GET) в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n    if (pathname === '/api/file/read') {\n        const filePath = url.searchParams.get('path');\n        if (!filePath) {\n            res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n            res.end(JSON.stringify({ ok: false, error: 'path required' }));\n            return;\n        }\n        const result = fileHandler.read(filePath);\n        res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n        res.end(JSON.stringify(result));\n        return;\n    }\n\n    // в”Җв”Җ File write (POST) в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n    if (pathname === '/api/file/write' && req.method === 'POST') {\n        let body = '';\n        req.on('data', chunk => body += chunk);\n        req.on('end', () => {\n            try {\n                const { path: filePath, content } = JSON.parse(body);\n                const result = fileHandler.write(filePath, content);\n                res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n                res.end(JSON.stringify(result));\n            } catch (e) {\n                res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n                res.end(JSON.stringify({ ok: false, error: e.message }));\n            }\n        });\n        return;\n    }\n\n    // в”Җв”Җ Backups list в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n    if (pathname === '/api/backups/list') {\n        const result = backupHandler.list();\n        res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' });\n        res.end(JSON.stringify(result));\n        return;\n    }\n\n    // в”Җв”Җ Backup create (POST) в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n    if (pathname === '/api/backups/create' && req.method === 'POST') {\n        let body = '';\n\n[182 more lines in file. Use offset=650 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773246004076}}
