{"type":"message","id":"a31318c5","parentId":"0e27ece0","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:31:06.884Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8ea148907e09486fbedfc8ca","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    <div class=\"ai-chat-panel\" id=\"aiChatPanel\">\n        <div class=\"ai-chat-header\">\n            <h4>\n                <span class=\"status-indicator-ring online\" style=\"width:8px; height:8px; border-width:2px;\"></span>\n                OpenClaw AI\n            </h4>\n            <button class=\"glass-btn sm ghost\" onclick=\"toggleAIChat()\">Г—</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ai-chat-messages\" id=\"aiChatMessages\">\n            <div class=\"ai-message assistant\">\n                <div class=\"msg-text\">Hello! How can I help you?</div>\n                <div class=\"msg-time\">Just now</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ai-chat-input\">\n            <input type=\"text\" class=\"glass-input\" id=\"aiChatInput\" placeholder=\"Type message...\" onkeypress=\"if(event.key==='Enter')sendAIMessage()\">\n            <button class=\"glass-btn sm primary\" onclick=\"sendAIMessage()\">Send</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\n         FLOATING WIDGETS\n         в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ -->\n    <!-- Clock Widget -->\n    <div class=\"floating-widget clock-widget\" id=\"clockWidget\">\n        <div class=\"clock-time\" id=\"clockTime\">--:--</div>\n        <div class=\"clock-date\" id=\"clockDate\">Loading...</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Quick Add Modal -->\n    <div class=\"quick-add-modal\" id=\"quickAddModal\">\n        <h4>вһ• Quick Add</h4>\n        <div class=\"quick-add-tabs\">\n            <button class=\"quick-add-tab active\" onclick=\"switchQuickAddTab('task')\">Task</button>\n            <button class=\"quick-add-tab\" onclick=\"switchQuickAddTab('note')\">Note</button>\n        </div>\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"glass-input\" id=\"quickAddInput\" placeholder=\"Enter text...\" onkeypress=\"if(event.key==='Enter')submitQuickAdd()\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:0.4rem; margin-top:0.5rem;\">\n            <button class=\"glass-btn primary\" onclick=\"submitQuickAdd()\">Add</button>\n            <button class=\"glass-btn ghost\" onclick=\"toggleQuickAdd()\">Cancel</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\n         SYSTEM STATUS MODAL\n         в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ -->\n    <div class=\"status-modal-overlay\" id=\"statusModalOverlay\" onclick=\"if(event.target===this)toggleStatusModal()\">\n        <div class=\"status-modal\">\n            <div class=\"status-modal-header\">\n                <h3>System Status</h3>\n\n[68 more lines in file. Use offset=970 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773246666712}}
