{"type":"message","id":"524115be","parentId":"7353dd58","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:32:02.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me create a simple update guide:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8dc7e6b126bf42c29a391207","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# рҹ“қ XMAD Dashboard Update Guide\n\n**Goal**: Enable STT/TTS and connect chat to OpenClaw properly\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”§ WHAT NEEDS TO BE UPDATED\n\n### 1. Chat Connection (app.js)\n\n**Current**: Chat sends to `/api/openclaw/message` (via XMAD server)  \n**Needed**: Chat should send directly to `http://localhost:18789/api/message` (OpenClaw gateway)\n\n**File**: `app.js` line 518-543\n\n**Replace** the existing `sendAIMessage()` function with the enhanced version from `ENHANCED_AI_CHAT.js`\n\n---\n\n### 2. Voice Input Button (index.html)\n\n**Add** voice record button to chat input:\n\n**Location**: In the AI chat panel (around line 926)\n\n**Current**:\n```html\n<div class=\"ai-chat-input\">\n    <input type=\"text\" class=\"glass-input\" id=\"aiChatInput\" placeholder=\"Type message...\" onkeypress=\"if(event.key==='Enter')sendAIMessage()\">\n    <button class=\"glass-btn sm primary\" onclick=\"sendAIMessage()\">Send</button>\n</div>\n```\n\n**Replace with**:\n```html\n<div class=\"ai-chat-input\" style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.5rem;\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex; gap:0.4rem; align-items:center;\">\n        <button id=\"voiceRecordBtn\" class=\"glass-btn sm ghost\" onclick=\"toggleVoiceRecording()\" title=\"Voice input (STT)\">\n            рҹҺӨ\n        </button>\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"glass-input\" id=\"aiChatInput\" placeholder=\"Type or click mic to speak...\" onkeypress=\"if(event.key==='Enter')sendAIMessage()\" style=\"flex:1;\">\n        <button class=\"glass-btn sm primary\" onclick=\"sendAIMessage()\">Send</button>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex; gap:0.4rem; font-size:0.7rem;\">\n        <button id=\"modeWhatsApp\" class=\"chip-btn active\" onclick=\"setChatMode('whatsapp')\">рҹ“ұ WhatsApp</button>\n        <button id=\"modeDirect\" class=\"chip-btn\" onclick=\"setChatMode('direct')\">рҹ’¬ Direct</button>\n        <span style=\"margin-left:auto; color:var(--text-muted);\" id=\"chatModeDisplay\">рҹ“ұ WhatsApp</span>\n    </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Add CSS (styles.css)\n\n**Add** these styles to `styles.css`:\n\n```css\n/* Voice button */\n#voiceRecordBtn {\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n}\n\n#voiceRecordBtn:active {\n    transform: scale(0.95);\n}\n\n#voiceRecordBtn.recording {\n    background: var(--red-500) !important;\n    animation: pulse 1s infinite;\n}\n\n@keyframes pulse {\n    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n    50% { opacity: 0.7; }\n}\n\n/* Chat mode buttons */\n.chip-btn {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n    padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;\n    border-radius: 15px;\n    font-size: 0.7rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.2s;\n}\n\n.chip-btn:hover {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\n}\n\n.chip-btn.active {\n    background: var(--primary-500);\n    color: white;\n    border-color: var(--primary-500);\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Add JavaScript (app.js)\n\n**Add** the enhanced functions to `app.js`:\n\n**Location**: After the existing `sendAIMessage()` function (around line 543)\n\n**Copy** from `ENHANCED_AI_CHAT.js`:\n- `toggleVoiceRecording()`\n- `startRecording()`\n- `stopRecording()`\n- `speakText()` (TTS function)\n- `setChatMode()`\n- `addMessage()` helper\n- `escapeHtml()` helper\n\n**Replace** the existing `sendAIMessage()` with the enhanced version.\n\n---\n\n## вң… WHAT THIS ENABLES\n\n### STT (Speech-to-Text)\n- Click рҹҺӨ button to start recording\n- Speak your message\n- Auto-sends when you stop speaking\n- Uses browser's Web Speech API\n\n### TTS (Text-to-Speech)\n- Responses are automatically spoken\n- Uses browser's Speech Synthesis API\n- English language\n- Natural voice\n\n### Chat Modes\n- **WhatsApp**: Sends to +971504042000 (Nova's WhatsApp)\n- **Direct**: Sends via API (no WhatsApp, faster)\n\n### Better UX\n- Typing indicator while waiting\n- Auto-scroll to latest message\n- Message timestamps\n- Error handling\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҜ QUICK UPDATE METHOD\n\n### Option 1: Manual Update (5 min)\n1. Open `app.js`\n2. Replace `sendAIMessage()` function\n3. Add voice functions from `ENHANCED_AI_CHAT.js`\n4. Open `index.html`\n5. Update AI chat input HTML\n6. Open `styles.css`\n7. Add CSS for chip-btn and voice button\n\n### Option 2: Copy-Paste (2 min)\n1. Copy `sendAIMessage()` from `ENHANCED_AI_CHAT.js`\n2. Paste into `app.js` (replace old one)\n3. Copy all voice functions from `ENHANCED_AI_CHAT.js`\n4. Paste into `app.js` (after `sendAIMessage()`)\n5. Update HTML in `index.html` (see above)\n6. Add CSS to `styles.css` (see above)\n\n---\n\n## рҹ§Ә TESTING\n\n### Test STT (Voice Input)\n1. Open dashboard: http://localhost:8765\n2. Click \"Open AI Chat\" button\n3. Click рҹҺӨ button\n4. Speak: \"Hello Nova\"\n5. Should auto-send and get response\n\n### Test TTS (Voice Output)\n1. Send any message\n2. Should hear the response spoken\n3. Check browser console for errors\n\n### Test Chat Modes\n1. Click \"рҹ“ұ WhatsApp\" - sends to WhatsApp\n2. Click \"рҹ’¬ Direct\" - sends via API\n3. Both should work\n\n---\n\n## рҹҗӣ TROUBLESHOOTING\n\n### STT Not Working\n**Check**: Browser supports Web Speech API\n```javascript\nconsole.log('SpeechRecognition:', 'webkitSpeechRecognition' in window || 'SpeechRecognition' in window);\n```\n\n**Fix**: Use Chrome or Edge browser\n\n### TTS Not Working\n**Check**: Browser supports Speech Synthesis\n```javascript\nconsole.log('SpeechSynthesis:', 'speechSynthesis' in window);\n```\n\n**Fix**: Enable in browser settings\n\n### Chat Not Connecting\n**Check**: OpenClaw gateway is running\n```bash\ncurl http://localhost:18789/health\n```\n\n**Fix**: Start OpenClaw\n```bash\n~/.openclaw/scripts/start-optimized.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ҡ FEATURE CHECKLIST\n\n- [ ] Chat connects to OpenClaw (port 18789)\n- [ ] WhatsApp mode works\n- [ ] Direct mode works\n- [ ] Voice input (STT) works\n- [ ] Voice output (TTS) works\n- [ ] Chat mode buttons visible\n- [ ] Error handling works\n- [ ] Typing indicator shows\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺү AFTER UPDATE\n\nYour XMAD dashboard will have:\n- вң… Full chat integration with OpenClaw\n- вң… Voice input (click рҹҺӨ to speak)\n- вң… Voice output (hear responses)\n- вң… WhatsApp/Direct mode toggle\n- вң… Better UX with typing indicator\n\n---\n\n**Files to Update**:\n1. `app.js` - Add voice functions\n2. `index.html` - Update chat input HTML\n3. `styles.css` - Add button styles\n\n**Reference File**: `ENHANCED_AI_CHAT.js` (has all the code)\n\n**Estimated Time**: 5-10 minutes\n\n---\n\n**Need help?** Check `ENHANCED_AI_CHAT.js` for complete working code!\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/DASHBOARD_UPDATE_GUIDE.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":47709,"output":1815,"cacheRead":50176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99700,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773246703687}}
