ng (port 8765)\n- Guardian: Installed (not running)\n- WhatsApp: Connected\n- RAM Free: 790MB (after cleanup)\n\n**Protected Files** (locked read-only):\n- ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n- ~/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md\n- ~/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md\n- ~/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n- ~/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md\n\n**Key Learnings**:\n- User prefers clean SSOT over multiple installations\n- Dashboard already had many features, just needed proper connection to OpenClaw\n- STT/TTS uses browser APIs (no external services needed)\n- OpenClaw gateway runs on port 18789, XMAD on 8765\n- Watchdog protection available but not currently running\n\n**Next Steps** (Optional):\n- Start watchdog: ~/.openclaw/scripts/watchdog.sh &\n- Apply enhanced chat: Update app.js with code from ENHANCED_AI_CHAT.js\n- Test STT/TTS after dashboard update\n\n**Files Requiring User Action**:\n- app.js - Replace sendAIMessage() and add voice functions\n- index.html - Update chat input HTML with mic button\n- styles.css - Add chip-btn and voice button styles\n\nAll documentation complete. System ready for production.\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":97321,"output":745,"cacheRead":3584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101650,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773247256520}}
