{"type":"message","id":"73820de0","parentId":"ddc9c261","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:42:00.344Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_daab660b235c435388510750","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Voice Provider Selection Analysis\n\n## Executive Summary\n\nThis document analyzes all voice-related providers and selects the best option from each company for the consolidated Voice Hub architecture.\n\n---\n\n## Company 1: Deepgram\n\n### Provider: Deepgram STT (Speech-to-Text)\n- **Type**: Cloud API\n- **Status**: вң… Configured (XMAD Ecosystem .env)\n- **Port**: N/A (API-based)\n\n### Selection Criteria\n\n| Criteria | Rating | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| Quality | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Industry-leading accuracy, especially for real-time |\n| Speed/Latency | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Sub-300ms latency for streaming |\n| Cost | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | $0.004/minute for Nova-2 (competitive) |\n| Language Support | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | 30+ languages |\n| Ease of Integration | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Excellent SDKs and documentation |\n\n### Verdict: вң… SELECTED\n**Reason**: Deepgram is the industry standard for real-time STT with excellent accuracy and low latency. Perfect for production use cases.\n\n---\n\n## Company 2: Eleven Labs\n\n### Provider: ElevenLabs TTS (Text-to-Speech)\n- **Type**: Cloud API\n- **Status**: вң… Configured (XMAD Ecosystem .env)\n- **Port**: N/A (API-based)\n\n### Selection Criteria\n\n| Criteria | Rating | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| Quality | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Best-in-class voice quality |\n| Speed/Latency | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | ~1-2 seconds generation time |\n| Cost | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | $5/month starter, $0.30/1000 chars |\n| Language Support | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | 29 languages |\n| Ease of Integration | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Simple REST API |\n\n### Verdict: вң… SELECTED\n**Reason**: ElevenLabs offers the best voice quality among API providers. Ideal for high-quality voice output when local inference is not available.\n\n---\n\n## Company 3: Qwen (Alibaba)\n\n### Provider: Qwen3-TTS\n- **Type**: Local/Cloud Hybrid\n- **Status**: вң… Available (Local microservice)\n- **Port**: 8001\n- **Model**: Qwen/Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B-CustomVoice\n\n### Selection Criteria\n\n| Criteria | Rating | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| Quality | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Very good multilingual quality |\n| Speed/Latency | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Moderate (requires GPU for best performance) |\n| Cost | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | FREE (local inference) |\n| Language Support | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | 10 languages (zh, en, ja, ko, de, fr, ru, pt, es, it) |\n| Ease of Integration | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Requires Python setup |\n\n### Verdict: вң… SELECTED\n**Reason**: Best multilingual option with voice cloning capabilities. Free local inference makes it ideal for multilingual applications.\n\n---\n\n## Company 4: Gemini (Google)\n\n### Provider: Gemini (LLM for Voice Orchestration)\n- **Type**: Cloud API\n- **Status**: вң… Configured (XMAD Ecosystem .env)\n- **Port**: N/A (API-based)\n\n### Selection Criteria\n\n| Criteria | Rating | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| Quality | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Excellent for voice conversation orchestration |\n| Speed/Latency | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Moderate (depends on model size) |\n| Cost | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Competitive pricing |\n| Language Support | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | 100+ languages |\n| Ease of Integration | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Well-documented API |\n\n### Verdict: вң… SELECTED\n**Reason**: Best for voice conversation orchestration and context-aware responses. Works as the brain behind voice interactions.\n\n---\n\n## Additional Providers (Non-Company Specific)\n\n### Groq Whisper STT\n- **Type**: Cloud API\n- **Status**: вң… Configured (OpenClaw config)\n- **Port**: N/A (API-based)\n\n| Criteria | Rating | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| Quality | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Whisper-large-v3 accuracy |\n| Speed/Latency | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Extremely fast (Groq's LPU) |\n| Cost | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | FREE during beta |\n| Language Support | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | 99 languages |\n| Ease of Integration | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Simple API |\n\n**Verdict**: вң… SELECTED - Best free option for English STT with excellent speed.\n\n### Chatterbox Turbo TTS\n- **Type**: Local\n- **Status**: вң… Available (Local microservice)\n- **Port**: 8000\n- **Model**: resemble-ai/chatterbox\n\n| Criteria | Rating | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| Quality | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Beats ElevenLabs in blind tests |\n| Speed/Latency | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Fast (Turbo version) |\n| Cost | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | FREE (local inference) |\n| Language Support | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | English primary, some multilingual |\n| Ease of Integration | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Requires Python setup |\n\n**Verdict**: вң… SELECTED - Best quality TTS available, with voice cloning and paralinguistic tags.\n\n### Kokoro-82M TTS\n- **Type**: Local\n- **Status**: вң… Available (Local microservice)\n- **Port**: 8002\n- **Model**: hexgrad/Kokoro-82M\n\n| Criteria | Rating | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| Quality | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Good quality for 82M params |\n| Speed/Latency | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Ultra-fast (96x real-time) |\n| Cost | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | FREE (local inference) |\n| Language Support | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | English primary |\n| Ease of Integration | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Lightweight, easy setup |\n\n**Verdict**: вң… SELECTED - Fastest TTS option, ideal for real-time applications.\n\n### SenseVoice STT\n- **Type**: Local\n- **Status**: вң… Available (Local microservice)\n- **Port**: 50000\n- **Model**: FunAudioLLM/SenseVoice-Small\n\n| Criteria | Rating | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| Quality | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Excellent multilingual accuracy |\n| Speed/Latency | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Fast (Small model) |\n| Cost | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | FREE (local inference) |\n| Language Support | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | 50+ languages with emotion detection |\n| Ease of Integration | вӯҗвӯҗвӯҗ | Requires Python setup |\n\n**Verdict**: вң… SELECTED - Best multilingual STT with emotion detection capabilities.\n\n---\n\n## Final Selected Providers (7 Total)\n\n### STT Providers (3)\n| Provider | Type | Best For |\n|----------|------|----------|\n| **Deepgram** | API | Production real-time STT |\n| **Groq Whisper** | API | Free fast STT (English) |\n| **SenseVoice** | Local | Multilingual STT with emotions |\n\n### TTS Providers (4)\n| Provider | Type | Best For |\n|----------|------|----------|\n| **ElevenLabs** | API | Best quality API TTS |\n| **Chatterbox** | Local | Best quality overall + voice cloning |\n| **Qwen3-TTS** | Local | Multilingual TTS + voice cloning |\n| **Kokoro** | Local | Ultra-fast real-time TTS |\n\n### Orchestration (1)\n| Provider | Type | Best For |\n|----------|------|----------|\n| **Gemini** | API | Voice conversation orchestration |\n\n---\n\n## Use Case Recommendations\n\n| Use Case | STT | TTS | LLM |\n|----------|-----|-----|-----|\n| **WhatsApp English** | Groq Whisper (FREE) | Chatterbox (best quality) | Gemini |\n| **WhatsApp Multi** | SenseVoice (50+ langs) | Qwen3-TTS (10 langs) | Gemini |\n| **Real-time Agent** | Deepgram (low latency) | Kokoro (96x real-time) | Gemini |\n| **Best Quality** | Groq Whisper | Chatterbox | Gemini |\n| **Cost-Effective** | Groq Whisper (FREE) | Qwen3-TTS (FREE) | Gemini |\n| **Privacy-First** | SenseVoice (local) | Chatterbox (local) | Local LLM |\n\n---\n\n## Next Steps\n\n1. вң… All providers selected\n2. вҸӯпёҸ Create consolidated architecture in `xmad-ai-voice/`\n3. вҸӯпёҸ Fix any broken implementations\n4. вҸӯпёҸ Create unified testing interface\n5. вҸӯпёҸ Document setup and troubleshooting\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773247320341}}
