{"type":"message","id":"1389a934","parentId":"730bd7b2","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:42:01.184Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c7d478da577e4b32a239a33f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 192\ndrwxr-xr-x   8 ahmadabdullah  staff    256 Mar  8 23:21 .\ndrwx------@ 23 ahmadabdullah  staff    736 Mar 11 20:41 ..\n-rw-r--r--@  1 ahmadabdullah  staff   6148 Mar 10 01:39 .DS_Store\n-rw-r--r--@  1 ahmadabdullah  staff  14675 Feb 26 23:21 GUARDIAN_ORCHESTRATOR_GUIDE.md\n-rw-r--r--   1 ahmadabdullah  staff   2697 Feb 26 17:01 README.md\n-rw-r--r--   1 ahmadabdullah  staff  21082 Mar  7 23:21 SSOT_API_KEYS_GUIDE.md\n-rw-r--r--   1 ahmadabdullah  staff   8293 Mar  6 02:13 VPN_SSH_REMOTE_ACCESS_SETUP.md\n-rw-------@  1 ahmadabdullah  staff  29233 Mar  8 23:21 openclaw-plan.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":212,"aggregated":"total 192\ndrwxr-xr-x   8 ahmadabdullah  staff    256 Mar  8 23:21 .\ndrwx------@ 23 ahmadabdullah  staff    736 Mar 11 20:41 ..\n-rw-r--r--@  1 ahmadabdullah  staff   6148 Mar 10 01:39 .DS_Store\n-rw-r--r--@  1 ahmadabdullah  staff  14675 Feb 26 23:21 GUARDIAN_ORCHESTRATOR_GUIDE.md\n-rw-r--r--   1 ahmadabdullah  staff   2697 Feb 26 17:01 README.md\n-rw-r--r--   1 ahmadabdullah  staff  21082 Mar  7 23:21 SSOT_API_KEYS_GUIDE.md\n-rw-r--r--   1 ahmadabdullah  staff   8293 Mar  6 02:13 VPN_SSH_REMOTE_ACCESS_SETUP.md\n-rw-------@  1 ahmadabdullah  staff  29233 Mar  8 23:21 openclaw-plan.md","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773247321172}}
{"type":"message","id":"94f03520","parentId":"1389a934","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:42:26.396Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me read the API keys guide and set up the voice integration:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fd8d99c190dc49ec84296731","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/important-docs/SSOT_API_KEYS_GUIDE.md","limit":100}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d9474d953dc14cc7bcf1a2b0","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Voice Integration Setup for XMAD Dashboard\n# Uses local microservices - NO additional memory for OpenClaw/WhatsApp\n\nset -e\n\nHOME_DIR=\"/Users/ahmadabdullah\"\nVOICE_DIR=\"$HOME_DIR/Desktop/ignore/voice-microservices\"\nXMAD_DIR=\"$HOME_DIR/Desktop/xmad-control-center\"\n\necho \"рҹҺӨ Setting up Voice Integration for XMAD Dashboard\"\necho \"в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\"\n\n# Create voice integration directory\nmkdir -p \"$XMAD_DIR/voice\"\n\n# Copy the best providers (based on PROVIDER_SELECTION.md)\necho \"рҹ“Ӣ Copying selected voice providers...\"\n\n# STT: SenseVoice (best multilingual + emotion detection)\nif [ -d \"$VOICE_DIR/stt-sensevoice\" ]; then\n    echo \"вң… SenseVoice STT - already available at port 50000\"\n    echo \"   Start: cd $VOICE_DIR/stt-sensevoice && ./start-all.sh\"\nelse\n    echo \"вқҢ SenseVoice not found\"\nfi\n\n# TTS: Chatterbox (best quality overall + voice cloning)\nif [ -d \"$VOICE_DIR/tts-chatterbox\" ]; then\n    echo \"вң… Chatterbox TTS - already available at port 8000\"\n    echo \"   Start: cd $VOICE_DIR/tts-chatterbox && ./start-all.sh\"\nelse\n    echo \"вқҢ Chatterbox not found\"\nfi\n\n# TTS: Kokoro (ultra-fast for real-time)\nif [ -d \"$VOICE_DIR/tts-kokoro\" ]; then\n    echo \"вң… Kokoro TTS - already available at port 8002\"\n    echo \"   Start: cd $VOICE_DIR/tts-kokoro && ./start-all.sh\"\nelse\n    echo \"вқҢ Kokoro not found\"\nfi\n\n# Create voice integration script\ncat > \"$XMAD_DIR/voice/voice-client.js\" << 'EOFJS'\n// Voice Client for XMAD Dashboard\n// Uses local microservices - NO impact on OpenClaw memory\n\nconst VOICE_SERVICES = {\n    stt: {\n        sensevoice: 'http://localhost:50000',\n        // Add more STT providers here if needed\n    },\n    tts: {\n        chatterbox: 'http://localhost:8000',\n        kokoro: 'http://localhost:8002',\n        qwen3: 'http://localhost:8001'\n    }\n};\n\n// STT: Speech to Text (SenseVoice)\nasync function speechToText(audioBlob, provider = 'sensevoice') {\n    const url = VOICE_SERVICES.stt[provider];\n    if (!url) throw new Error(`STT provider ${provider} not found`);\n\n    const formData = new FormData();\n    formData.append('audio', audioBlob);\n\n    const response = await fetch(`${url}/stt`, {\n        method: 'POST',\n        body: formData\n    });\n\n    if (!response.ok) throw new Error('STT request failed');\n    const data = await response.json();\n    return data.text || data.transcript;\n}\n\n// TTS: Text to Speech (Chatterbox - best quality)\nasync function textToSpeech(text, provider = 'chatterbox') {\n    const url = VOICE_SERVICES.tts[provider];\n    if (!url) throw new Error(`TTS provider ${provider} not found`);\n\n    const response = await fetch(`${url}/tts`, {\n        method: 'POST',\n        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n        body: JSON.stringify({ text })\n    });\n\n    if (!response.ok) throw new Error('TTS request failed');\n    const audioBlob = await response.blob();\n    return audioBlob;\n}\n\n// Play audio\nfunction playAudio(audioBlob) {\n    const audio = new Audio(URL.createObjectURL(audioBlob));\n    audio.play();\n    return audio;\n}\n\n// Export for use in dashboard\nif (typeof module !== 'undefined' && module.exports) {\n    module.exports = { speechToText, textToSpeech, playAudio };\n}\nEOFJS\n\n# Create startup script\ncat > \"$XMAD_DIR/voice/start-voice-services.sh\" << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\n# Start all voice microservices\n\nHOME_DIR=\"/Users/ahmadabdullah\"\nVOICE_DIR=\"$HOME_DIR/Desktop/ignore/voice-microservices\"\n\necho \"рҹҺӨ Starting Voice Microservices...\"\n\n# Start SenseVoice STT (port 50000)\nif [ -d \"$VOICE_DIR/stt-sensevoice\" ]; then\n    cd \"$VOICE_DIR/stt-sensevoice\"\n    if ! pgrep -f \"python.*webui.py\" > /dev/null; then\n        echo \"в–¶пёҸ  Starting SenseVoice STT...\"\n        ./start-all.sh &\n        sleep 5\n        echo \"вң… SenseVoice STT ready at http://localhost:50000\"\n    else\n        echo \"вң… SenseVoice STT already running\"\n    fi\nfi\n\n# Start Chatterbox TTS (port 8000) - BEST QUALITY\nif [ -d \"$VOICE_DIR/tts-chatterbox\" ]; then\n    cd \"$VOICE_DIR/tts-chatterbox\"\n    if ! pgrep -f \"python.*webui.py\" > /dev/null; then\n        echo \"в–¶пёҸ  Starting Chatterbox TTS...\"\n        ./start-all.sh &\n        sleep 5\n        echo \"вң… Chatterbox TTS ready at http://localhost:8000\"\n    else\n        echo \"вң… Chatterbox TTS already running\"\n    fi\nfi\n\n# Start Kokoro TTS (port 8002) - ULTRA FAST\nif [ -d \"$VOICE_DIR/tts-kokoro\" ]; then\n    cd \"$VOICE_DIR/tts-kokoro\"\n    if ! pgrep -f \"python.*webui.py\" > /dev/null; then\n        echo \"в–¶пёҸ  Starting Kokoro TTS...\"\n        ./start-all.sh &\n        sleep 5\n        echo \"вң… Kokoro TTS ready at http://localhost:8002\"\n    else\n        echo \"вң… Kokoro TTS already running\"\n    fi\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"рҹҺӨ All voice services ready!\"\necho \"STT: http://localhost:50000 (SenseVoice)\"\necho \"TTS: http://localhost:8000 (Chatterbox - best quality)\"\necho \"TTS: http://localhost:8002 (Kokoro - ultra fast)\"\nEOF\n\nchmod +x \"$XMAD_DIR/voice/start-voice-services.sh\"\n\n# Create README\ncat > \"$XMAD_DIR/voice/README.md\" << 'EOF'\n# Voice Integration for XMAD Dashboard\n\n## Overview\n\nLocal voice microservices for XMAD Dashboard - **NO impact on OpenClaw/WhatsApp memory**\n\n## Services\n\n### STT (Speech-to-Text)\n- **Provider**: SenseVoice\n- **Port**: 50000\n- **Features**: 50+ languages, emotion detection\n- **Usage**: Click рҹҺӨ in XMAD dashboard\n\n### TTS (Text-to-Speech)\n- **Primary**: Chatterbox (port 8000) - Best quality\n- **Secondary**: Kokoro (port 8002) - Ultra fast (96x real-time)\n- **Features**: Voice cloning, paralinguistic tags\n\n## Startup\n\nStart all voice services:\n```bash\n~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/voice/start-voice-services.sh\n```\n\nOr start individually:\n```bash\ncd ~/Desktop/ignore/voice-microservices/stt-sensevoice && ./start-all.sh\ncd ~/Desktop/ignore/voice-microservices/tts-chatterbox && ./start-all.sh\ncd ~/Desktop/ignore/voice-microservices/tts-kokoro && ./start-all.sh\n```\n\n## API Usage\n\n### STT: Audio to Text\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:50000/stt \\\n  -F \"audio=@input.wav\"\n```\n\n### TTS: Text to Audio\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:8000/tts \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"text\":\"Hello world\"}' \\\n  --output output.wav\n```\n\n## Integration with XMAD\n\nThe voice services run independently from OpenClaw:\n- **Separate processes** - No memory impact\n- **Local only** - No cloud API costs\n- **High quality** - Chatterbox beats ElevenLabs\n- **Fast** - Kokoro is 96x real-time\n\n## Notes\n\n- Voice services use Python + AI models\n- Requires more RAM (~2GB when all running)\n- Can be stopped when not needed\n- OpenClaw continues working independently\nEOF\n\necho \"\"\necho \"вң… Voice integration setup complete!\"\necho \"\"\necho \"рҹ“Ғ Files created:\"\necho \"   $XMAD_DIR/voice/voice-client.js\"\necho \"   $XMAD_DIR/voice/start-voice-services.sh\"\necho \"   $XMAD_DIR/voice/README.md\"\necho \"\"\necho \"рҹҡҖ To start voice services:\"\necho \"   $XMAD_DIR/voice/start-voice-services.sh\"\necho \"\"\necho \"вҡ пёҸ  Note: Voice services run independently from OpenClaw\"\necho \"   They will NOT impact OpenClaw/WhatsApp memory usage\"\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/setup-voice-integration.sh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d11fbcf7fefe4a89b36e727f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/setup-voice-integration.sh && /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/setup-voice-integration.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":98761,"output":2113,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102026,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773247321182}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c92739a","parentId":"94f03520","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:42:26.433Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fd8d99c190dc49ec84296731","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SSOT API Keys - Complete Guide\n\n> **Single Source of Truth for All API Keys**\n> Generated: 2026-02-27\n> Version: 2.0\n\n---\n\n## Table of Contents\n\n1. [Architecture Overview](#architecture-overview)\n2. [API Provider Formats](#api-provider-formats)\n3. [Key Locations](#key-locations)\n4. [VPN + SSH Remote Access](#vpn--ssh-remote-access)\n5. [All Keys Inventory](#all-keys-inventory)\n6. [How to Use Keys](#how-to-use-keys)\n7. [How to Use in Scripts](#how-to-use-in-scripts)\n8. [How to Add Keys to Projects](#how-to-add-keys-to-projects)\n9. [How to Add New Keys](#how-to-add-new-keys)\n10. [Best Practices](#best-practices)\n11. [Troubleshooting](#troubleshooting)\n12. [Quick Reference](#quick-reference)\n\n---\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                  macOS KEYCHAIN                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ              (Root of Trust - Master Backup)            в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  All secrets stored with SSOT_* prefix                 в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Hardware-backed by Apple Secure Enclave               в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                          в”Ӯ\n                          в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                   INFISICAL                             в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ           (Runtime Secrets Provider)                    в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Project ID: 3f265951-5e47-4460-88c1-ad9bee65b1ac      в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Environment: dev, staging, prod                        в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  13+ secrets available for injection                    в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                          в”Ӯ\n                          в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                   PROJECTS                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ            (Zero Secrets Zone)                          в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  No .env files allowed                                  в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  No hardcoded secrets                                   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  All secrets via Infisical injection                    в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Provider Formats\n\n**CRITICAL: Each provider uses different API formats. Using the wrong format will fail.**\n\n### z.ai (GLM Models)\n\n```bash\n# z.ai uses Anthropic-compatible API (NOT OpenAI format!)\n# Endpoint: https://api.z.ai/api/anthropic/v1/messages\n# Header: x-api-key (NOT Authorization: Bearer)\n# Models: GLM-5, GLM-4.7, GLM-4-Plus\n\n# Correct API call:\ncurl -X POST \"https://api.z.ai/api/anthropic/v1/messages\" \\\n  -H \"x-api-key: YOUR_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"anthropic-version: 2023-06-01\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"GLM-5\",\n    \"max_tokens\": 100,\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello\"}]\n  }'\n\n# Response format: .content[0].text\n```\n\n### Groq (OpenAI-Compatible)\n\n```bash\n# Groq uses standard OpenAI format\n# Endpoint: https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/chat/completions\n# Header: Authorization: Bearer\n# Models: llama-3.3-70b-versatile, moonshotai/kimi-k2-instruct, llama-3.1-8b-instant\n\ncurl -X POST \"https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/chat/completions\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer YOUR_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"llama-3.3-70b-versatile\",\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello\"}],\n    \"max_tokens\": 100\n\n[632 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773247346429}}
