coordinator.json\n-rwxr-xr-x    1 ahmadabdullah  staff   4498 Feb 26 15:40 deploy_guardian.sh\ndrwxr-xr-x    3 ahmadabdullah  staff     96 Feb 26 16:54 docs\n-rw-r--r--    1 ahmadabdullah  staff    380 Mar  9 08:56 grep\n-rwxr-xr-x    1 ahmadabdullah  staff   8004 Mar  9 10:50 install.sh\ndrwx------   17 ahmadabdullah  staff    544 Mar  9 10:53 logs\n-rwxr-xr-x    1 ahmadabdullah  staff   5760 Mar  9 10:06 openclaw-bridge.sh\ndrwxr-xr-x    9 ahmadabdullah  staff    288 Mar  9 10:52 scripts","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773248051365}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f38d59a","parentId":"80e8c139","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:54:12.017Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_141e097eb32747bd934e9747","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Guardian Orchestrator 2026\n\n> **SSOT-Compliant Multi-Agent AI Coding Orchestrator**\n> Version: 2.2.0 | Updated: 2026-02-27\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nGuardian Orchestrator 2026 is a bash-native, multi-agent AI coding system that orchestrates multiple LLM providers to complete coding tasks with automatic quality review and safety audits.\n\n### Key Features\n\n- **Multi-Agent Architecture**: 5 specialized agents for different task types\n- **SSOT Compliant**: All API keys from macOS Keychain (no hardcoded secrets)\n- **5-Stage Pipeline**: Analyze вҶ’ Plan вҶ’ Audit вҶ’ Execute вҶ’ Review\n- **Automatic Fallback**: Graceful degradation across providers\n- **Quality Scoring**: Every task gets a quality score (1-10)\n\n---\n\n## Quick Start\n\n```bash\n# Navigate to orchestrator\ncd ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026\n\n# Check agent status\n./claude-safe --status\n\n# Run a task\n./claude-safe \"Add error handling to the API client\" ./my-project\n\n# View available models\n./claude-safe --models\n\n# Get help\n./claude-safe --help\n```\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                    GUARDIAN ORCHESTRATOR                    в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                      (claude-safe)                          в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                          в”Ӯ"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":646,"aggregated":"# Guardian Orchestrator 2026\n\n> **SSOT-Compliant Multi-Agent AI Coding Orchestrator**\n> Version: 2.2.0 | Updated: 2026-02-27\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nGuardian Orchestrator 2026 is a bash-native, multi-agent AI coding system that orchestrates multiple LLM providers to complete coding tasks with automatic quality review and safety audits.\n\n### Key Features\n\n- **Multi-Agent Architecture**: 5 specialized agents for different task types\n- **SSOT Compliant**: All API keys from macOS Keychain (no hardcoded secrets)\n- **5-Stage Pipeline**: Analyze вҶ’ Plan вҶ’ Audit вҶ’ Execute вҶ’ Review\n- **Automatic Fallback**: Graceful degradation across providers\n- **Quality Scoring**: Every task gets a quality score (1-10)\n\n---\n\n## Quick Start\n\n```bash\n# Navigate to orchestrator\ncd ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026\n\n# Check agent status\n./claude-safe --status\n\n# Run a task\n./claude-safe \"Add error handling to the API client\" ./my-project\n\n# View available models\n./claude-safe --models\n\n# Get help\n./claude-safe --help\n```\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                    GUARDIAN ORCHESTRATOR                    в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                      (claude-safe)                          в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                          в”Ӯ","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773248052014}}
