{"type":"message","id":"b1b3cb73","parentId":"afe37220","timestamp":"2026-03-11T16:54:40.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me answer all your questions:\n\n---\n\n# рҹ“– **Complete Answer to Your Questions**\n\n## 1. **Why Can't I Update the Dashboard?**\n\n**I CAN!** I just didn't automatically. Here's why:\n\n**I Created**:\n- вң… Documentation files\n- вң… Reference code\n- вң… Setup scripts\n\n**I Should Have**:\n- вқҢ Asked you: \"Should I update the dashboard now?\"\n- вқҢ Or just done it directly\n\n**Lesson Learned**: Next time I'll either:\n1. Ask first, OR\n2. Just do it and tell you\n\n---\n\n## 2. **Sub-Agents - When & How to Use**\n\n### Available Agents\n\n| Agent | Best For | Example |\n|-------|----------|---------|\n| **Coding Agent** | Building features, PR reviews | \"Add chat system\" |\n| **Gemini** | Quick questions | \"What's X?\" |\n| **GitHub** | GitHub operations | \"Check PR #42\" |\n| **Weather** | Weather queries | \"Weather in Dubai\" |\n\n### **Who Decides?**\n\n**I DO!** Based on task:\n\n```\nSimple edit? вҶ’ I do it directly\nNew feature? вҶ’ Coding Agent\nGitHub work? вҶ’ GitHub skill\nQuestion? вҶ’ Gemini skill\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. **Guardian - How to Start & Modes**\n\n### What is Guardian?\n**Multi-agent AI coding orchestrator** - 5 agents working together\n\n### Location\n`~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/`\n\n### How to Start\n```bash\ncd ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026\n./claude-safe --status\n./claude-safe \"your task\" ./project-path\n```\n\n### Two Modes\n\n**Mode 1: Multi-Agent (Default)**\n- 5 stages: Analyze вҶ’ Plan вҶ’ Audit вҶ’ Execute вҶ’ Review\n- Best for: Large projects, production code\n- Slower but better quality\n\n**Mode 2: Single Agent (Fast)**\n- Direct execution\n- Best for: Quick fixes\n- Faster but less thorough\n\n### Guardian's 5 Agents\n1. **Analyzer** - Classifies task\n2. **Planner** (Gemini) - Creates plan\n3. **Guardian** (DeepSeek) - Safety audit\n4. **Worker** - Executes code\n5. **Reviewer** - Quality check\n\n---\n\n## 4. **Which is Better - Guardian or Nova's Agents?**\n\n| Use This... | For This... |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| **Nova (direct)** | Simple edits, read files, run commands |\n| **Coding Agent** | New features, PR reviews, refactoring |\n| **Guardian** | Large projects, production code (multi-agent review) |\n\n### Quick Decision Tree\n\n```\nTask: \"Fix typo in file\"\nвҶ’ Use Nova (edit directly)\n\nTask: \"Add chat feature\"\nвҶ’ Use Coding Agent\n\nTask: \"Refactor entire app\"\nвҶ’ Use Guardian (multi-agent)\n```\n\n---\n\n## вң… **Full Guide Created**\n\nI created a complete guide for you:\n**`~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/NOVA_CAPABILITIES_GUIDE.md`**\n\nIt covers:\n- What I can/cannot do\n- When to use each agent\n- How Guardian works\n- Guardian's 2 modes\n- Decision matrix\n- Practical examples\n\n**Check it out!**\n\n---\n\n**Want me to update the dashboard now with the chat/voice features?**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":38432,"output":736,"cacheRead":9600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48768,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773248071413}}
