{"type":"message","id":"b0c898e9","parentId":"282a1a43","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:06:16.697Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"2A328021F0AEDC06D3C2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+971504042000\",\n  \"sender\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant (+971504042000)\",\n  \"id\": \"+971504042000\",\n  \"name\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant\",\n  \"e164\": \"+971504042000\"\n}\n```\n\nOk but the guardians mode we have one mode to only plan and give the task without edit and emplementinf and the second is to run them with fully implemenation and apply all changes . Check that and alsk test them now . Make sure the wirks and no issue for bith mode . And make sure also your agents have the neeed api keys from our SSOT keys\n\nI want you to save this SSOT keys in your memory as always yiu will use them and no hardcoded or expose for keys\nThen also guardians as you will also always use them in most of the coding tasks \nAnd also xmad-control-center. This is very important project to finish building it as it should be the workspace for you where everything should be saved here from your persona brain memory heartbeat memory and all related to you. So I have easy acsess and always uodate it for better results and shape to match our works. Also the tasks I gave you we should add them all with the progress so we can know . Note , notification automations Calender and other important things all should be here . So itвҖҷs the workspace and the place where me and yiu have acsess and organize , plan, control, follow up all the works"}],"timestamp":1773248776692}}
