{"type":"message","id":"9eff7bc6","parentId":"d7817a3e","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:06:28.337Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9ed224a850a14ffcbd97a2ba","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Guardian Orchestrator 2026 вҖ” Usage\n\nMODES:\n  ./claude-safe \"task\"              Suggest mode (default) - output only\n  ./claude-safe --suggest \"task\"    Suggest mode (explicit)\n  ./claude-safe --execute \"task\"    Execute mode - apply changes to files\n  ./claude-safe --dry-run \"task\"    Preview what execute would do\n  ./claude-safe --rollback <id>     Restore files from backup session\n\nOTHER:\n  ./claude-safe --status            Check all agent connectivity\n  ./claude-safe --models            List all configured models\n  ./claude-safe --help              Show this help\n\nExamples:\n  ./claude-safe \"Fix the login bug in auth.ts\"\n  ./claude-safe --execute \"Add rate limiting to the API\" ./my-project\n  ./claude-safe --dry-run \"Refactor UserService\" .\n  ./claude-safe --rollback session-20260309-120000\n\nPipeline:\n  Task вҶ’ Analyze вҶ’ Plan вҶ’ Guardian Audit вҶ’ Worker вҶ’ Review вҶ’ [Execute]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2565,"aggregated":"Guardian Orchestrator 2026 вҖ” Usage\n\nMODES:\n  ./claude-safe \"task\"              Suggest mode (default) - output only\n  ./claude-safe --suggest \"task\"    Suggest mode (explicit)\n  ./claude-safe --execute \"task\"    Execute mode - apply changes to files\n  ./claude-safe --dry-run \"task\"    Preview what execute would do\n  ./claude-safe --rollback <id>     Restore files from backup session\n\nOTHER:\n  ./claude-safe --status            Check all agent connectivity\n  ./claude-safe --models            List all configured models\n  ./claude-safe --help              Show this help\n\nExamples:\n  ./claude-safe \"Fix the login bug in auth.ts\"\n  ./claude-safe --execute \"Add rate limiting to the API\" ./my-project\n  ./claude-safe --dry-run \"Refactor UserService\" .\n  ./claude-safe --rollback session-20260309-120000\n\nPipeline:\n  Task вҶ’ Analyze вҶ’ Plan вҶ’ Guardian Audit вҶ’ Worker вҶ’ Review вҶ’ [Execute]","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773248788334}}
