{"type":"message","id":"38ed8fb0","parentId":"4092080f","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:06:38.562Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cea7ebf3e0764050ba3e5ee4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SSOT API Keys - Complete Guide\n\n> **Single Source of Truth for All API Keys**\n> Generated: 2026-02-27\n> Version: 2.0\n\n---\n\n## Table of Contents\n\n1. [Architecture Overview](#architecture-overview)\n2. [API Provider Formats](#api-provider-formats)\n3. [Key Locations](#key-locations)\n4. [VPN + SSH Remote Access](#vpn--ssh-remote-access)\n5. [All Keys Inventory](#all-keys-inventory)\n6. [How to Use Keys](#how-to-use-keys)\n7. [How to Use in Scripts](#how-to-use-in-scripts)\n8. [How to Add Keys to Projects](#how-to-add-keys-to-projects)\n9. [How to Add New Keys](#how-to-add-new-keys)\n10. [Best Practices](#best-practices)\n11. [Troubleshooting](#troubleshooting)\n12. [Quick Reference](#quick-reference)\n\n---\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                  macOS KEYCHAIN                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ              (Root of Trust - Master Backup)            в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  All secrets stored with SSOT_* prefix                 в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Hardware-backed by Apple Secure Enclave               в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                          в”Ӯ\n                          в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                   INFISICAL                             в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ           (Runtime Secrets Provider)                    в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Project ID: 3f265951-5e47-4460-88c1-ad9bee65b1ac      в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  Environment: dev, staging, prod                        в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  13+ secrets available for injection                    в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n                          в”Ӯ\n                          в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                   PROJECTS                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ            (Zero Secrets Zone)                          в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  No .env files allowed                                  в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  No hardcoded secrets                                   в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  All secrets via Infisical injection                    в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Provider Formats\n\n**CRITICAL: Each provider uses different API formats. Using the wrong format will fail.**\n\n### z.ai (GLM Models)\n\n```bash\n# z.ai uses Anthropic-compatible API (NOT OpenAI format!)\n# Endpoint: https://api.z.ai/api/anthropic/v1/messages\n# Header: x-api-key (NOT Authorization: Bearer)\n# Models: GLM-5, GLM-4.7, GLM-4-Plus\n\n# Correct API call:\ncurl -X POST \"https://api.z.ai/api/anthropic/v1/messages\" \\\n  -H \"x-api-key: YOUR_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"anthropic-version: 2023-06-01\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"GLM-5\",\n    \"max_tokens\": 100,\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello\"}]\n  }'\n\n# Response format: .content[0].text\n```\n\n### Groq (OpenAI-Compatible)\n\n```bash\n# Groq uses standard OpenAI format\n# Endpoint: https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/chat/completions\n# Header: Authorization: Bearer\n# Models: llama-3.3-70b-versatile, moonshotai/kimi-k2-instruct, llama-3.1-8b-instant\n\ncurl -X POST \"https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/chat/completions\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer YOUR_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"llama-3.3-70b-versatile\",\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello\"}],\n    \"max_tokens\": 100\n  }'\n\n# Response format: .choices[0].message.content\n```\n\n### DeepSeek (OpenAI-Compatible)\n\n```bash\n# DeepSeek uses OpenAI format\n# Endpoint: https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions\n# Header: Authorization: Bearer\n# Models: deepseek-chat, deepseek-reasoner\n\ncurl -X POST \"https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer YOUR_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"deepseek-chat\",\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello\"}],\n    \"max_tokens\": 100\n  }'\n\n# Response format: .choices[0].message.content\n```\n\n### Gemini (Native Format)\n\n```bash\n# Gemini uses its own format (key in URL)\n# Endpoint: https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/MODEL:generateContent?key=KEY\n# Models: gemini-2.5-flash, gemini-2.0-flash\n\ncurl -X POST \"https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-2.5-flash:generateContent?key=YOUR_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"contents\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"parts\": [{\"text\": \"Hello\"}]}],\n    \"generationConfig\": {\"maxOutputTokens\": 100}\n  }'\n\n# Response format: .candidates[0].content.parts[0].text\n```\n\n### OpenRouter (OpenAI-Compatible)\n\n```bash\n# OpenRouter uses OpenAI format\n# Endpoint: https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/chat/completions\n# Header: Authorization: Bearer\n# Models: Many models including free tier\n\ncurl -X POST \"https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/chat/completions\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer YOUR_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"anthropic/claude-3-haiku\",\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello\"}],\n    \"max_tokens\": 100\n  }'\n\n# Response format: .choices[0].message.content\n```\n\n### Quick Reference Table\n\n| Provider | Format | Auth Header | Response Path |\n|----------|--------|-------------|---------------|\n| z.ai | Anthropic | `x-api-key` | `.content[0].text` |\n| Groq | OpenAI | `Authorization: Bearer` | `.choices[0].message.content` |\n| DeepSeek | OpenAI | `Authorization: Bearer` | `.choices[0].message.content` |\n| Gemini | Native | `?key=` in URL | `.candidates[0].content.parts[0].text` |\n| OpenRouter | OpenAI | `Authorization: Bearer` | `.choices[0].message.content` |\n\n---\n\n## What We Did\n\n### Step 1: Key Inventory & Classification\n- Audited all 19 API keys across the system\n- Classified into: OPERATIONAL (13), CLI (4), DEPRECATED (2)\n- Identified keys from: z.ai, OpenRouter, Gemini, ElevenLabs, Deepgram, E2B, Supabase, Clerk, NextAuth, GitHub\n\n### Step 2: Infisical Setup\n- Created new Infisical project \"SSOT-keys\"\n- Project ID: `3f265951-5e47-4460-88c1-ad9bee65b1ac`\n- Imported all 13 OPERATIONAL keys\n- Created service token stored in Keychain\n\n### Step 3: Cleanup\n- Backed up all .env files to `~/env-backup-ssot/`\n- Deleted .env files from all projects\n- Updated package.json scripts with Infisical injection\n\n### Step 4: Guardian Orchestrator\n- Created deployment scripts\n- Added CLI aliases for different AI providers\n- Set up health check system\n\n### Step 5: VPN + SSH Remote Access (2026-03-06)\n- Installed Tailscale VPN (CLI v1.94.2)\n- Configured SSH with password + key authentication\n\n[532 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773248798557}}
{"type":"message","id":"59b4225d","parentId":"38ed8fb0","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:06:53.661Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cc4c9972aa374f57a1d063f4","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"tender-trail","timeout":15000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dbac7c0cd8ef4931bf5b8330","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026 && cat .env | grep -E \"API_KEY|BASE_URL\" | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7c8a337cb34848b88e04e038","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# SSOT API Keys - Quick Reference for Nova\n\n**Last Updated**: 2026-03-11\n**Purpose**: Nova's reference for API keys (NO hardcoded keys)\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”‘ Key Locations (SSOT - Single Source of Truth)\n\n### Primary Storage\n- **Infisical** (Runtime): Project ID `3f265951-5e47-4460-88c1-ad9bee65b1ac`\n- **macOS Keychain** (Master): All secrets with `SSOT_*` prefix\n- **Projects**: ZERO secrets (all injected via Infisical)\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ӣ Available Keys (Infisical + Keychain)\n\n### AI/LLM Providers\n\n| Key Name | Provider | Usage | Status |\n|----------|----------|-------|--------|\n| `SSOT_ZAI_API_KEY` | z.ai | GLM-5, GLM-4.7 models | вң… Active |\n| `SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY` | Groq | Llama 3.3, Kimi K2, GPT-OSS | вң… Active |\n| `SSOT_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY` | DeepSeek | DeepSeek-V3, DeepSeek-R1 | вң… Active |\n| `SSOT_GEMINI_API_KEY` | Google | Gemini 2.5 Flash, 2.0 Flash | вң… Active |\n| `SSOT_OPENROUTER_API_KEY` | OpenRouter | Multi-provider router | вң… Active |\n\n### Voice Services\n\n| Key Name | Provider | Usage | Status |\n|----------|----------|-------|--------|\n| `SSOT_DEEPGRAM_API_KEY` | Deepgram | STT (Speech-to-Text) | вң… Active |\n| `SSOT_ELEVENLABS_API_KEY` | ElevenLabs | TTS (Text-to-Speech) | вң… Active |\n\n### Database/Auth\n\n| Key Name | Provider | Usage | Status |\n|----------|----------|-------|--------|\n| `SSOT_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` | Supabase | Database access | вң… Active |\n| `SSOT_SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY` | Supabase | Admin operations | вң… Active |\n| `SSOT_CLERK_SECRET_KEY` | Clerk | Authentication | вң… Active |\n| `SSOT_NEXTAUTH_SECRET` | NextAuth | Auth sessions | вң… Active |\n\n### Other Services\n\n| Key Name | Provider | Usage | Status |\n|----------|----------|-------|--------|\n| `SSOT_E2B_API_KEY` | E2B | Code execution sandbox | вң… Active |\n| `SSOT_GITHUB_TOKEN` | GitHub | GitHub API access | вң… Active |\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”§ How to Use Keys (CLI)\n\n### Method 1: Infisical CLI (Recommended)\n\n```bash\n# Inject all secrets into environment\neval $(infisical run --env=dev -- your-command)\n\n# Example with Node\neval $(infisical run --env=dev -- node server.js)\n\n# Example with Python\neval $(infisical run --env=dev -- python app.py)\n```\n\n### Method 2: Get Specific Key\n\n```bash\n# Get single key\nexport GROQ_API_KEY=$(infisical get --env=dev SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY)\n\n# Use in command\ninfisical run --env=dev -- npm start\n```\n\n### Method 3: From macOS Keychain\n\n```bash\n# Get SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY\nsecurity find-generic-password -w -s \"SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY\"\n\n# Get SSOT_ZAI_API_KEY\nsecurity find-generic-password -w -s \"SSOT_ZAI_API_KEY\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹҡ« Rules for Nova\n\n### вң… DO\n- Use Infisical CLI for runtime injection\n- Reference this file for key names\n- Check Guardian's .env for examples\n- Use security commands to access Keychain\n\n### вқҢ NEVER\n- Hardcode API keys in files\n- Create .env files with secrets\n- Commit keys to git\n- Share keys in chat/output\n- Create unencrypted backups\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҜ Common Use Cases\n\n### Use Case 1: Start Guardian\n```bash\ncd ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026\n# Guardian already has keys in .env (from Keychain)\n./claude-safe \"task\" ./project\n```\n\n### Use Case 2: Use Coding Agent\n```bash\n# Coding agent will use Infisical automatically\n# Keys injected at runtime\n```\n\n### Use Case 3: Make API Call\n```bash\n# Get key first\nexport GROQ_API_KEY=$(infisical get --env=dev SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY)\n\n# Use it\ncurl -X POST \"https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/chat/completions\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $GROQ_API_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"llama-3.3-70b-versatile\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Hello\"}]}'\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”Қ Verify Keys Work\n\n```bash\n# Test Groq\nexport GROQ_API_KEY=$(infisical get --env=dev SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY)\ncurl -X POST \"https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/chat/completions\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $GROQ_API_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"llama-3.3-70b-versatile\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"test\"}],\"max_tokens\":10}'\n\n# Test z.ai\nexport ZAI_API_KEY=$(infisical get --env=dev SSOT_ZAI_API_KEY)\ncurl -X POST \"https://api.z.ai/api/anthropic/v1/messages\" \\\n  -H \"x-api-key: $ZAI_API_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"anthropic-version: 2023-06-01\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"GLM-5\",\"max_tokens\":10,\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"test\"}]}'\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ҡ Guardian Agent Keys\n\nGuardian uses these keys (from ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/.env):\n\n| Agent | Key | Model |\n|-------|-----|-------|\n| Guardian (orchestrator) | `SSOT_ZAI_API_KEY` | GLM-5 |\n| Coder | `SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY` | Kimi K2 |\n| Reasoning | `SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY` | GPT-OSS-120B |\n| Fast | `SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY` | Llama 4 Scout |\n| Planner | `SSOT_GEMINI_API_KEY` | Gemini 2.5 Flash |\n| Workhorse | `SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY` | Qwen3 32B |\n\nAll keys already configured in Guardian!\nJust run: `./claude-safe \"task\" ./project`\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“қ Quick Reference Commands\n\n```bash\n# Check Infisical status\ninfisical status\n\n# List all secrets\ninfisical list --env=dev\n\n# Get specific secret\ninfisical get --env=dev SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY\n\n# Inject into command\ninfisical run --env=dev -- npm start\n\n# Check Keychain for SSOT keys\nsecurity find-generic-password -w -s \"SSOT_*\" 2>/dev/null\n\n# Verify Guardian has keys\ncd ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026 && ./claude-safe --status\n```\n\n---\n\n## вҡ пёҸ Important Notes\n\n1. **Never hardcode keys** - Always use Infisical or Keychain\n2. **Guardian is configured** - Keys already in .env\n3. **Nova's agents use Infisical** - Automatic injection\n4. **Projects have zero secrets** - All injected at runtime\n5. **Master backup in Keychain** - Can restore if needed\n\n---\n\n**End of Reference**\n\nGenerated: 2026-03-11\nFor: Nova (AI Assistant)\nPurpose: SSOT API key reference\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace/SSOT_KEYS_REFERENCE.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":3233,"output":1856,"cacheRead":49152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54241,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773248798561}}
