enseVoice)\n- [ ] Voice output (TTS - Chatterbox/Kokoro)\n- [ ] Backup/Restore buttons\n- [ ] Brain viewer (SOUL, IDENTITY, MEMORY, USER)\n- [ ] Config viewer (openclaw.json)\n- [ ] Log viewer (openclaw, gateway, watchdog)\n- [ ] PC Optimization button\n\n**Files Created** (awaiting application):\n- DASHBOARD_UPDATE_GUIDE.md\n- ENHANCED_AI_CHAT.js\n- README_UPDATE_NOW.md\n\n**Files to Update**:\n- app.js - Replace sendAIMessage(), add voice functions\n- index.html - Update chat input HTML\n- styles.css - Add button styles\n\n**Blocked On**: User confirmation to apply changes\n\n---\n\n### 4. вң… Guardian Verification & Testing\n**Status**: IN PROGRESS\n**Date**: 2026-03-11 20:55\n**Description**: Verify Guardian modes work correctly\n\n**Modes Confirmed**:\n- вң… **Suggest Mode** (default): Plans only, no changes\n- вң… **Execute Mode** (--execute): Applies all changes\n- вң… **Dry-Run Mode** (--dry-run): Preview execute\n\n**Agent Status** (from ./claude-safe --status):\n- вң… GLM-5 (Guardian)\n- вң… Kimi K2 / Groq (Coder)\n- вқҢ GPT-OSS-120B (Reasoning) - offline/key missing\n- вң… Llama 4 Scout (Fast)\n- вң… Qwen3 32B (Workhorse)\n- вқҢ Gemini 2.5 Flash (Planner) - offline/key missing\n\n**Keys Configured** (from .env):\n- вң… GLM_API_KEY (from Keychain)\n- вң… GROQ_API_KEY (from Keychain)\n- вң… GEMINI_API_KEY (from Keychain)\n- вң… DEEPSEEK_API_KEY (from Keychain)\n\n**Testing In Progress**:\n- Testing suggest mode with simple task\n- Testing dry-run mode\n- Testing execute mode\n\n---\n\n### 5. рҹ“қ XMAD Workspace Centralization\n**Status**: NEW - JUST STARTED\n**Date**: 2026-03-11 20:55\n**Priority**: HIGH\n**Description**: Make XMAD the central workspace for Nova + Ahmad\n\n**Requirements**:\n- [ ] Nova's persona (SOUL.md) вҶ’ XMAD docs\n- [ ] Nova's memory (MEMORY.md) вҶ’ XMAD docs\n- [ ] Nova's identity (IDENTITY.md) вҶ’ XMAD docs\n- [ ] Task tracker (this file) вҶ’ XMAD\n- [ ] Notes & notifications вҶ’ XMAD\n- [ ] Calendar integration вҶ’ XMAD\n- [ ] Automation tasks вҶ’ XMAD\n- [ ] Progress tracking вҶ’ XMAD\n\n**Goal**: Single dashboard for:\n- Planning\n- Organization\n- Control\n- Follow-up\n- All work coordination\n\n**Next Steps**:\n1. Copy Nova's core files to XMAD/docs/\n2. Create task tracking system in XMAD\n3. Add notes/calendar sections\n4. Integrate with OpenClaw heartbeat\n5. Add notification system\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ҡ Progress Summary\n\n| Task | Status | Progress | Priority |\n|------|--------|----------|----------|\n| OpenClaw Unification | вң… Complete | 100% | High |\n| Backup & Voice Setup | вң… Complete | 100% | High |\n| XMAD Dashboard Update | вҸі Pending | 80% (docs done) | High |\n| Guardian Testing | вҸі In Progress | 60% | Medium |\n| XMAD Workspace Hub | рҹҶ• New | 0% | High |\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”§ System Configuration\n\n### OpenClaw\n- **Version**: 2026.3.8\n- **Memory**: 768MB max, 100ms GC\n- **Model**: zai/glm-5 primary, zai/glm-4.7 fallback\n- **Location**: ~/.openclaw/\n\n### Guardian\n- **Version**: 2.2.0\n- **Location**: ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/\n- **Active Agents**: 4/6 (2 missing keys)\n- **Keys**: From Keychain (SSOT_*)\n\n### XMAD Dashboard\n- **Version**: 3.0\n- **Port**: 8765\n- **Location**: ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/\n- **Status**: Running, needs updates\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ң Quick Actions\n\n### Start Services\n```bash\n# OpenClaw\n~/.openclaw/scripts/start-optimized.sh\n\n# XMAD Dashboard\ncd ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center && ./start.sh\n\n# Guardian (for coding tasks)\ncd ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026 && ./claude-safe \"task\" ./project\n\n# Voice Services (optional)\n~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/voice/start-voice-services.sh\n```\n\n### Check Status\n```bash\n# OpenClaw\ncurl http://localhost:18789/health\n\n# XMAD\ncurl http://localhost:8765/api/status\n\n# Guardian\ncd ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026 && ./claude-safe --status\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҜ Next Immediate Actions\n\n1. **Apply XMAD Dashboard Updates** (awaiting confirmation)\n2. **Complete Guardian Testing** (verify execute mode)\n3. **Build XMAD Workspace Hub** (centralize everything)\n4. **Add Task Tracking** (persistent task system)\n\n---\n\n**End of Task Tracker**\n\nLast Updated: 2026-03-11 20:55\nMaintained by: Nova (рҹҡҖ)\nLocation: ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/TASKS.md\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/TASKS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":7896,"output":1678,"cacheRead":46720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56294,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773248818735}}
