{"type":"message","id":"a1c9a513","parentId":"db01a060","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:22:00.788Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-11 21:06:58 GMT+4] Exec completed (tender-t, code 0) :: в•”в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•— в•‘ Guardian Orchestrator вҖ” Agent Status в•‘ в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•қ вң… GLM-5 (Guardian) вң… Kimi K2 / GвҖҰ\nSystem: [2026-03-11 21:07:28 GMT+4] Exec completed (salty-lo, code 0) :: / For CommonJS // or // import helloWorld from './hello.js'; // For ES6 modules console.log(helloWorld()); // Should print \"Hello World\" ``` Run `test.js` using Node.js: ```bash nвҖҰ\nSystem: [2026-03-11 21:07:49 GMT+4] Exec completed (young-wi, code 0) :: в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ EXECUTOR: Applying File Changes в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ Project: /tmp/test-guardian-suggest Dry-run: --dry-run \ud83dвҖҰ\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"2A849A2785BF10F7820E\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+971504042000\",\n  \"sender\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant (+971504042000)\",\n  \"id\": \"+971504042000\",\n  \"name\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant\",\n  \"e164\": \"+971504042000\"\n}\n```\n\nYes .\nSee now. Xmad-control-center in a temporary project and dashboard. All xmad-control-center will be moved to the nextjs monorepo project and deploy it also . \nSo first step to build this temprory xmad-control-center and brainstorm and add all what we need and organize them all there. \nNext we will move them to be in desktop/euiui project or create new clean nextjs latest bun biome tailwind and move them to be needed components from euiui project to the new one and build the dashboard and the control pages . \n\nFinal step is to move this nextjs control center and itвҖҷs dashboard and add it to the final monirepo in desktop/platform-monorepo \nTo replace the factory-dashboard ther so we have the final complete controler brain to control all what we have in xmad control center and manage and monitor the multi tenants and projects and all the monirepo from one place . \nThis all need proper plan, audit , check all our sources from the other projects like the voice-microservice and xmad-ecosystem and some opensources the best and latest so we can add them all to creat the final ecosystem runs by agents and create projects and tenants on the go very fast from all the standlone modular packages we have. \nNo need to rush doing All one time.. we will plan it correctly and create the roadmap and progress and then continue the works some automated like and some live. Until all done. \nWe will use all your agents and guardians , and you to maximize the production."}],"timestamp":1773249720775}}
{"type":"message","id":"8999492a","parentId":"a1c9a513","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:22:23.774Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! This is a BIG vision. Let me create a comprehensive roadmap and plan for this multi-phase ecosystem build."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c5a6e550f991448885545e66","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# рҹҡҖ XMAD Control Center - Complete Ecosystem Roadmap\n\n**Vision**: Build the ultimate AI-powered control center for managing multi-tenant projects, agents, and services\n\n**Date**: 2026-03-11\n**Status**: Planning Phase\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ӣ The Big Picture\n\n```\nPhase 1: Current XMAD (Temp)\n    вҶ“\nPhase 2: Next.js Standalone\n    вҶ“\nPhase 3: Platform Monorepo (Final)\n```\n\n**Final Goal**: Replace factory-dashboard with AI-powered control center\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҜ Three-Phase Plan\n\n### **Phase 1: Temporary XMAD Control Center**\n**Location**: `~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/`\n**Status**: вң… Running (Node.js + vanilla HTML)\n**Purpose**: Prototype, brainstorm, organize all features\n**Duration**: 1-2 weeks\n\n**Objectives**:\n- [ ] Add all Nova's files (SOUL, MEMORY, IDENTITY, USER)\n- [ ] Build task tracking system\n- [ ] Add notes/calendar features\n- [ ] Integrate OpenClaw monitoring\n- [ ] Add Guardian control panel\n- [ ] Voice services integration\n- [ ] Documentation hub\n- [ ] Notification system\n- [ ] Test all features\n- [ ] Document what works/doesn't\n\n**Deliverables**:\n- Working prototype\n- Feature list (what we want)\n- Component inventory\n- Data structures\n- API requirements\n- Lessons learned\n\n---\n\n### **Phase 2: Next.js Standalone Dashboard**\n**Location**: `~/Desktop/xmad-dashboard-nextjs/` (new)\n**Tech Stack**:\n- Next.js 15 (latest)\n- Bun (runtime)\n- Biome (linter/formatter)\n- Tailwind CSS\n- TypeScript\n- shadcn/ui components\n\n**Purpose**: Production-ready standalone dashboard\n**Duration**: 3-4 weeks\n\n**Source Components**:\n- From `~/Desktop/euiui/` (existing UI components)\n- From current XMAD (features)\n- From open-source (best packages)\n- From voice-microservices (integrations)\n\n**Key Features**:\n1. **Dashboard Home**\n   - System status overview\n   - Quick actions\n   - Recent activities\n   - Metrics/charts\n\n2. **OpenClaw Control**\n   - Start/stop/restart\n   - Memory monitoring\n   - Log viewer\n   - Config editor\n   - Brain viewer (SOUL, MEMORY, etc.)\n\n3. **Guardian Orchestrator**\n   - Task submission\n   - Mode selection (suggest/execute/dry-run)\n   - Agent status\n   - Progress tracking\n   - Result viewer\n\n4. **Multi-Tenant Management**\n   - Tenant list\n   - Create/delete tenants\n   - Tenant settings\n   - Per-tenant configs\n\n5. **Project Management**\n   - Project list\n   - Create projects (from templates)\n   - Project templates (standalone packages)\n   - Build/deploy controls\n\n6. **Voice Services Hub**\n   - STT providers (SenseVoice, Deepgram, Groq)\n   - TTS providers (Chatterbox, Kokoro, Qwen3, ElevenLabs)\n   - Voice testing\n   - Provider status\n\n7. **Agent Workspace**\n   - Nova's persona editor\n   - Memory viewer/editor\n   - Task tracker\n   - Notes system\n   - Calendar integration\n\n8. **Documentation Center**\n   - API docs\n   - Guides\n   - Tutorials\n   - System architecture\n\n9. **Notification System**\n   - Alerts\n   - Status updates\n   - Task completions\n   - Error notifications\n\n10. **Settings**\n    - API keys (SSOT integration)\n    - Preferences\n    - System configs\n    - User management\n\n**Deliverables**:\n- Next.js app with all features\n- Component library\n- API routes\n- Database schemas\n- Deployment configs\n\n---\n\n### **Phase 3: Platform Monorepo Integration**\n**Location**: `~/Desktop/platform-monorepo/`\n**Purpose**: Replace factory-dashboard with AI-powered control center\n**Duration**: 4-6 weeks\n\n**Integration Points**:\n1. **Multi-Tenant System**\n   - Tenant creation/management\n   - Isolation per tenant\n   - Tenant-specific configs\n\n2. **Project Templates**\n   - Standalone packages\n   - Auto-scaffolding\n   - Template gallery\n\n3. **Agent Automation**\n   - Guardian orchestration\n   - Nova integration\n   - Sub-agent management\n\n4. **CI/CD Integration**\n   - Auto-build on changes\n   - Deploy previews\n   - Production deployments\n\n5. **Monitoring**\n   - All services\n   - Logs aggregation\n   - Metrics collection\n   - Alerting\n\n**Deliverables**:\n- Monorepo integration\n- Factory dashboard replaced\n- Full ecosystem control\n- Multi-tenant support\n- Agent-powered automation\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ҡ Source Inventory\n\n### Existing Projects to Audit\n\n1. **voice-microservices** (`~/Desktop/ignore/voice-microservices/`)\n   - Providers: SenseVoice, Chatterbox, Kokoro, Qwen3\n   - APIs: STT, TTS endpoints\n   - Status: Working, need integration\n\n2. **xmad-ecosystem** (if exists)\n   - Components\n   - Services\n   - Utilities\n   - Status: Need to check\n\n3. **euiui** (`~/Desktop/euiui/`)\n   - UI components\n   - Design system\n   - Reusable parts\n   - Status: Need to audit\n\n4. **factory-dashboard** (in monorepo)\n   - Current implementation\n   - What to replace\n   - Features to keep\n   - Status: Need to audit\n\n5. **platform-monorepo** (`~/Desktop/platform-monorepo/`)\n   - Structure\n   - Existing apps\n   - Integration points\n   - Status: Need to audit\n\n---\n\n## рҹӨ– Agent & Guardian Usage Plan\n\n### Nova (Me)\n**Role**: Project coordinator, documentation, planning\n**Tasks**:\n- Create roadmaps\n- Write documentation\n- Coordinate agents\n- Review progress\n- Update task tracker\n- Brainstorm features\n\n### Coding Agent\n**Role**: Feature implementation, refactoring\n**Tasks**:\n- Build Next.js components\n- Implement API routes\n- Refactor code from euiui\n- Create project templates\n- Write tests\n\n### Guardian Orchestrator\n**Role**: Large-scale coding, multi-file changes\n**Tasks**:\n- Migrate components\n- Refactor large codebases\n- Create new features\n- Review code quality\n- Execute mode for deployments\n\n### Gemini\n**Role**: Quick Q&A, research\n**Tasks**:\n- Research best practices\n- Answer technical questions\n- Summarize documentation\n- Generate ideas\n\n---\n\n## рҹ—ӮпёҸ Component Inventory (To Build)\n\n### Dashboard Components\n```\ndashboard/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ home/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ overview.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ quick-actions.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ recent-activity.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ metrics-chart.tsx\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ control-panel.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ memory-monitor.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ log-viewer.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ config-editor.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ brain-viewer.tsx\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ guardian/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ task-submit.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ mode-selector.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ agent-status.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ progress-tracker.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ result-viewer.tsx\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ tenants/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tenant-list.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tenant-create.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tenant-settings.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ tenant-config.tsx\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ projects/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ project-list.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ project-create.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ template-gallery.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ build-deploy.tsx\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ voice/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ provider-status.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ stt-tester.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tts-tester.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ voice-settings.tsx\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ workspace/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ persona-editor.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ memory-viewer.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ task-tracker.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ notes-system.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ calendar.tsx\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ docs/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ api-docs.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ guides.tsx\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ tutorials.tsx\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ notifications/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ notification-center.tsx\nв””в”Җв”Җ settings/\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ api-keys.tsx\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ preferences.tsx\n    в””в”Җв”Җ system-config.tsx\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“қ Data Structures\n\n### Tenant\n```typescript\ninterface Tenant {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  slug: string;\n  createdAt: Date;\n  configs: TenantConfig[];\n  projects: Project[];\n}\n```\n\n### Project\n```typescript\ninterface Project {\n  id: string;\n  tenantId: string;\n  name: string;\n  template: string;\n  status: 'building' | 'deployed' | 'error';\n  createdAt: Date;\n}\n```\n\n### Task\n```typescript\ninterface Task {\n  id: string;\n  title: string;\n  status: 'todo' | 'in-progress' | 'done';\n  priority: 'low' | 'medium' | 'high';\n  assignee: 'nova' | 'coding-agent' | 'guardian';\n  createdAt: Date;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ—“пёҸ Timeline (Rough Estimate)\n\n### Phase 1: Temporary XMAD\n- Week 1: Add features, organize, document\n- Week 2: Test, refine, create inventory\n\n**Duration**: 2 weeks\n\n### Phase 2: Next.js Dashboard\n- Week 1: Setup, audit sources, design system\n- Week 2: Core components (dashboard, OpenClaw, Guardian)\n- Week 3: Advanced features (tenants, projects, voice)\n- Week 4: Workspace, docs, notifications, polish\n\n**Duration**: 4 weeks\n\n### Phase 3: Monorepo Integration\n- Week 1: Audit monorepo, plan integration\n- Week 2: Tenant system integration\n- Week 3: Project templates system\n- Week 4: Agent automation\n- Week 5: CI/CD, monitoring\n- Week 6: Testing, polish, deploy\n\n**Duration**: 6 weeks\n\n**Total**: 12 weeks (~3 months)\n\n---\n\n## вң… Next Immediate Actions (Phase 1)\n\n### 1. Audit Existing Projects\n```bash\n# Check euiui components\nls -la ~/Desktop/euiui/\n\n# Check platform-monorepo\nls -la ~/Desktop/platform-monorepo/\n\n# Check factory-dashboard\nfind ~/Desktop/platform-monorepo -name \"*factory*\" -o -name \"*dashboard*\"\n```\n\n### 2. Brainstorm Features\n- Open TASKS.md in XMAD\n- Add all feature ideas\n- Organize by category\n- Prioritize by importance\n\n### 3. Copy Nova Files\n```bash\n# Copy to XMAD workspace\ncp ~/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/docs/\ncp ~/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/docs/\ncp ~/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/docs/\ncp ~/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/docs/\n```\n\n### 4. Create Component Inventory\n- List all components needed\n- Check what exists in euiui\n- Mark what to build\n- Note open-source alternatives\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҜ Success Criteria\n\n### Phase 1 Success\n- [ ] All features documented in TASKS.md\n- [ ] Component inventory complete\n- [ ] Data structures defined\n- [ ] Nova files integrated\n- [ ] Working prototype tested\n\n### Phase 2 Success\n- [ ] Next.js app deployed\n- [ ] All features working\n- [ ] Component library built\n- [ ] APIs tested\n- [ ] Documentation complete\n\n### Phase 3 Success\n- [ ] Integrated in monorepo\n- [ ] Factory dashboard replaced\n- [ ] Multi-tenant system working\n- [ ] Agent automation running\n- [ ] Production deployed\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ҡ Progress Tracking\n\n**Current Phase**: Phase 1 - Temporary XMAD\n**Progress**: 10% (planning started)\n\n**Overall Progress**: 3% (of all 3 phases)\n\n---\n\n**Next Step**: Start Phase 1 by auditing existing projects and brainstorming features\n\n---\n\n**Roadmap End**\n\nCreated: 2026-03-11\nBy: Nova (рҹҡҖ)\nStatus: Planning Phase - Ready to execute\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/ECOSYSTEM_ROADMAP.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":851,"output":2767,"cacheRead":61952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773249720778}}
