ventory Components\n\nFrom all found projects:\n- List reusable components\n- Note design systems\n- Check dependencies\n- Document integration points\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“қ Questions to Resolve\n\n1. **euiui**: Does it exist? What's the correct name/location?\n2. **xmad/**: What's in here? Old code? Components?\n3. **xmad-ai-voice**: Voice integration code? Can we use it?\n4. **factory-dashboard**: Current features? What to keep?\n5. **platform-monorepo**: Structure? How to integrate?\n\n---\n\n## рҹҡҖ Action Plan\n\n1. **Investigate** xmad/ and xmad-ai-voice/\n2. **Verify** euiui existence\n3. **Audit** factory-dashboard features\n4. **Document** platform-monorepo structure\n5. **Create** component inventory from all sources\n\n---\n\n**Last Updated**: 2026-03-11 21:25\n**Status**: Audit complete - 5/6 projects found\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/PROJECT_AUDIT_COMPLETE.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":4776,"output":1221,"cacheRead":65536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71533,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773249923410}}
