 (to be replaced)\n- auth-proxy\n- shadi-v2\n- app-template\n- Packages\n\n**Tech Stack**:\n- Bun (runtime)\n- Biome (linter)\n- TypeScript\n- Multi-app monorepo\n\n---\n\n## вқҢ Projects Out of Scope (For Now)\n\n- вқҢ xmad (in ignore/) - Skip\n- вқҢ xmad-ai-voice (in ignore/) - Skip\n- вқҢ xmad-ecosystem - Skip\n- вқҢ voice-microservices - Already audited\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ӣ Three-Phase Plan (Refined)\n\n### Phase 1: xmad-control-center (Temp)\n**Duration**: 2 weeks\n**Goal**: Prototype, brainstorm, organize features\n\n**Tasks**:\n- [ ] Copy Nova files to XMAD\n- [ ] Build task tracker\n- [ ] Add notes/calendar\n- [ ] Test OpenClaw integration\n- [ ] Test Guardian integration\n- [ ] Document all features\n- [ ] Create component inventory\n\n### Phase 2: Next.js Dashboard (Standalone)\n**Duration**: 4 weeks\n**Tech**: Next.js 15 + Bun + Biome + Tailwind\n**Source**: [UI library] + XMAD features\n**Goal**: Production-ready dashboard\n\n**Tasks**:\n- [ ] Setup Next.js project\n- [ ] Audit UI component library\n- [ ] Migrate components\n- [ ] Build all features\n- [ ] Test everything\n\n### Phase 3: Platform Monorepo Integration\n**Duration**: 6 weeks\n**Goal**: Replace factory-dashboard\n**Tasks**:\n- [ ] Integrate into monorepo\n- [ ] Multi-tenant support\n- [ ] Agent automation\n- [ ] Deploy to production\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”Қ Next Immediate Action\n\n**Find the UI Component Library**:\n\n```bash\n# List Desktop files\nls -la ~/Desktop/\n\n# Search for UI library\nfind ~/Desktop -maxdepth 2 -type d -iname \"*eui*\"\nfind ~/Desktop -maxdepth 2 -type d -iname \"*glass*\"\nfind ~/Desktop -maxdepth 2 -type d -iname \"*liquid*\"\n```\n\n**Expected Name**: Something like \"euiui\", \"glass-ui\", \"liquid-ui\", etc.\n\n---\n\n**Last Updated**: 2026-03-11 21:30\n**Status**: Searching for UI component library\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/FOCUSED_SCOPE.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":5663,"output