{"type":"message","id":"30ed306b","parentId":"d1ae80bd","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:29:31.543Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d49c6b78ccb64def8d1362e1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"name\": \"ein-ui\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"authors\": [\n    \"Ehsan Ghaffar <ghafari.5000@gmail.com>\"\n  ],\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"next build\",\n    \"dev\": \"next dev\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint .\",\n    \"lint:fix\": \"eslint . --fix\",\n    \"start\": \"next start\",\n    \"analyze\": \"next experimental-analyze\",\n    \"registry:build\": \"shadcn build\",\n    \"registry:search\": \"shadcn search\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest\",\n    \"test:watch\": \"vitest --watch\",\n    \"test:coverage\": \"vitest --coverage\",\n    \"test:ui\": \"vitest --ui\"\n  },\n  \"keywords\": [],\n  \"author\": \"\",\n  \"license\": \"ISC\",\n  \"packageManager\": \"bun@1.3.10\",\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@radix-ui/react-accordion\": \"^1.2.12\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-alert-dialog\": \"^1.1.15\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-avatar\": \"^1.1.11\","}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":303,"aggregated":"{\n  \"name\": \"ein-ui\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"authors\": [\n    \"Ehsan Ghaffar <ghafari.5000@gmail.com>\"\n  ],\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"next build\",\n    \"dev\": \"next dev\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint .\",\n    \"lint:fix\": \"eslint . --fix\",\n    \"start\": \"next start\",\n    \"analyze\": \"next experimental-analyze\",\n    \"registry:build\": \"shadcn build\",\n    \"registry:search\": \"shadcn search\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest\",\n    \"test:watch\": \"vitest --watch\",\n    \"test:coverage\": \"vitest --coverage\",\n    \"test:ui\": \"vitest --ui\"\n  },\n  \"keywords\": [],\n  \"author\": \"\",\n  \"license\": \"ISC\",\n  \"packageManager\": \"bun@1.3.10\",\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@radix-ui/react-accordion\": \"^1.2.12\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-alert-dialog\": \"^1.1.15\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-avatar\": \"^1.1.11\",","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773250171536}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c6770f0","parentId":"30ed306b","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:29:31.869Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cb32214465e646ab9d46eac1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Ein UI вҖ” Liquid Glass Components (Shadcn Registry)\n\n[![Demo](https://img.shields.io/badge/demo-Demo%20Site-brightgreen)](https://ui.eindev.ir)\n[![Registry](https://img.shields.io/badge/registry-JSON-brightgreen?style=flat)](/r/registry.json)\n[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.0-blue?style=flat)](#key-features)\n[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-ISC-blue?style=flat)](/LICENCE)\n[![TypeScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/TypeScript-вң”-blue?style=flat)](https://www.typescriptlang.org/)\n[![Next.js%2016](https://img.shields.io/badge/Next.js-v16-black?style=flat)](https://nextjs.org/docs)\n[![Tailwind%20CSS](https://img.shields.io/badge/Tailwind%20v4-%20%20-06B6D4?style=flat&logo=tailwindcss&logoColor=white)](https://tailwindcss.com/)\n\n<img src=\"public/screenshot.png\" alt=\"Next.js 16 Starter\"  style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 15px; max-width: 80%;\" />\n<br/>\n\nWelcome! Ein UI is a collection of beautiful, ready-made \"liquid glass\" components that you can preview, copy, and use in your website or app. This guide explains how to preview the components, get code snippets, and add a component to your project вҖ” no developer knowledge required.\n\nвң… Great for: designers and frontend developers who want shareable, copy-and-paste UI components\nwith consistent design patterns and built-in accessibility.\n\n---\n\n## Key features\n\n- Collection of handcrafted, accessible components built on top of Radix UI primitives and\n  Tailwind CSS v4 (TypeScript + React 19).\n- Components are distributed using the shadcn registry format вҖ” components are easy to install\n  into other projects using the `shadcn` CLI.\n- Built-in documentation site and component previews (Next.js 16 + app router)\n- Example page templates / blocks (e.g., Admin Panel) to showcase layout patterns.\n- Zod validation examples and server/client component patterns for modern full-stack apps.\n\n---\n\n## Quick links\n\n- **Preview docs**: [Live preview](https://ui.eindev.ir)\n- **Registry JSON**: [Registry JSON](/r/registry.json)\n- **Try components**: For details, see `app/docs/components/*`\n\n---\n\n## Get started (local development)\n\nRequirements: Node.js 20+ (recommended), pnpm (optional but used in this repo), or npm/yarn.\n\n1. Clone the repo\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/ehsanghaffar/ein-ui.git\ncd ein-ui-shadcn-register\n```"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":324,"aggregated":"# Ein UI вҖ” Liquid Glass Components (Shadcn Registry)\n\n[![Demo](https://img.shields.io/badge/demo-Demo%20Site-brightgreen)](https://ui.eindev.ir)\n[![Registry](https://img.shields.io/badge/registry-JSON-brightgreen?style=flat)](/r/registry.json)\n[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.0-blue?style=flat)](#key-features)\n[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-ISC-blue?style=flat)](/LICENCE)\n[![TypeScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/TypeScript-вң”-blue?style=flat)](https://www.typescriptlang.org/)\n[![Next.js%2016](https://img.shields.io/badge/Next.js-v16-black?style=flat)](https://nextjs.org/docs)\n[![Tailwind%20CSS](https://img.shields.io/badge/Tailwind%20v4-%20%20-06B6D4?style=flat&logo=tailwindcss&logoColor=white)](https://tailwindcss.com/)\n\n<img src=\"public/screenshot.png\" alt=\"Next.js 16 Starter\"  style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 15px; max-width: 80%;\" />\n<br/>\n\nWelcome! Ein UI is a collection of beautiful, ready-made \"liquid glass\" components that you can preview, copy, and use in your website or app. This guide explains how to preview the components, get code snippets, and add a component to your project вҖ” no developer knowledge required.\n\nвң… Great for: designers and frontend developers who want shareable, copy-and-paste UI components\nwith consistent design patterns and built-in accessibility.\n\n---\n\n## Key features\n\n- Collection of handcrafted, accessible components built on top of Radix UI primitives and\n  Tailwind CSS v4 (TypeScript + React 19).\n- Components are distributed using the shadcn registry format вҖ” components are easy to install\n  into other projects using the `shadcn` CLI.\n- Built-in documentation site and component previews (Next.js 16 + app router)\n- Example page templates / blocks (e.g., Admin Panel) to showcase layout patterns.\n- Zod validation examples and server/client component patterns for modern full-stack apps.\n\n---\n\n## Quick links\n\n- **Preview docs**: [Live preview](https://ui.eindev.ir)\n- **Registry JSON**: [Registry JSON](/r/registry.json)\n- **Try components**: For details, see `app/docs/components/*`\n\n---\n\n## Get started (local development)\n\nRequirements: Node.js 20+ (recommended), pnpm (optional but used in this repo), or npm/yarn.\n\n1. Clone the repo\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/ehsanghaffar/ein-ui.git\ncd ein-ui-shadcn-register\n```","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773250171862}}
{"type":"message","id":"72f5338e","parentId":"1c6770f0","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:29:38.592Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n# рҹҺү **FOUND IT! ein-ui - Liquid Glass Components!**\n\n## вң… **Perfect UI Library Found!**\n\n**Project**: **ein-ui**\n**Location**: `~/Desktop/ein-ui/`\n**Style**: **Liquid Glass Components** (exactly what you wanted!)\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ұ **ein-ui Details**\n\n### Tech Stack\n- вң… Next.js 16\n- вң… React 19\n- вң… TypeScript\n- вң… Tailwind CSS v4\n- вң… Radix UI primitives\n- вң… Shadcn registry format\n- вң… Bun (package manager)\n\n### Features\n- рҹҺЁ **Liquid glass design** (glassmorphism)\n- рҹ“Ұ **Copy-paste components** (shadcn CLI)\n- рҹ“– **Built-in documentation**\n- рҹ–јпёҸ **Component previews**\n- рҹ”§ **Example page templates**\n- вҷҝ **Accessible components**\n- вң… **Zod validation**\n\n### Registry\n- **Format**: Shadcn registry\n- **Install with**: `shadcn CLI`\n- **Live Demo**: https://ui.eindev.ir\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҜ **Updated Three-Phase Plan**\n\n### Phase 1: xmad-control-center (Temp)\n**Duration**: 2 weeks\n**Current project - prototype & brainstorm**\n\n### Phase 2: Next.js Dashboard\n**Duration**: 4 weeks\n**Tech**: Next.js 15 + Bun + Biome + Tailwind\n**Components**: **From ein-ui** (liquid glass style!)\n**Source**: ein-ui + current XMAD features\n\n### Phase 3: Platform Monorepo\n**Duration**: 6 weeks\n**Integration**: Replace factory-dashboard\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ғ **Final Project List**\n\n| Project | Purpose | Status |\n|---------|---------|--------|\n| вң… **xmad-control-center** | Current prototype | Phase 1 |\n| вң… **ein-ui** | UI components (liquid glass) | Phase 2 source |\n| вң… **platform-monorepo** | Final destination | Phase 3 |\n\n---\n\n## рҹҡҖ **Ready to Build!**\n\n**All pieces identified**:\n1. вң… Current XMAD (prototype)\n2. вң… ein-ui (liquid glass components)\n3. вң… Platform monorepo (final home)\n\n**Next**: Start Phase 1 with current XMAD!\n\n**Shall I begin building the prototype features?**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":1809,"output":509,"cacheRead":75648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77966,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773250171867}}
