{"type":"message","id":"bd9f3b35","parentId":"5e8a6450","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:35:03.979Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"2A4B558E4986F447434C\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+971504042000\",\n  \"sender\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant (+971504042000)\",\n  \"id\": \"+971504042000\",\n  \"name\": \"Golden Cruise Restaurant\",\n  \"e164\": \"+971504042000\"\n}\n```\n\nYes. Start the agents or guardians so they can refactor xmad control center. \nThen make all what we have there as a modular to match the monirepo for easy move later.\nOrganize the side menu and dashboard fully redesign it to somthing cover all what we need \nAdd all needed tasks and plans and what we already discussed for the project from control center to nextjs tk monirepo"}],"timestamp":1773250503967}}
{"type":"message","id":"d28d56a5","parentId":"bd9f3b35","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:35:24.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Let me deploy Guardian to refactor XMAD Control Center with agents:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1cfdf57b81184b22b6b46ace","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# рҹӨ– Guardian Task - XMAD Control Center Refactoring\n\n**Task**: Complete refactoring of xmad-control-center to modular, monorepo-ready structure\n\n**Date**: 2026-03-11 21:35\n**Mode**: Execute (apply all changes)\n**Target**: ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҜ Objectives\n\n1. **Modularize structure** - Make everything reusable components\n2. **Redesign dashboard** - Complete redesign with proper sections\n3. **Reorganize side menu** - Logical navigation structure\n4. **Add all features** - Everything we discussed\n5. **Monorepo-ready** - Easy migration to platform-monorepo\n6. **Task tracking** - Add all tasks and plans\n7. **Documentation** - Full roadmap and progress tracking\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“Ӣ Required Changes\n\n### 1. Structure Refactoring\n```\nxmad-control-center/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ components/          # Modular components\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ dashboard/       # Dashboard widgets\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ openclaw/        # OpenClaw controls\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ guardian/        # Guardian controls\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tenants/         # Tenant management\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ projects/        # Project management\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ voice/           # Voice services\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ workspace/       # Nova's workspace\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ shared/          # Shared UI components\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ pages/              # Route pages\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ api/                # API routes\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ lib/                # Utilities\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ styles/             # Global styles\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ docs/               # Documentation\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ tasks/              # Task tracking\nв””в”Җв”Җ config/             # Configurations\n```\n\n### 2. Dashboard Redesign\n**Sections needed**:\n- Overview/Home (system status, quick actions)\n- OpenClaw Control (start/stop, logs, memory, config)\n- Guardian Orchestrator (tasks, agents, results)\n- Tenant Management (list, create, settings)\n- Project Management (list, create, templates, deploy)\n- Voice Services Hub (STT/TTS providers, testing)\n- Workspace (Nova's persona, memory, tasks, notes, calendar)\n- Documentation (guides, API docs, tutorials)\n- Settings (API keys, preferences, system config)\n- Notifications (alerts, updates)\n- Task Tracker (roadmap, progress, todos)\n\n### 3. Side Menu Structure\n```\nрҹ“Ҡ Dashboard\n  рҹҸ  Overview\n  рҹ“Ҳ Metrics\n\nрҹӨ– OpenClaw\n  в–¶пёҸ Controls\n  рҹ“Ҡ Monitor\n  рҹ“қ Logs\n  рҹ§  Brain View\n  вҡҷпёҸ Config\n\nрҹӣЎпёҸ Guardian\n  рҹ“Ӣ Submit Task\n  рҹ”§ Agent Status\n  рҹ“Ҡ Progress\n  рҹ“„ Results\n\nрҹҸў Tenants\n  рҹ“Ӯ List Tenants\n  вһ• Create Tenant\n  вҡҷпёҸ Settings\n\nрҹ“Ұ Projects\n  рҹ“Ӯ List Projects\n  вһ• Create Project\n  рҹ“Ұ Templates\n  рҹҡҖ Deploy\n\nрҹҺӨ Voice\n  рҹҺӨ STT Providers\n  рҹ”Ҡ TTS Providers\n  рҹ§Ә Test Voice\n  вҡҷпёҸ Settings\n\nрҹ’ј Workspace\n  рҹ‘Ө Persona (SOUL)\n  рҹ§  Memory\n  рҹ“Ӣ Tasks\n  рҹ“қ Notes\n  рҹ“… Calendar\n\nрҹ“ҡ Documentation\n  рҹ“– Guides\n  рҹ”§ API Docs\n  рҹҺ“ Tutorials\n\nрҹ”” Notifications\n  рҹ”” Alerts\n  рҹ“ў Updates\n\nвҡҷпёҸ Settings\n  рҹ”‘ API Keys\n  рҹҺЁ Preferences\n  рҹ”§ System\n\nрҹ“Ҡ Progress\n  рҹ—әпёҸ Roadmap\n  рҹ“Ҳ Status\n```\n\n### 4. Features to Add\n- [ ] Complete task tracking system\n- [ ] Roadmap viewer (3 phases)\n- [ ] Progress indicators\n- [ ] Nova's files (SOUL, MEMORY, IDENTITY, USER)\n- [ ] Notes system\n- [ ] Calendar integration\n- [ ] Notification center\n- [ ] Enhanced chat (WhatsApp/Direct)\n- [ ] Voice controls (STT/TTS)\n- [ ] Backup/Restore\n- [ ] All documentation in one place\n\n### 5. Monorepo Compatibility\n- Modular component structure\n- Clear dependencies\n- API route separation\n- Config-based routing\n- Easy to extract to monorepo/apps/\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺЁ Design Requirements\n\n**Style**: Prepare for ein-ui liquid glass components\n- Glassmorphism cards\n- Smooth animations\n- Dark/light mode ready\n- Responsive design\n- Modern UI patterns\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“қ Tasks to Track\n\n### Phase 1: Current XMAD (2 weeks)\n- [ ] Refactor structure\n- [ ] Redesign dashboard\n- [ ] Add all sections\n- [ ] Implement task tracking\n- [ ] Add Nova files\n- [ ] Test all features\n- [ ] Document everything\n\n### Phase 2: Next.js Dashboard (4 weeks)\n- [ ] Setup Next.js 15 + Bun + Biome\n- [ ] Integrate ein-ui components\n- [ ] Migrate all features\n- [ ] Add authentication\n- [ ] Deploy standalone\n\n### Phase 3: Monorepo (6 weeks)\n- [ ] Move to platform-monorepo/apps/\n- [ ] Replace factory-dashboard\n- [ ] Multi-tenant support\n- [ ] Agent automation\n- [ ] Production deploy\n\n---\n\n## вң… Success Criteria\n\n1. **Modular Structure** - Everything is reusable components\n2. **Complete Redesign** - Professional dashboard with all sections\n3. **Organized Navigation** - Logical menu structure\n4. **Task Tracking** - All tasks and plans visible\n5. **Monorepo-Ready** - Easy to move to platform-monorepo\n6. **Fully Functional** - All features working\n7. **Well Documented** - Clear docs and progress tracking\n\n---\n\n**Priority**: HIGH\n**Complexity**: HIGH (multi-file refactoring)\n**Estimated Time**: 2-3 hours (with Guardian agents)\n**Risk Level**: MEDIUM (backup exists)\n\n---\n\n## рҹҡҖ Execute with Guardian\n\n**Command**:\n```bash\ncd ~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026\n./claude-safe --execute \"Refactor xmad-control-center to modular structure with complete dashboard redesign, organized navigation, all features added, and monorepo-ready architecture\" ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/\n```\n\n**Expected Output**:\n- Refactored component structure\n- Redesigned dashboard\n- Organized side menu\n- All features implemented\n- Task tracking system\n- Monorepo-compatible code\n\n---\n\n**Ready to execute!**\n","path":"/Users/ahma