rd Sections\n- рҹҸ  **Home** - System overview\n- рҹӨ– **OpenClaw** - Start/stop, logs, memory, config\n- рҹӣЎпёҸ **Guardian** - Task submission, agent status\n- рҹ“Ұ **Tenants** - Tenant management\n- рҹ“Ғ **Projects** - Project management\n- рҹҺӨ **Voice** - Voice services hub\n- рҹ’ј **Workspace** - Nova's persona, memory, tasks\n- рҹ“ҡ **Docs** - Documentation\n- вҡҷпёҸ **Settings** - API keys, preferences\n\n### API Endpoints\n- `/api/openclaw/<action>` - OpenClaw control\n- `/api/guardian/<action>` - Guardian control\n- `/api/tailscale/<action>` - Tailscale VPN\n- `/api/ssh/<action>` - SSH server\n- `/api/script/<name>` - Run scripts\n- `/api/file/read` - Read files\n- `/api/logs/read` - Read logs\n\n---\n\n## рҹ”§ Control Commands\n\n### Start Dashboard\n```bash\ncd ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center\n./start-dashboard.sh\n```\n\n### Stop Dashboard\n```bash\nlsof -ti :8765 | xargs kill -9\n```\n\n### Check Status\n```bash\nlsof -i :8765\n```\n\n---\n\n## рҹ“ұ What's Working\n\nвң… Dashboard UI loaded\nвң… OpenClaw monitoring (527MB RAM)\nвң… WhatsApp status\nвң… All API endpoints\nвң… Legacy server running\n\n---\n\n## рҹҺҜ Next Steps\n\nThe dashboard is running with the **legacy UI** (original HTML/JS).\n\n**To see the new Vue 3 dashboard** (modular version):\n1. Install Vue dependencies (pending)\n2. Start Vite dev server\n3. Access at same port\n\n**Current Status**: Legacy server running, ready for use! рҹҺү\n\n---\n\n**Last Updated**: 2026-03-11 22:05\n**Dashboard**: рҹҹў ONLINE\n**Access**: http://192.168.70.83:8765\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/DASHBOARD_RUNNING.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":1838,"output":861,"cacheRead":97536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100235,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773252186430}}
