{"type":"message","id":"f333f7b7","parentId":"cbc762ff","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:08:20.155Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n# рҹӣ пёҸ **COMPLETE TOOLS INVENTORY**\n\n## **19 Total Tools Found & Documented!**\n\n### рҹ”җ **Network & VPN** (2 tools)\n1. **SSH Manager** - Start/stop SSH server, manage keys\n2. **Tailscale VPN** - Connect VPN, check status (IP: 100.121.254.21)\n\n### рҹӨ– **AI & Automation** (2 tools)\n3. **OpenClaw Controller** - Start/stop, monitor, logs (527MB running)\n4. **Guardian Orchestrator** - Multi-agent coding (suggest/execute/dry-run modes)\n\n### рҹ“Ҡ **Monitoring** (3 tools)\n5. **System Monitor** - CPU, RAM, disk stats\n6. **Watchdog** - Auto-restart OpenClaw (available, not running)\n7. **Performance Logger** - Structured logging, baselines\n\n### вҡЎ **Optimization** (1 tool)\n8. **PC Optimizer** - Kill processes, free RAM (from OPTIMIZE_PC.sh)\n\n### рҹ’ҫ **Backup** (1 tool)\n9. **Backup Manager** - Create/restore backups\n\n### рҹҺӨ **Voice** (1 tool)\n10. **Voice Manager** - Start/stop voice services (SenseVoice, Chatterbox, Kokoro)\n\n### рҹ’¬ **Integration Bots** (3 tools)\n11. **Discord Voice Bot**\n12. **Slack Voice Bot**\n13. **Teams Voice Bot**\n\n### рҹ“қ **Productivity** (3 tools)\n14. **Task Tracker** - Roadmap, phases, progress\n15. **Notes System** - (Planned)\n16. **Calendar** - (Planned)\n\n### рҹ”” **Other** (3 tools)\n17. **Notification Center** - Alerts, updates\n18. **API Keys Manager** - SSOT, Infisical, Keychain (13+ keys)\n19. **Memory Editor** - View/edit OpenClaw memory\n\n---\n\n**Full inventory created**: `COMPLETE_TOOLS_INVENTORY.md` вң…\n\n**All 19 tools documented with features, API endpoints, and usage!**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":101544,"output":455,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103151,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":177325