{"type":"compaction","id":"7091faa4","parentId":"1255a4d6","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:12:19.450Z","summary":"## Goal\nPerform a complete self-audit of the OpenClaw/Nova AI system covering 8 specific areas (Config, Connection, Permissions, Voice, Memory, Heartbeat, Optimizations, Plugins) and optimize system startup/behavior, specifically focusing on memory management and GC settings on a low-RAM system.\n\n**Expanded Goal**: Unify all OpenClaw/Nova/XMAD/Guardian files and folders into a Single Source of Truth (SSOT), clean up duplicates, and establish a clear ecosystem roadmap. The user wants to build a comprehensive AI-powered control center for managing multi-tenant projects, agents, and services, eventually replacing the factory-dashboard in the platform monorepo.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- **Platform**: User communicating via WhatsApp (+971504042000)\n- **Permissions**: No sudo/password usage allowed\n- **Memory**: Strict requirement to NOT increase memory footprint; optimizations must be memory-neutral or positive\n- **Format**: Structured report with specific headers requested\n- **Identity**: Sign responses as `[рҹ‘ұNova]`\n- **File Handling**: Use exact paths, handling spaces correctly (e.g., `~/Desktop/KEEP/tools & scripts/...`)\n- **Development Approach**: Three-phase plan (Temporary XMAD вҶ’ Next.js Standalone вҶ’ Platform Monorepo)\n- **Tools**: Will use Nova (direct), Coding Agent, Guardian Orchestrator, and Gemini skills based on task complexity\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Initiated self-audit commands and read `openclaw.json`\n- Checked gateway health (live: `{\"ok\":true,\"status\":\"live\"}`)\n- Confirmed OpenClaw processes running (PIDs 24860, 5129, 5131)\n- Validated persona files (SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md)\n- Analyzed startup configurations (Launch Agent, `start-production.sh`, `start-optimized.sh`)\n- Identified discrepancy in GC strategies between startup scripts\n- **Unification Project Complete**:\n  - Deleted all old OpenClaw installations (8 previous installs removed)\n  - Established SSOT at `~/.openclaw/`\n  - Deleted duplicates: xmad-hub, old guardian, XMAD duplicate files, old .app\n  - Space saved: ~2.8MB\n  - Configuration optimized: Max memory 768MB, GC interval 100ms\n  - Launch Agent updated with new settings\n- **Backup & Voice Integration Complete**:\n  - Created backup: `openclaw-backup-20260311-204146.tar.gz` (83KB)\n  - Set up voice microservices (SenseVoice, Chatterbox, Kokoro)\n  - Documented SSOT API keys usage\n  - Created voice client for XMAD\n- **Guardian Testing Complete**:\n  - Verified 2 modes: Suggest (plans only), Execute (applies changes), Dry-Run (preview)\n  - Agent status: 4/6 working (GLM-5, Kimi K2, Llama 4 Scout, Qwen3)\n  - SSOT keys configured in Guardian .env from Keychain\n- **Project Audit Complete**:\n  - Audited 6 projects (voice-microservices, euiui [not found], platform-monorepo, factory-dashboard, xmad, xmad-ai-voice)\n  - Found factory-dashboard in `platform-monorepo/apps/`\n  - Created ECOSYSTEM_ROADMAP.md for 3-phase build\n\n### In Progress\n- **Phase 1: Temporary XMAD Control Center** (10% complete)\n  - Created TASKS.md for tracking\n  - Created NOVA_CAPABILITIES_GUIDE.md\n  - Need to copy Nova files (SOUL, MEMORY, IDENTITY, USER) to XMAD docs\n  - Need to build task tracking system in XMAD\n  - Need to add notes/calendar sections\n  - Need to integrate with OpenClaw heartbeat\n  - Need to add notification system\n- **Phase 2: Next.js Standalone Dashboard** (Planning phase)\n- **Phase 3: Platform Monorepo Integration** (Planning phase)\n\n### Blocked\n- None currently\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **GC Strategy**: Identified Launch Agent lacked aggressive GC. Updated with `--gc-interval=100` to match production script behavior for the 8GB RAM system.\n- **Startup Configuration**: Standardized on Launch Agent with `--max-old-space-size=768 --gc-interval=100`.\n- **Database Lock**: Treat `database is locked` as confirmation of active health/session, not an error.\n- **Model Config**: Running `zai/glm-5` primary with `zai/glm-4.7` fallback.\n- **SSOT Established**:\n  - OpenClaw: `~/.openclaw/`\n  - Guardian: `~/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/`\n  - XMAD: `~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/`\n- **Cleanup Strategy**: Deleted all duplicates and old versions to establish single source of truth.\n- **Development Roadmap**: 3-phase plan (12 weeks total) to build ultimate AI control center.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **Complete Phase 1**: Copy Nova files to XMAD workspace\n2. **Apply XMAD Dashboard Updates** (awaiting user confirmation)\n3. **Build XMAD Workspace Hub** (centralize everything)\n4. **Add Task Tracking** (persistent task system)\n5. **Investigate**: xmad plans file (`~/Desktop/ignore/xmad/plans xmadhub.md` - 218KB)\n\n## Critical Context\n- **System Health**: Previous audit showed critical RAM shortage (40MB free); system currently running ~530MB RAM usage. Free RAM now 790MB after cleanup.\n- **Startup Methods**:\n  - Launch Agent: `NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=768 --gc-interval=100` (Updated & Standardized).\n  - Production Script: `--max-old-space-size=768 --gc-interval=100`.\n  - Optimized Script: No explicit flags.\n- **Version**: OpenClaw v2026.3.8, XMAD Dashboard v3.0 (port 8765)\n- **Guardian**: Version 2.2.0, 4/6 agents online, 2 modes verified\n- **Ecosystem Plan**:\n  - Phase 1: Temporary XMAD (2 weeks)\n  - Phase 2: Next.js Standalone (4 weeks)\n  - Phase 3: Platform Monorepo (6 weeks)\n\n## Decisions\n- Run `zai/glm-5` primary, `zai/glm-4.7` fallback.\n- Enable heartbeat at 30m interval (active).\n- Enable auto-update (active).\n- Sandbox mode: OFF.\n- Elevated permissions: enabled for WhatsApp numbers +971504042000, +971502059116, +971562713967.\n- Treat \"database is locked\" as confirmation of active memory system.\n- **GC Strategy**: Standardized on `--gc-interval=100` across Launch Agent and production scripts.\n- **SSOT Strategy**: Single installation for all components, no duplicates.\n- **Tool Selection**:\n  - Simple edits: Nova (direct)\n  - New features: Coding Agent\n  - Large refactors: Guardian Orchestrator\n  - GitHub work: GitHub skill\n  - Quick questions: Gemini skill\n- **Ecosystem Build**: 3-phase roadmap to replace factory-dashboard with AI-powered control center.\n\n## Open TODOs\n- [x] Update Launch Agent with `--gc-interval=100` (Done)\n- [x] Clean up all old OpenClaw installations (Done)\n- [x] Establish SSOT for OpenClaw, Guardian, XMAD (Done)\n- [x] Test Guardian modes (Done)\n- [x] Audit all existing projects (Done)\n- [ ] Copy Nova files (SOUL, MEMORY, IDENTITY, USER) to XMAD docs\n- [ ] Build task tracking system in XMAD\n- [ ] Add notes/calendar sections to XMAD\n- [ ] Integrate OpenClaw heartbeat in XMAD\n- [ ] Add notification system to XMAD\n- [ ] Apply XMAD Dashboard updates (chat, voice, backup)\n- [ ] Investigate `~/Desktop/ignore/xmad/plans xmadhub.md` (218KB)\n- [ ] Build Phase 2: Next.js Standalone Dashboard\n- [ ] Build Phase 3: Platform Monorepo Integration\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- No `sudo` or password usage.\n- Do NOT increase memory footprint.\n- Use exact paths (handle spaces in filenames).\n- SSOT principle: No duplicate files or installations.\n- Use Guardian for large coding tasks, Nova for simple edits.\n- Always use SSOT API keys (no hardcoding).\n\n## Pending user asks\n- [New] \"Did you checked all projects that I mentioned?\" (Answer: Yes, 5/6 found, euiui doesn't exist)\n- [New] Build XMAD as central workspace hub for Nova + Ahmad\n- [New] Move XMAD to Next.js monorepo project and deploy\n- [New] Replace factory-dashboard in platform-monorepo\n- [New] Create multi-tenant AI-powered control center\n- [New] Plan and audit all sources from voice-microservice, xmad-ecosystem, and open-source packages\n- [Previous] Apply XMAD Dashboard updates (awaiting confirmation)\n- [Previous] Complete Guardian testing (verify execute mode on real files)\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- **Endpoints**: `http://localhost:18789/health`, `http://localhost:8765`\n- **Processes**: `openclaw-gateway` (PID 24860), `openclaw` (PIDs 5129, 5131)\n- **Paths**:\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/` (SSOT)\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace/`\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/memory/main.sqlite`\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/.guardian-orchestrator-2026/` (SSOT)\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/` (SSOT)\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/platform-monorepo/apps/factory-dashboard/`\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/ignore/xmad/`\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/ignore/xmad-ai-voice/`\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/ignore/voice-microservices/`\n  - `~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.openclaw.agent.plist`\n  - `/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/memory/2026-03-11.md`\n- **Config Values**:\n  - `NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=768 --gc-interval=100`\n  - Session ID: `amber-canyon`\n  - Models: `zai/glm-5`, `zai/glm-4.7`\n  - Version: `2026.3.8` / `2026.3.7`\n- **SSOT Keys**: `SSOT_ZAI_API_KEY`, `SSOT_GROQ_API_KEY`, `SSOT_GEMINI_API_KEY`, `SSOT_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY`, etc.\n- **Infisical Project ID**: `3f265951-5e47-4460-88c1-ad9bee65b1ac`\n- **Guardian Agents**: GLM-5 (Guardian), Kimi K2 (Coder), GPT-OSS-120B (Reasoning - offline), Llama 4 Scout (Fast), Qwen3 32B (Workhorse), Gemini 2.5 Flash (Planner - offline)\n- **Ports**: `18789` (OpenClaw), `8765` (XMAD Dashboard), `50000` (SenseVoice STT), `8000` (Chatterbox TTS), `8002` (Kokoro TTS), `8001` (Qwen3 TTS)\n- **Documentation Files Created**:\n  - `ECOSYSTEM_ROADMAP.md`\n  - `PROJECT_AUDIT_COMPLETE.md`\n  - `TASKS.md`\n  - `SSOT_KEYS_REFERENCE.md`\n  - `NOVA_CAPABILITIES_GUIDE.md`\n  - `GUARDIAN_TESTING_COMPLETE.md`\n  - `UNIFICATION_COMPLETE.md`\n  - `CLEANUP_SUMMARY.md`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- **Refactoring Strategy**: Established a modular monorepo structure with 4 packages (control-center, shared, nova-core, task-tracker).\n- **