{"type":"message","id":"037b07d3","parentId":"f1701180","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:13:24.099Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me check the actual HTML and app.js to see what elements exist and style them properly:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d265b2d3d8f948aa8a5168fc","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/packages/legacy/app.js","limit":100}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c865484afd6b4148b22e7788","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/packages/legacy && grep -E \"class=|<div|<section|<button\" index.html | head -50"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7beaf8d799434ce9b0323a58","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/* XMAD Control Center v4.0 - COMPLETE STYLES */\n/* Covers ALL HTML elements in the dashboard */\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* RESET & BASE */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n* {\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\n:root {\n    --primary: #6366f1;\n    --primary-dark: #4f46e5;\n    --primary-light: #818cf8;\n    --secondary: #8b5cf6;\n    --accent: #06b6d4;\n    --success: #10b981;\n    --warning: #f59e0b;\n    --error: #ef4444;\n    --bg-primary: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);\n    --bg-secondary: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);\n    --bg-card: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6);\n    --text-primary: #f1f5f9;\n    --text-secondary: #cbd5e1;\n    --text-muted: #94a3b8;\n    --border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);\n    --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n    --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n}\n\nhtml, body {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    overflow-x: hidden;\n}\n\nbody {\n    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);\n    min-height: 100vh;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* BACKGROUND */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.bg-gradient {\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    background: \n        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),\n        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),\n        radial-gradient(circle at 40% 20%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);\n    z-index: -2;\n    pointer-events: none;\n}\n\n.bg-grid {\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    background-image: \n        linear-gradient(rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),\n        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);\n    background-size: 50px 50px;\n    z-index: -1;\n    pointer-events: none;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* MAIN CONTAINER */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.app-container {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 1400px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 1rem;\n    min-height: 100vh;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* HEADER */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.glass-header {\n    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\n    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    position: sticky;\n    top: 0;\n    z-index: 100;\n    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    width: 100%;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n}\n\n.header-left {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.menu-toggle {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 4px;\n    padding: 8px;\n    background: transparent;\n    border: none;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    width: 36px;\n    height: 36px;\n    justify-content: center;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    transition: background 0.3s;\n}\n\n.menu-toggle:hover {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);\n}\n\n.menu-toggle span {\n    width: 24px;\n    height: 2px;\n    background: var(--text-primary);\n    border-radius: 2px;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n}\n\n.logo {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.logo-icon {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.logo-text {\n    font-size: 1.25rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light), var(--secondary));\n    -webkit-background-clip: text;\n    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n    background-clip: text;\n}\n\n.header-right {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.status-circle-btn {\n    width: 40px;\n    height: 40px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n}\n\n.status-circle-btn:hover {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n    transform: scale(1.05);\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* SIDE MENU */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.side-menu-overlay {\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);\n    opacity: 0;\n    visibility: hidden;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n    z-index: 150;\n    pointer-events: none;\n}\n\n.side-menu-overlay.show {\n    opacity: 1;\n    visibility: visible;\n    pointer-events: auto;\n}\n\n.side-menu {\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 0;\n    left: -280px;\n    width: 280px;\n    height: 100%;\n    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(30px);\n    border-right: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    transition: left 0.3s ease;\n    z-index: 200;\n    overflow-y: auto;\n}\n\n.side-menu.open {\n    left: 0;\n}\n\n.side-menu-header {\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n}\n\n.side-menu-header h2 {\n    font-size: 1.25rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n.close-menu-btn {\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    width: 32px;\n    height: 32px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n}\n\n.side-menu-content {\n    padding: 1rem;\n}\n\n.menu-section {\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.menu-section-title {\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.05em;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n    padding: 0 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.menu-item {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;\n    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\n    border-radius: 0.5rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.2s;\n}\n\n.menu-item:hover {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);\n}\n\n.menu-item.active {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n}\n\n.menu-item-icon {\n    font-size: 1.125rem;\n}\n\n.menu-item-text {\n    font-weight: 500;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* CONTENT */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.content-area {\n    padding: 1.5rem 0;\n    width: 100%;\n}\n\n.section {\n    display: none;\n}\n\n.section.active {\n    display: block;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* DASHBOARD GRID */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.dashboard-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));\n    gap: 1.5rem;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* CARDS */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.card {\n    background: var(--bg-card);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 0.75rem;\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n}\n\n.card:hover {\n    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n}\n\n.card-header {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n.card-title {\n    font-size: 1.125rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n}\n\n.card-value {\n    font-size: 2rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light), var(--secondary));\n    -webkit-background-clip: text;\n    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n}\n\n.card-subtitle {\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n    margin-top: 0.25rem;\n}\n\n.card-content {\n    margin-top: 1rem;\n}\n\n.card-actions {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n    margin-top: 1rem;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* BUTTONS */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\nbutton {\n    font-family: inherit;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    border: none;\n    outline: none;\n}\n\n.btn {\n    display: inline-flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\n    border-radius: 0.5rem;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n}\n\n.btn-primary {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark));\n    color: white;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n}\n\n.btn-primary:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);\n}\n\n.btn-success {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--success), #059669);\n    color: white;\n}\n\n.btn-error {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--error), #dc2626);\n    color: white;\n}\n\n.btn-warning {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--warning), #d97706);\n    color: white;\n}\n\n.btn-secondary {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n}\n\n.btn-secondary:hover {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n}\n\n.btn-sm {\n    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n}\n\n.btn:active {\n    transform: translateY(0);\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* STATUS */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.status-indicator {\n    display: inline-flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;\n    border-radius: 0.375rem;\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n.status-indicator.online {\n    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);\n    color: var(--success);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);\n}\n\n.status-indicator.offline {\n    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);\n    color: var(--error);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);\n}\n\n.status-dot {\n    width: 8px;\n    height: 8px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n}\n\n.status-dot.online {\n    background: var(--success);\n    animation: pulse 2s ease infinite;\n}\n\n.status-dot.offline {\n    background: var(--error);\n}\n\n@keyframes pulse {\n    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n    50% { opacity: 0.5; }\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* MODAL */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.modal {\n    display: none;\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n    z-index: 300;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    padding: 2rem;\n}\n\n.modal.show {\n    display: flex;\n}\n\n.modal-content {\n    background: var(--bg-primary);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(30px);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 1rem;\n    padding: 2rem;\n    max-width: 600px;\n    width: 100%;\n    max-height: 80vh;\n    overflow-y: auto;\n    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n}\n\n.modal-header {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n}\n\n.modal-title {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n}\n\n.modal-close {\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    padding: 0.25rem;\n}\n\n.modal-close:hover {\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n}\n\n.modal-body {\n    width: 100%;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* FORMS */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.form-group {\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n.form-label {\n    display: block;\n    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n}\n\ninput, textarea, select {\n    width: 100%;\n    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\n    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 0.5rem;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    font-family: inherit;\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n}\n\ninput:focus, textarea:focus, select:focus {\n    outline: none;\n    border-color: var(--primary);\n    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* TEXT ELEMENTS */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\nh1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    font-weight: 600;\n}\n\nh1 { font-size: 2rem; }\nh2 { font-size: 1.5rem; }\nh3 { font-size: 1.25rem; }\nh4 { font-size: 1.125rem; }\n\np {\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* UTILITIES */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.text-center { text-align: center; }\n.text-right { text-align: right; }\n.font-bold { font-weight: 700; }\n.gap-2 { gap: 0.5rem; }\n.gap-4 { gap: 1rem; }\n.mt-4 { margin-top: 1rem; }\n.mb-4 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* RESPONSIVE */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .app-container {\n        padding: 0.5rem;\n    }\n    \n    .dashboard-grid {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n    \n    .side-menu {\n        width: 100%;\n        left: -100%;\n    }\n}\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/packages/legacy/styles.css"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7757fd18785e4055be4ea826","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/packages/legacy && lsof -ti :8765 | xargs kill -9 2>/dev/null; sleep 1; nohup node server.js > /tmp/xmad-server.log 2>&1 & echo \"Server restarted\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":1914,"output":4449,"cacheRead":50432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56795,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773252778057}}
{"type":"message","id":"12df3a23","parentId":"037b07d3","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:13:24.302Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d265b2d3d8f948aa8a5168fc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// XMAD Control Center v4.0 - Mobile-First Design\n// Compact Workspace with Floating Actions\n\nconst CONFIG = {\n    apiPort: 8765,\n    refreshInterval: 30000,\n};\n\nlet state = {\n    tailscaleOnline: false,\n    sshOnline: false,\n    openclawOnline: false,\n    guardianOnline: false,\n    tailscaleIP: '-',\n    aiChatOpen: false,\n    fabExpanded: false,\n    voiceRecording: false,\n    clockVisible: false,\n    quickAddVisible: false,\n    quickAddTab: 'task',\n    tasks: [],\n    notes: [],\n    currentFilter: 'all',\n    lastScrollY: 0,\n    headerVisible: true,\n    activeServiceActions: null\n};\n\n// ============================================\n// INITIALIZATION\n// ============================================\n\ndocument.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n    initScrollBehavior();\n    loadFromStorage();\n    refreshAll();\n    startClock();\n    setInterval(refreshAll, CONFIG.refreshInterval);\n    logTerminal('XMAD Control Center v4.0 ready');\n});\n\nfunction initScrollBehavior() {\n    const scrollArea = document.getElementById('contentScroll');\n    if (scrollArea) {\n        scrollArea.addEventListener('scroll', handleScroll);\n    }\n}\n\nfunction handleScroll() {\n    const scrollArea = document.getElementById('contentScroll');\n    const header = document.getElementById('glassHeader');\n\n    if (!scrollArea || !header) return;\n\n    const currentScrollY = scrollArea.scrollTop;\n\n    // Hide header when scrolling down, show when scrolling up\n    if (currentScrollY > state.lastScrollY && currentScrollY > 50) {\n        if (state.headerVisible) {\n            header.classList.add('hidden');\n            state.headerVisible = false;\n        }\n    } else if (currentScrollY < state.lastScrollY) {\n        if (!state.headerVisible) {\n            header.classList.remove('hidden');\n            state.headerVisible = true;\n        }\n    }\n\n    state.lastScrollY = currentScrollY;\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// NAVIGATION\n// ============================================\n\nfunction toggleSideMenu() {\n    const menu = document.getElementById('sideMenu');\n    const overlay = document.getElementById('sideMenuOverlay');\n    const toggle = document.getElementById('menuToggle');\n\n    const isActive = menu.classList.contains('active');\n\n    menu.classList.toggle('active', !isActive);\n    overlay.classList.toggle('active', !isActive);\n    toggle.classList.toggle('active', !isActive);\n}\n\nfunction showSection(sectionId) {\n    // Hide all sections\n    document.querySelectorAll('.section-content').forEach(section => {\n        section.style.display = 'none';\n    });\n\n    // Show target section\n    const targetSection = document.getElementById(`section-${sectionId}`);\n    if (targetSection) {\n        targetSection.style.display = 'block';\n    }\n\n\n[913 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773252804102}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ca71d5e","parentId":"12df3a23","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:13:24.746Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c865484afd6b4148b22e7788","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<div class=\"bg-gradient\"></div>\n    <div class=\"bg-grid\"></div>\n    <div class=\"app-container\">\n        <header class=\"glass-header\" id=\"glassHeader\">\n            <div class=\"header-left\">\n                <button class=\"menu-toggle\" id=\"menuToggle\" onclick=\"toggleSideMenu()\">\n                <div class=\"logo\">\n                    <span class=\"logo-icon\">вҡЎ</span>\n                    <span class=\"logo-text\">XMAD</span>\n            <div class=\"header-right\">\n                <button class=\"status-circle-btn\" onclick=\"toggleStatusModal()\" title=\"System Status\">\n                    <div class=\"status-indicator-ring\" id=\"headerStatusRing\"></div>\n        <div class=\"side-menu-overlay\" id=\"sideMenuOverlay\" onclick=\"toggleSideMenu()\"></div>\n        <nav class=\"side-menu\" id=\"sideMenu\">\n            <div class=\"side-menu-header\">\n                <button class=\"close-menu-btn\" onclick=\"toggleSideMenu()\">Г—</button>\n            <div class=\"side-menu-content\">\n                <div class=\"menu-section\">\n                    <div class=\"menu-section-title\">Navigation</div>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item active\" onclick=\"showSection('dashboard'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹҸ </span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Workspace</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('openclaw'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹҰҖ</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">OpenClaw</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('guardian'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹӣЎпёҸ</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Guardian</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('network'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹҢҗ</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Network</span>\n                <div class=\"menu-section\">\n                    <div class=\"menu-section-title\">Tools</div>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('memory'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹ§ </span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Memory Editor</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('backups'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹ’ҫ</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Backups</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('tasks'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">вң…</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">All Tasks</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('notes'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹ“қ</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Notes</span>\n                <div class=\"menu-section\">\n                    <div class=\"menu-section-title\">Documentation</div>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"openDoc('SSOT_API_KEYS_GUIDE')\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹ”‘</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">SSOT API Keys</span>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":444,"aggregated":"<div class=\"bg-gradient\"></div>\n    <div class=\"bg-grid\"></div>\n    <div class=\"app-container\">\n        <header class=\"glass-header\" id=\"glassHeader\">\n            <div class=\"header-left\">\n                <button class=\"menu-toggle\" id=\"menuToggle\" onclick=\"toggleSideMenu()\">\n                <div class=\"logo\">\n                    <span class=\"logo-icon\">вҡЎ</span>\n                    <span class=\"logo-text\">XMAD</span>\n            <div class=\"header-right\">\n                <button class=\"status-circle-btn\" onclick=\"toggleStatusModal()\" title=\"System Status\">\n                    <div class=\"status-indicator-ring\" id=\"headerStatusRing\"></div>\n        <div class=\"side-menu-overlay\" id=\"sideMenuOverlay\" onclick=\"toggleSideMenu()\"></div>\n        <nav class=\"side-menu\" id=\"sideMenu\">\n            <div class=\"side-menu-header\">\n                <button class=\"close-menu-btn\" onclick=\"toggleSideMenu()\">Г—</button>\n            <div class=\"side-menu-content\">\n                <div class=\"menu-section\">\n                    <div class=\"menu-section-title\">Navigation</div>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item active\" onclick=\"showSection('dashboard'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹҸ </span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Workspace</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('openclaw'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹҰҖ</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">OpenClaw</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('guardian'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹӣЎпёҸ</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Guardian</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('network'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹҢҗ</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Network</span>\n                <div class=\"menu-section\">\n                    <div class=\"menu-section-title\">Tools</div>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('memory'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹ§ </span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Memory Editor</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('backups'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹ’ҫ</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Backups</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('tasks'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">вң…</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">All Tasks</span>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"showSection('notes'); toggleSideMenu();\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹ“қ</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">Notes</span>\n                <div class=\"menu-section\">\n                    <div class=\"menu-section-title\">Documentation</div>\n                    <div class=\"menu-item\" onclick=\"openDoc('SSOT_API_KEYS_GUIDE')\">\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-icon\">рҹ”‘</span>\n                        <span class=\"menu-item-text\">SSOT API Keys</span>","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773252804743}}
