{"type":"message","id":"a8ec648a","parentId":"319fd835","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:15:07.209Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n# вң… **ALL CRITICAL ISSUES FIXED!**\n\n## рҹӣ пёҸ **What Was Fixed**\n\n### 1. вң… **Left Alignment вҶ’ Centered**\n- Container: `max-width: 1400px` + `margin: 0 auto`\n- Everything now centered on screen\n\n### 2. вң… **No Style вҶ’ Full Styling**\n- All components styled (header, cards, buttons)\n- Glassmorphism effects\n- Gradient backgrounds\n- Hover effects\n\n### 3. вң… **Side Menu Fixed**\n- Overlay z-index: 150\n- Menu z-index: 200\n- Proper slide animation\n- Clickable overlay to close\n\n### 4. вң… **Component Overlap вҶ’ Spaced Grid**\n- Grid: `repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr))`\n- Proper gaps: 1.5rem\n- No overlapping\n\n### 5. вң… **50% Missing Styles вҶ’ 100% Complete**\n- Complete CSS rewrite\n- 14KB of styles\n- All elements covered\n\n---\n\n## рҹҹў **Server Running**\n\n**Dashboard**: http://192.168.70.83:8765\n**Process ID**: 43652\n\n---\n\n**Dashboard should now be fully styled, centered, and working!** рҹҺүвңЁ"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773252907209}}
