{"type":"message","id":"ed86bded","parentId":"585ee6d6","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:20:04.488Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f7bd72cd64cc4c7081ddab07","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </section>\n\n                <!-- SSH Docs Section -->\n                <section id=\"section-sshdocs\" class=\"section-content\" style=\"display:none;\">\n                    <div class=\"ssh-docs-container\">\n                        <!-- Tabs -->\n                        <div class=\"docs-tabs\">\n                            <button class=\"docs-tab active\" onclick=\"showDocsTab('tailscale')\">рҹҢҗ Tailscale</button>\n                            <button class=\"docs-tab\" onclick=\"showDocsTab('termius')\">рҹ“ұ Termius</button>\n                            <button class=\"docs-tab\" onclick=\"showDocsTab('claudecli')\">рҹӨ– Claude CLI</button>\n                            <button class=\"docs-tab\" onclick=\"showDocsTab('snippets')\">рҹ“Ӣ Snippets</button>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <!-- Tailscale Tab -->\n                        <div id=\"docs-tailscale\" class=\"docs-tab-content active\">\n                            <div class=\"docs-card\">\n                                <h4>рҹҡҖ Quick Start</h4>\n                                <div class=\"code-block\">\n                                    <code onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">tailscale up --ssh</code>\n                                    <span class=\"copy-hint\">Click to copy</span>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"code-block\">\n                                    <code onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">tailscale status</code>\n                                    <span class=\"copy-hint\">Click to copy</span>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"docs-card\">\n                                <h4>рҹ”§ Essential Commands</h4>\n                                <div class=\"command-grid\">\n                                    <div class=\"cmd-item\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">\n                                        <span class=\"cmd-title\">Check Status</span>\n                                        <code>tailscale status</code>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"cmd-item\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">\n                                        <span class=\"cmd-title\">Ping Node</span>\n                                        <code>tailscale ping &lt;node&gt;</code>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"cmd-item\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">\n                                        <span class=\"cmd-title\">List Peers</span>\n                                        <code>tailscale status --peers</code>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"cmd-item\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">\n                                        <span class=\"cmd-title\">IP Address</span>\n                                        <code>tailscale ip</code>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"cmd-item\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">\n                                        <span class=\"cmd-title\">Enable SSH</span>\n                                        <code>tailscale up --ssh</code>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"cmd-item\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">\n                                        <span class=\"cmd-title\">Connect</span>\n                                        <code>tailscale connect</code>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"cmd-item\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">\n                                        <span class=\"cmd-title\">Disconnect</span>\n                                        <code>tailscale down</code>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"cmd-item\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">\n                                        <span class=\"cmd-title\">Logout</span>\n                                        <code>tailscale logout</code>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"cmd-item\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">\n                                        <span class=\"cmd-title\">Debug Mode</span>\n                                        <code>tailscale debug</code>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"docs-card\">\n                                <h4>рҹ”җ SSH Connection</h4>\n                                <div class=\"code-block\">\n                                    <code onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">ssh user@&lt;tailscale-ip&gt;</code>\n                                    <span class=\"copy-hint\">Click to copy</span>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"code-block\">\n                                    <code onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">ssh ahmadabdullah@100.121.254.21</code>\n                                    <span class=\"copy-hint\">Your connection</span>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tip-box\">\n                                    <strong>рҹ’Ў Pro Tip:</strong> Tailscale SSH removes the need for SSH keys! Just enable with <code>tailscale up --ssh</code>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"docs-card\">\n                                <h4>вҡЎ Advanced Tricks</h4>\n                                <ul class=\"tips-list\">\n                                    <li><strong>Exit Nodes:</strong> Route all traffic through a Tailscale node\n                                        <div class=\"code-block inline\"><code onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">tailscale up --exit-node=&lt;node&gt;</code></div>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li><strong>Advertise Routes:</strong> Share local network\n                                        <div class=\"code-block inline\"><code onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">tailscale up --advertise-routes=192.168.1.0/24</code></div>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li><strong>Serve HTTPS:</strong> Expose local services\n                                        <div class=\"code-block inline\"><code onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">tailscale serve https:443 / http://localhost:8765</code></div>\n                                    </li>\n                                    <li><strong>Funnel:</strong> Public URL for local service\n                                        <div class=\"code-block inline\"><code onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">tailscale funnel 8765</code></div>\n                                    </li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"docs-card\">\n                                <h4>рҹӣЎпёҸ Security Best Practices</h4>\n                                <ul class=\"tips-list\">\n                                    <li>Enable MFA on your Tailscale account</li>\n                                    <li>Use ACLs to restrict access between nodes</li>\n                                    <li>Use tags for servers (not user emails)</li>\n                                    <li>Enable Tailscale SSH and disable password auth</li>\n                                    <li>Review connected devices regularly</li>\n                                    <li>Use ephemeral nodes for temporary access</li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <!-- Termius Tab -->\n                        <div id=\"docs-termius\" class=\"docs-tab-content\">\n                            <div class=\"docs-card\">\n                                <h4>рҹ“ұ iOS Quick Tips</h4>\n                                <ul class=\"tips-list\">\n                                    <li><strong>3D Touch/Haptic Touch</strong> - Quick access to recent hosts</li>\n                                    <li><strong>Swipe left/right</strong> - Switch between open sessions</li>\n                                    <li><strong>Pinch to zoom</strong> - Adjust font size dynamically</li>\n                                    <li><strong>Long press</strong> - Access host options menu</li>\n                                    <li><strong>Two-finger tap</strong> - Toggle keyboard visibility</li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"docs-card\">\n                                <h4>вҢЁпёҸ External Keyboard Shortcuts</h4>\n                                <div class=\"shortcut-grid\">\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Cmd + T</kbd>\n                                        <span>New tab</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Cmd + W</kbd>\n                                        <span>Close tab</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Cmd + 1-9</kbd>\n                                        <span>Switch tabs</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Cmd + K</kbd>\n                                        <span>Clear terminal</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Cmd + L</kbd>\n                                        <span>Clear screen</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Cmd + Shift + E</kbd>\n                                        <span>Snippets panel</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Ctrl + A</kbd>\n                                        <span>Start of line</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Ctrl + E</kbd>\n                                        <span>End of line</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Ctrl + U</kbd>\n                                        <span>Clear line</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Ctrl + C</kbd>\n                                        <span>Cancel command</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Ctrl + D</kbd>\n                                        <span>Logout/EOF</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"shortcut-item\">\n                                        <kbd>Ctrl + Z</kbd>\n                                        <span>Suspend</span>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"docs-card\">\n                                <h4>рҹ”§ Essential Settings</h4>\n                                <ul class=\"tips-list\">\n                                    <li><strong>Face ID/Touch ID Lock</strong> - Enable in Settings вҶ’ Security</li>\n                                    <li><strong>Keep Screen Awake</strong> - Settings вҶ’ Terminal вҶ’ Prevent Sleep</li>\n                                    <li><strong>Font Size</strong> - Adjust in Settings вҶ’ Terminal вҶ’ Font</li>\n                                    <li><strong>Color Schemes</strong> - Choose from built-in or custom</li>\n                                    <li><strong>Key Sync</strong> - Sync SSH keys across all devices</li>\n                                    <li><strong>Host Groups</strong> - Organize servers into groups</li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"docs-card\">\n                                <h4>рҹҡҖ Snippets (Save Commands)</h4>\n                                <p style=\"font-size:0.7rem; color:var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">Create reusable command snippets for quick access</p>\n                                <div class=\"code-block\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">\n\n[488 more lines in file. Use offset=550 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773253204483}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c5706ea","parentId":"ed86bded","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:21:00.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good, I can see the HTML structure. Now let me check what the actual CSS variables are being used in the HTML and create a comprehensive fix. I notice the HTML uses CSS variables like `var(--text-secondary)`, `var(--cyan-400)`, `var(--emerald-400)`, `var(--amber-400)` which aren't defined in my CSS. Let me fix this properly:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_598e6dfa92964b82ae2afdcd","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/* XMAD Control Center v4.0 - COMPLETE CSS WITH ALL VARIABLES */\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* RESET & VARIABLES - INCLUDING ALL CSS VARIABLES USED IN HTML */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n* {\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\n:root {\n    /* Primary Colors */\n    --primary: #6366f1;\n    --primary-dark: #4f46e5;\n    --primary-light: #818cf8;\n    --secondary: #8b5cf6;\n    --accent: #06b6d4;\n    \n    /* Semantic Colors */\n    --success: #10b981;\n    --success-light: #34d399;\n    --warning: #f59e0b;\n    --warning-light: #fbbf24;\n    --error: #ef4444;\n    --error-light: #f87171;\n    --info: #3b82f6;\n    --info-light: #60a5fa;\n    \n    /* Extended Color Palette */\n    --cyan-400: #22d3ee;\n    --cyan-500: #06b6d4;\n    --emerald-400: #34d399;\n    --emerald-500: #10b981;\n    --amber-400: #fbbf24;\n    --amber-500: #f59e0b;\n    --rose-400: #fb7185;\n    --rose-500: #f43f5e;\n    --violet-400: #a78bfa;\n    --violet-500: #8b5cf6;\n    \n    /* Backgrounds */\n    --bg-dark: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);\n    --bg-card: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);\n    --bg-card-hover: rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.9);\n    --bg-input: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);\n    \n    /* Text Colors */\n    --text-primary: #f1f5f9;\n    --text-secondary: #cbd5e1;\n    --text-muted: #94a3b8;\n    \n    /* Borders */\n    --border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);\n    --border-hover: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);\n    --border-focus: var(--primary);\n}\n\nhtml, body {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    overflow-x: hidden;\n}\n\nbody {\n    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    background: #0f172a;\n    min-height: 100vh;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* BACKGROUND - CRITICAL FIX FOR WHITE BACKGROUND ON SCROLL */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.bg-gradient, .bg-grid {\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    z-index: -1;\n    pointer-events: none;\n}\n\n.bg-gradient {\n    background: \n        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),\n        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);\n}\n\n.bg-grid {\n    background-image: \n        linear-gradient(rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),\n        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);\n    background-size: 50px 50px;\n}\n\n/* Critical: Ensure body background never changes to white */\nhtml, body {\n    background-color: #0f172a !important;\n    background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%) !important;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* APP CONTAINER - CENTERED */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.app-container {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 1400px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 1rem;\n    position: relative;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* HEADER */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.glass-header {\n    background: var(--bg-dark);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\n    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    position: sticky;\n    top: 0;\n    z-index: 100;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n    width: 100%;\n}\n\n.glass-header.hidden {\n    transform: translateY(-100%);\n}\n\n.header-left, .header-right {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.menu-toggle {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 4px;\n    padding: 8px;\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n    cursor: pointer;\n    width: 40px;\n    height: 40px;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n}\n\n.menu-toggle:hover {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n}\n\n.menu-toggle span {\n    width: 24px;\n    height: 2px;\n    background: var(--text-primary);\n    border-radius: 2px;\n}\n\n.logo {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.logo-icon {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.logo-text {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light), var(--secondary));\n    -webkit-background-clip: text;\n    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n}\n\n.status-circle-btn {\n    width: 44px;\n    height: 44px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n}\n\n.status-circle-btn:hover {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n    transform: scale(1.05);\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* SIDE MENU */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.side-menu-overlay {\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);\n    opacity: 0;\n    visibility: hidden;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n    z-index: 150;\n    pointer-events: none;\n}\n\n.side-menu-overlay.active {\n    opacity: 1;\n    visibility: visible;\n    pointer-events: auto;\n}\n\n.side-menu {\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 0;\n    left: -300px;\n    width: 300px;\n    height: 100%;\n    background: var(--bg-dark);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(30px);\n    border-right: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    transition: left 0.3s ease;\n    z-index: 200;\n    overflow-y: auto;\n}\n\n.side-menu.active {\n    left: 0;\n}\n\n.side-menu-header {\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n}\n\n.side-menu-header h2 {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n}\n\n.close-menu-btn {\n    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);\n    color: var(--error);\n    width: 36px;\n    height: 36px;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n}\n\n.close-menu-btn:hover {\n    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);\n}\n\n.side-menu-content {\n    padding: 1rem;\n}\n\n.menu-section {\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n}\n\n.menu-section-title {\n    font-size: 0.7rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\n    padding: 0 0.75rem;\n}\n\n.menu-item {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 0.75rem;\n    padding: 0.875rem 1rem;\n    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;\n    border-radius: 0.625rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.2s;\n    border: 1px solid transparent;\n}\n\n.menu-item:hover {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);\n    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n}\n\n.menu-item.active {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.25);\n    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);\n}\n\n.menu-item-icon {\n    font-size: 1.25rem;\n}\n\n.menu-item-text {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-size: 0.95rem;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* MAIN CONTENT & SCROLL */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.main-content {\n    width: 100%;\n}\n\n.content-scroll {\n    width: 100%;\n    overflow-y: auto;\n    padding: 1rem 0;\n    /* Critical: Prevent white background on scroll */\n    background: transparent !important;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* SECTIONS */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.section-content {\n    display: none;\n    width: 100%;\n    animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease;\n}\n\n.section-content.active {\n    display: block;\n}\n\n@keyframes fadeIn {\n    from {\n        opacity: 0;\n        transform: translateY(10px);\n    }\n    to {\n        opacity: 1;\n        transform: translateY(0);\n    }\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* CARDS - COMPLETE STYLING */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.task-input-card, .tasks-card, .docs-card {\n    background: var(--bg-card);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\n    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 1rem;\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n}\n\n.task-input-card h3, .tasks-card h3, .docs-card h3, .docs-card h4 {\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    font-size: 1.125rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n.docs-card h4 {\n    font-size: 1rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\n}\n\n.task-input-card h3 {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n}\n\n.tasks-card h3 {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n}\n\n.task-input-row {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 0.75rem;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* GLASS INPUTS */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.glass-input, .glass-textarea {\n    width: 100%;\n    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;\n    background: var(--bg-input);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 0.625rem;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    font-family: inherit;\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n}\n\n.glass-input:focus, .glass-textarea:focus {\n    outline: none;\n    border-color: var(--border-focus);\n    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);\n    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);\n}\n\n.glass-textarea {\n    min-height: 150px;\n    resize: vertical;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* GLASS BUTTONS */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.glass-btn {\n    display: inline-flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n    padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;\n    border-radius: 0.625rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    border: 1px solid transparent;\n    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n}\n\n.glass-btn.primary {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark));\n    color: white;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n}\n\n.glass-btn.primary:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);\n}\n\n.glass-btn.secondary {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n}\n\n.glass-btn.secondary:hover {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n}\n\n.glass-btn.ghost {\n    background: transparent;\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n    border-color: var(--border-color);\n}\n\n.glass-btn.ghost:hover {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);\n    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n}\n\n.glass-btn.sm {\n    padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* EMPTY STATE */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.empty-state {\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 2rem;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* DOCS TABS */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.docs-tabs {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n    overflow-x: auto;\n}\n\n.docs-tab {\n    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\n    border-radius: 0.5rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.2s;\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n}\n\n.docs-tab:hover {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);\n}\n\n.docs-tab.active {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n}\n\n.docs-tab-content {\n    display: none;\n}\n\n.docs-tab-content.active {\n    display: block;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* COMMAND GRID */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.command-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n    gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.cmd-item {\n    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 0.75rem;\n    padding: 1rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.3s;\n}\n\n.cmd-item:hover {\n    border-color: var(--primary);\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n}\n\n.cmd-title {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* CODE BLOCKS */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.code-block {\n    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 0.5rem;\n    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;\n    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Courier New', monospace;\n    font-size: 0.8125rem;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    overflow-x: auto;\n    position: relative;\n}\n\n.code-block code {\n    color: var(--cyan-400);\n}\n\n.code-block.inline {\n    display: inline;\n    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.copy-hint {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 0.5rem;\n    right: 0.5rem;\n    font-size: 0.7rem;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;\n    border-radius: 0.25rem;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* TIPS LIST */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.tips-list {\n    list-style: none;\n    padding: 0;\n}\n\n.tips-list li {\n    padding: 0.75rem 0;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n}\n\n.tips-list li:last-child {\n    border-bottom: none;\n}\n\n.tip-box {\n    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);\n    border-radius: 0.5rem;\n    padding: 1rem;\n    margin: 1rem 0;\n}\n\n.tip-box strong {\n    color: var(--primary-light);\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* SHORTCUT GRID */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.shortcut-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n    gap: 0.75rem;\n}\n\n.shortcut-item {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;\n    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.4);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.shortcut-item kbd {\n    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    border-radius: 0.25rem;\n    padding: 0.125rem 0.375rem;\n    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    color: var(--cyan-400);\n}\n\n.shortcut-item span {\n    font-size: 0.8125rem;\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* SSH DOCS CONTAINER */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n.ssh-docs-container {\n    padding: 1rem 0;\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* TABLES */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\ntable {\n    width: 100%;\n    border-collapse: collapse;\n}\n\ntable td {\n    padding: 0.5rem;\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n}\n\ntable code {\n    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n    padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;\n    font-size: 0.8125rem;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n}\n\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n/* RESPONSIVE */\n/* в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ */\n\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .app-container { padding: 0.75rem; }\n    .side-menu { width: 85%; left: -85%; }\n    .glass-header { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; }\n    .task-input-card, .tasks-card, .docs-card { padding: 1.25rem; }\n    .command-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .shortcut-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .task-input-row { flex-direction: column; }\n}\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/packages/legacy/styles.css"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4833527c963d433291d8185d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/packages/legacy && wc -l styles.css"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02081733f96c4eb884487bc9","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# вң… COMPREHENSIVE FIX APPLIED\n\n## Issues Fixed:\n\n### 1. вң… White Background on Scroll\n**Root Cause**: CSS variables were missing and body background wasn't forced\n**Fix**: \n- Added `background-color: #0f172a !important` to html, body\n- Added `background: transparent !important` to .content-scroll\n- This ensures background never turns white\n\n### 2. вң… Missing CSS Variables\n**Root Cause**: HTML used undefined CSS variables\n**Variables Added**:\n- `--cyan-400`, `--emerald-400`, `--amber-400`\n- `--violet-400`, `--rose-400`\n- `--success-light`, `--warning-light`, `--error-light`\n- All color variants used in HTML\n\n### 3. вң… Everything Under Quick Add Task Has No Style\n**Root Cause**: Missing styles for:\n- .task-input-card\n- .tasks-card\n- .task-input-row\n- .empty-state\n- All docs elements\n\n**Fix**: Complete styling for all card types and content elements\n\n### 4. вң… Docs Elements Missing\n**Added**:\n- .docs-tabs, .docs-tab, .docs-tab-content\n- .command-grid, .cmd-item, .cmd-title\n- .code-block (inline and block)\n- .tips-list, .tip-box\n- .shortcut-grid, .shortcut-item\n- .ssh-docs-container\n- table styling\n\n### 5. вң… Glass Inputs & Buttons\n**Added**:\n- .glass-input, .glass-textarea\n- .glass-btn (prim