ll emoji characters in index.html\n     - [ ] Document current color scheme and dark theme variables\n     \n     ## Execution Steps\n     \n     ### Step 1: Audit Current State\n     - Action: Analyze index.html to identify all UI components, emojis, and structural elements\n     - Files: ~/Desktop/xmad-control-center/packages/legacy/index.html\n     - Expected Result: Complete inventory of emojis, components, and current styling issues\n     \n     ### Step 2: Document Styling Issues\n     - Action: Open dashboard in browser and document all visual inconsistencies (background scroll issues, button styling, text visibility, card borders, modal behaviors, animations)\n     - Files: Create audit-notes.md\n     - Expected Result: Detailed list of all styling problems with screenshots/descriptions\n     \n     ### Step 3: Create Icon Replacement Strategy\n     - Action: Map each emoji to appropriate Unicode symbol or inline SVG (12-16px)\n     - Files: Create icon-mapping.md\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ Stage 3/5: GUARDIAN AUDIT в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\nрҹӣЎпёҸ  GUARDIAN AUDIT: Reviewing planвҖҰ\n\nвҡ   Warnings detected. Proceeding with caution.\nPlan modifies CSS files which could affect large portions of the UI - recommend visual testing after changes\nBackup strategy is mentioned but should be verified before execution\nChanges to index.html structure may have downstream effects on any JavaScript that references emoji content\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ Stage 4/5: WORKER EXECUTION в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\nвҡҷ  WORKER AGENT DISPATCHING\n   Role:      \n   Agent:     \n   Task Type:  | Complexity: \n\nрҹҡҖ Executing task with agent: \n\nвң… WORKER COMPLETE\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ Stage 5/5: REVIEW в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв