- [ ] Create SVG icon library for replacements\n     \n     ## Execution Steps\n     \n     ### Step 1: Initial Audit and Assessment\n     - Action: Analyze all UI components in index.html and identify styling issues\n     - Files: index.html, styles.css, styles-additional.css, app.js\n     - Expected Result: Complete list of all styling problems, emoji locations, and component inventory\n     \n     ### Step 2: Create SVG Icon Library\n     - Action: Create a new file with SVG icons for all emoji replacements\n     - Files: Create icons.svg in the project root\n     - Expected Result: SVG file containing 12-16px icons for all required replacements (settings, close, menu, etc.)\n     \n     ### Step 3: Fix Background Scrolling Issues\n     - Action: Update CSS to prevent background color changes on scroll\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ Stage 3/5: GUARDIAN AUDIT в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\nрҹӣЎпёҸ  GUARDIAN AUDIT: Reviewing planвҖҰ\n\nвҡ   Warnings detected. Proceeding with caution.\nPlan modifies multiple files (5+ files including HTML, CSS, JS) - consider reviewing changes incrementally\nModifying index.html structure - ensure JavaScript event bindings are not broken by emoji replacements\nCreating new SVG icon library file - verify file is properly referenced and doesn't introduce XSS vectors if using inline SVGs\nAnimations in app.js may affect accessibility - ensure reduced-motion preferences are respected\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ Stage 4/5: WORKER EXECUTION в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\nвҡҷ  WORKER AGENT DISPATCHING\n   Role:      \n   Agent:     \n   Task Type:  | Complexity: \n\nрҹҡҖ Executing task with agent: \n\nвң… WORKER COMPLETE\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ Stage 5/5: REVIEW в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”