{"type":"message","id":"77467c2b","parentId":"3d9b54b2","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:38:03.107Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_72e472ec52c74cc9b03b2d77","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"name\": \"ein-ui\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"authors\": [\n    \"Ehsan Ghaffar <ghafari.5000@gmail.com>\"\n  ],\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"next build\",\n    \"dev\": \"next dev\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint .\",\n    \"lint:fix\": \"eslint . --fix\",\n    \"start\": \"next start\",\n    \"analyze\": \"next experimental-analyze\",\n    \"registry:build\": \"shadcn build\",\n    \"registry:search\": \"shadcn search\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest\",\n    \"test:watch\": \"vitest --watch\",\n    \"test:coverage\": \"vitest --coverage\",\n    \"test:ui\": \"vitest --ui\"\n  },\n  \"keywords\": [],\n  \"author\": \"\",\n  \"license\": \"ISC\",\n  \"packageManager\": \"bun@1.3.10\",\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@radix-ui/react-accordion\": \"^1.2.12\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-alert-dialog\": \"^1.1.15\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-avatar\": \"^1.1.11\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-checkbox\": \"^1.3.3\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-dialog\": \"^1.1.15\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-label\": \"^2.1.8\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-popover\": \"^1.1.15\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-progress\": \"^1.1.8\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-radio-group\": \"^1.3.8\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-scroll-area\": \"^1.2.10\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-select\": \"^2.2.6\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-separator\": \"^1.1.8\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-slider\": \"^1.3.6\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-slot\": \"^1.2.4\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-switch\": \"^1.2.6\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-tabs\": \"^1.1.13\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-tooltip\": \"^1.2.8\",\n    \"@vercel/analytics\": \"^1.6.1\",\n    \"@wandry/analytics-sdk\": \"^1.16.0\",\n    \"class-variance-authority\": \"^0.7.1\",\n    \"clsx\": \"^2.1.1\",\n    \"framer-motion\": \"^12.34.3\",\n    \"lucide-react\": \"^0.575.0\",\n    \"next\": \"^16.1.6\",\n    \"next-themes\": \"^0.4.6\",\n    \"react\": \"19.2.4\",\n    \"react-dom\": \"19.2.4\",\n    \"shadcn\": \"^3.8.5\",\n    \"tailwind-merge\": \"^3.4.1\",\n    \"tailwindcss-animate\": \"^1.0.7\",\n    \"zod\": \"^4.3.6\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@eslint/eslintrc\": \"^3.3.3\",\n    \"@tailwindcss/postcss\": \"^4.2.0\",\n    \"@testing-library/jest-dom\": \"^6.9.1\",\n    \"@testing-library/react\": \"^16.3.2\",\n    \"@types/node\": \"^25.3.0\",\n    \"@types/react\": \"19.2.14\",\n    \"@types/react-dom\": \"19.2.3\",\n    \"@vitejs/plugin-react\": \"^5.1.4\",\n    \"@vitest/coverage-v8\": \"^4.0.18\",\n    \"@vitest/ui\": \"^4.0.18\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^9.39.2\",\n    \"eslint-config-next\": \"16.1.6\",\n    \"jsdom\": \"^28.1.0\",\n    \"tailwindcss\": \"^4.2.0\",\n    \"tw-animate-css\": \"^1.4.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.9.3\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^4.0.18\"\n  },\n  \"trustedDependencies\": [\n    \"unrs-resolver\"\n  ]\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773254283102}}
{"type":"message","id":"40521c55","parentId":"77467c2b","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:38:21.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Ein UI is a **React/Next.js** project with beautiful liquid glass components. This is much better than trying to fix the old HTML/CSS dashboard. Let me create a new XMAD dashboard using ein-ui:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1c7e9e235917445bbbd4d88e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/ein-ui && find . -name \"*.tsx\" -path \"*/components/*\" | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_365fc301c9be49b6b424610e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# рҹҺЁ Creating XMAD Dashboard with ein-ui\n\n## Location\nCreate inside: `/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/ein-ui/app/xmad-dashboard/`\n\n## Why ein-ui?\n- вң… React 19 + Next.js 16\n- вң… Liquid glass components (already styled)\n- вң… Tailwind CSS v4\n- вң… Radix UI primitives\n- вң… Professional design system\n- вң… Small icons (lucide-react)\n- вң… Copy-paste components\n\n## Plan\n\n### Phase 1: Create Dashboard Page\n1. Create new page in ein-ui\n2. Use existing components\n3. Build XMAD layout\n\n### Phase 2: Components Needed\n- Mini widgets (glass cards)\n- Navigation (sidebar)\n- Status indicators\n- Buttons (small, with icons)\n- Cards (glass effect)\n- Modals\n\n### Phase 3: Features\n- OpenClaw status\n- Guardian status\n- Task management\n- Network controls\n- System monitoring\n\n---\n\n**This will give us a professional, beautiful dashboard!**","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/ein-ui/XMAD_DASHBOARD_PLAN.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00f7b82806844e7193118d6b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/ein-ui && ls -la app/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0314216ac06a49a08237e9df","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { Card } from \"@/components/ui/card\"\nimport { Button } from \"@/components/ui/button\"\nimport { Badge } from \"@/components/ui/badge\"\nimport { \n  Cpu, \n  HardDrive, \n  Wifi, \n  Shield,\n  CheckCircle2,\n  AlertCircle,\n  XCircle,\n  Settings,\n  Power,\n  RefreshCw\n} from \"lucide-react\"\n\nexport default function XmadDashboard() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-slate-950\">\n      {/* Background grid */}\n      <div className=\"fixed inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-10 pointer-events-none\" />\n      \n      {/* Main container */}\n      <div className=\"relative z-10 container mx-auto p-6\">\n        {/* Header */}\n        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n            <div className=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center\">\n              <span className=\"text-white font-bold text-xl\">в¬Ў</span>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <h1 className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">XMAD Control Center</h1>\n              <p className=\"text-sm text-slate-400\">v4.0</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <Button variant=\"ghost\" size=\"icon\">\n              <RefreshCw className=\"h-4 w-4\" />\n            </Button>\n            <Button variant=\"ghost\" size=\"icon\">\n              <Settings className=\"h-4 w-4\" />\n            </Button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Widgets Row */}\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-6\">\n          {/* OpenClaw Widget */}\n          <Card className=\"glass-card p-4 border-cyan-500/30 hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-3\">\n              <div className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/20 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                <Cpu className=\"h-4 w-4 text-cyan-400\" />\n              </div>\n              <Badge variant=\"outline\" className=\"bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 border-green-500/30\">\n                <CheckCircle2 className=\"h-3 w-3 mr-1\" />\n                Running\n              </Badge>\n            </div>\n            <h3 className=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-1\">OpenClaw</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1\">527 MB</p>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-slate-400\">AI Gateway</p>\n          </Card>\n\n          {/* Guardian Widget */}\n          <Card className=\"glass-card p-4 border-purple-500/30 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-3\">\n              <div className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                <Shield className=\"h-4 w-4 text-purple-400\" />\n              </div>\n              <Badge variant=\"outline\" className=\"bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 border-green-500/30\">\n                <CheckCircle2 className=\"h-3 w-3 mr-1\" />\n                Online\n              </Badge>\n            </div>\n            <h3 className=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-1\">Guardian</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1\">4/6</p>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-slate-400\">Agents Active</p>\n          </Card>\n\n          {/* Memory Widget */}\n          <Card className=\"glass-card p-4 border-blue-500/30 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-3\">\n              <div className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                <HardDrive className=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-400\" />\n              </div>\n              <Badge variant=\"outline\" className=\"bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 border-green-500/30\">\n                <CheckCircle2 className=\"h-3 w-3 mr-1\" />\n                Good\n              </Badge>\n            </div>\n            <h3 className=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-1\">Memory</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1\">790 MB</p>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-slate-400\">Free RAM</p>\n          </Card>\n\n          {/* Network Widget */}\n          <Card className=\"glass-card p-4 border-indigo-500/30 hover:border-indigo-500/50 transition-all\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-3\">\n              <div className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/20 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                <Wifi className=\"h-4 w-4 text-indigo-400\" />\n              </div>\n              <Badge variant=\"outline\" className=\"bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 border-green-500/30\">\n                <CheckCircle2 className=\"h-3 w-3 mr-1\" />\n                Connected\n              </Badge>\n            </div>\n            <h3 className=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-1\">Network</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1\">VPN</p>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-slate-400\">Tailscale</p>\n          </Card>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Quick Actions */}\n        <Card className=\"glass-card p-6\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Quick Actions</h2>\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n            <Button variant=\"outline\" className=\"h-auto py-3 flex-col gap-2\">\n              <Power className=\"h-4 w-4\" />\n              <span className=\"text-sm\">Optimize PC</span>\n            </Button>\n            <Button variant=\"outline\" className=\"h-auto py-3 flex-col gap-2\">\n              <RefreshCw className=\"h-4 w-4\" />\n              <span className=\"text-sm\">Restart</span>\n            </Button>\n            <Button variant=\"outline\" className=\"h-auto py-3 flex-col gap-2\">\n              <Shield className=\"h-4 w-4\" />\n              <span className=\"text-sm\">Guardian</spa