workspace-critical-rules>\n## Every Session\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` вҖ” this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` вҖ” this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Safety\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>","firstKeptEntryId":"1a25caa8","tokensBefore":106889,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":["/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/ALIGNMENT_FIXED.md","/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/AUDIT_REPORT.md","/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/COMPREHENSIVE_FIX_APPLIED.md","/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/CRITICAL_FIXES_APPLIED.md","/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/FINAL_FIX_COMPLETE.md","/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/GUARDIAN_AUDIT_TASK.md","/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/GUARDIAN_SUGGEST_COMPLETE.md","/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/STYLES_COMPLETE.md","/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/STYLES_FINAL_COMPLETE.md","/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/packages/legacy/styles-additional.css","/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/packages/legacy/styles.css"]},"fromHook":true}
