{"type":"message","id":"a8eae3fc","parentId":"4cd266ff","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:47:52.638Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent idea! Let me deploy this to Vercel using the ein-ui template. I'll create a new project, update it for XMAD, and it will auto-deploy!"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3d1f43d7e6254037ba7cb1c4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop && git clone https://github.com/ehsanghaffar/ein-ui.git xmad-control-vercel 2>&1 | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7a8305067afd468faf9d42a9","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# рҹҡҖ XMAD Control - Vercel Deployment Plan\n\n## What We're Doing:\n\n### 1. Clone ein-ui Template\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/ehsanghaffar/ein-ui.git xmad-control-vercel\n```\n\n### 2. Configure Project\n- Update package.json (name, description)\n- Configure Infisical for SSOT keys\n- Set up Vercel auto-deploy\n\n### 3. Build XMAD Dashboard\n- Create dashboard in new project\n- Use glassy liquid components\n- Add XMAD features\n- Small icons (no emojis)\n\n### 4. Deploy to Vercel\n- Push to GitHub\n- Auto-deploy on commit\n- Live URL available\n\n---\n\n**Guardian will handle this entire process!**","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/VERCEL_DEPLOY_PLAN.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f57be3fb6edd4ad98e725e05","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/platform-monorepo/.env.example"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ed553059e1d1486ca6d68749","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/platform-monorepo && cat .gitlab-ci.yml 2>/dev/null || cat .github/workflows/*.yml 2>/dev/null | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":23776,"output":354,"cacheRead":9728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33858,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773254867477}}
