{"type":"message","id":"fab802ee","parentId":"59b5f805","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:48:13.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The ein-ui repo isn't publicly accessible for cloning. Let me check your local ein-ui and create a new project from it:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0ce6118cc0b14444a3f50c59","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop && cp -r ein-ui xmad-control-vercel 2>&1 | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4ebb8c7f4ce745878bbcfe51","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"name\": \"xmad-control\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"XMAD Control Center - AI-powered control center with glassmorphism UI\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"authors\": [\n    \"Ahmad Abdullah\"\n  ],\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"next build\",\n    \"dev\": \"next dev\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint .\",\n    \"lint:fix\": \"eslint . --fix\",\n    \"start\": \"next start\",\n    \"analyze\": \"next experimental-analyze\",\n    \"registry:build\": \"shadcn build\",\n    \"registry:search\": \"shadcn search\"\n  },\n  \"keywords\": [\"dashboard\", \"control-center\", \"ai\", \"openclaw\", \"guardian\"],\n  \"author\": \"Ahmad Abdullah\",\n  \"license\": \"ISC\",\n  \"packageManager\": \"bun@1.3.10\",\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@radix-ui/react-accordion\": \"^1.2.12\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-alert-dialog\": \"^1.1.15\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-avatar\": \"^1.1.11\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-checkbox\": \"^1.3.3\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-dialog\": \"^1.1.15\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-label\": \"^2.1.8\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-popover\": \"^1.1.15\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-progress\": \"^1.1.8\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-radio-group\": \"^1.3.8\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-scroll-area\": \"^1.2.10\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-select\": \"^2.2.6\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-separator\": \"^1.1.8\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-slider\": \"^1.3.6\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-slot\": \"^1.2.4\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-switch\": \"^1.2.6\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-tabs\": \"^1.1.13\",\n    \"@radix-ui/react-tooltip\": \"^1.2.8\",\n    \"@vercel/analytics\": \"^1.6.1\",\n    \"class-variance-authority\": \"^0.7.1\",\n    \"clsx\": \"^2.1.1\",\n    \"framer-motion\": \"^12.34.3\",\n    \"lucide-react\": \"^0.575.0\",\n    \"next\": \"^16.1.6\",\n    \"next-themes\": \"^0.4.6\",\n    \"react\": \"19.2.4\",\n    \"react-dom\": \"19.2.4\",\n    \"shadcn\": \"^3.8.5\",\n    \"tailwind-merge\": \"^3.4.1\",\n    \"tailwindcss-animate\": \"^1.0.7\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@eslint/eslintrc\": \"^3.3.3\",\n    \"@tailwindcss/postcss\": \"^4.2.0\",\n    \"@types/node\": \"^25.3.0\",\n    \"@types/react\": \"19.2.14\",\n    \"@types/react-dom\": \"19.2.3\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^9.39.2\",\n    \"eslint-config-next\": \"16.1.6\",\n    \"tailwindcss\": \"^4.2.0\",\n    \"tw-animate-css\": \"^1.4.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.9.3\"\n  }\n}\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/package.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_09c1375139a146c68cfd510f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# XMAD Control Center\n\nAI-powered control center with beautiful glassmorphism UI.\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- **React 19** - Latest React\n- **Next.js 16** - Modern framework\n- **Tailwind CSS v4** - Utility styling\n- **Radix UI** - Accessible components\n- **Framer Motion** - Smooth animations\n- **Lucide Icons** - Clean icon system\n\n## Features\n\n- рҹӨ– OpenClaw integration\n- рҹӣЎпёҸ Guardian agent control\n- рҹ“Ҡ System monitoring\n- рҹҢҗ Network management\n- рҹ”§ PC optimization\n- рҹ“қ Task management\n\n## Development\n\n```bash\nbun install\nbun dev\n```\n\nVisit [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)\n\n## Deployment\n\nThis project auto-deploys to Vercel on commit to main branch.\n\n### Environment Variables (via Infisical SSOT)\n\n- OpenClaw Gateway URL\n- Guardian API endpoints\n- System monitoring config\n\n## License\n\nISC\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Deskt