{"type":"message","id":"b5f7ac10","parentId":"5efd86ee","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:49:40.175Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! GitHub repository created and pushed! Now let me create the Vercel configuration:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3ae3290d2aa844b1b5b2be17","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"buildCommand\": \"bun run build\",\n  \"outputDirectory\": \".next\",\n  \"devCommand\": \"bun run dev\",\n  \"installCommand\": \"bun install\",\n  \"framework\": \"nextjs\",\n  \"regions\": [\"hkg1\"],\n  \"env\": {\n    \"NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL\": \"@xmad-app-url\",\n    \"OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL\": \"@openclaw-gateway-url\",\n    \"GUARDIAN_API_URL\": \"@guardian-api-url\"\n  }\n}\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/vercel.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_36a324be33964a32a50d6b48","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# XMAD Control Center\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n![XMAD Control](https://img.shields.io/badge/XMAD-Control-6366f1?style=for-the-badge&logo=next.js)\n![Next.js](https://img.shields.io/badge/Next.js-16.1.6-black?style=for-the-badge&logo=next.js)\n![React](https://img.shields.io/badge/React-19-61dafb?style=for-the-badge&logo=react)\n\n**AI-powered control center with beautiful glassmorphism UI**\n\n[![Deploy](https://vercel.com/button)](https://xmad-control.vercel.app)\n\n</div>\n\n## Features\n\n- рҹӨ– **OpenClaw Integration** - Control OpenClaw AI gateway\n- рҹӣЎпёҸ **Guardian Control** - Manage Guardian agents\n- рҹ“Ҡ **System Monitoring** - Real-time system stats\n- рҹҢҗ **Network Management** - Tailscale, SSH, VPN\n- рҹ”§ **PC Optimization** - One-click optimization\n- рҹ“қ **Task Management** - Track and manage tasks\n- рҹҺЁ **Glassmorphism UI** - Beautiful liquid glass design\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- **React 19** - Latest React features\n- **Next.js 16** - Modern full-stack framework\n- **Tailwind CSS v4** - Utility-first styling\n- **Radix UI** - Accessible component primitives\n- **Framer Motion** - Smooth animations\n- **Lucide Icons** - Clean icon system\n\n## Development\n\n```bash\n# Install dependencies\nbun install\n\n# Run development server\nbun dev\n\n# Build for production\nbun run build\n\n# Start production server\nbun start\n```\n\nVisit [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)\n\n## Deployment\n\nThis project auto-deploys to [Vercel](https://vercel.com) on every push to the `main` branch.\n\n### Environment Variables (via Infisical SSOT)\n\nConfigure these in Vercel project settings:\n\n- `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` - Application URL\n- `OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL` - OpenClaw gateway endpoint\n- `GUARDIAN_API_URL` - Guardian API endpoint\n\n## License\n\nISC В© Ahmad Abdullah\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\">\nMade with вқӨпёҸ by Ahmad Abdullah\n</div>\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/README.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4e7fbf25dfe942a79bb51fb8","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# вң… XMAD Control - Vercel Ready!\n\n## GitHub Repository: вң… Complete\n\n**URL**: https://github.com/xmad11/xmad-control\n\n**Status**: вң… Pushed and ready\n\n---\n\n## Vercel Configuration: вң… Complete\n\n**File**: `vercel.json` created\n\n**Settings**:\n- Build: `bun run build`\n- Framework: Next.js 16\n- Region: Hong Kong (hkg1)\n- Environment variables configured\n\n---\n\n## Next Steps: Connect to Vercel\n\n### 1. Go to Vercel\nVisit: https://vercel.com/new\n\n### 2. Import Repository\n- Click \"Add New Project\"\n- Select `xmad-control` from GitHub\n- Click \"Import\"\n\n### 3. Configure\n- Framework: Next.js (auto-detected)\n- Build Command: `bun run build` (auto-detected)\n- Region: Hong Kong (recommended)\n\n### 4. Deploy\n- Click \"Deploy\"\n- Wait ~2 minutes\n- Get your Vercel URL!\n\n---\n\n## After Deploy\n\n### Auto-Deploy Workflow:\n1. Make changes locally\n2. `git add . && git commit -m \"message\"`\n3. `git push`\n4. Vercel auto-deploys!\n5. Check live URL вң…\n\n---\n\n## Current Features:\n\n### Dashboard (app/xmad-dashboard/page.tsx)\n- вң… 4 Glass widgets\n- вң… Status badges\n- вң… Quick actions\n- вң… Dark gradient background\n- вң… NO emojis!\n- вң… Small Lucide icons (14-16px)\n\n---\n\n**Ready to deploy to Vercel!** рҹҡҖ","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/VERCEL_READY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0b795f973eef474782d22e71","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel && git add . && git commit -m \"Add Vercel configuration and update README\" && git push 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":2117,"output":1115,"cacheRead":38528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41760,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773254963366}}
