{"type":"message","id":"9629641f","parentId":"d60597de","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:49:58.205Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n# рҹҺү **XMAD CONTROL - READY FOR VERCEL!**\n\n## What I Did:\n\n### 1. Created New Project вң…\n- Copied ein-ui to `xmad-control-vercel/`\n- Updated package.json for XMAD\n- Created beautiful dashboard with glassmorphism UI\n\n### 2. GitHub Repository вң…\n- **URL**: https://github.com/xmad11/xmad-control\n- **Status**: Pushed and ready\n- **Auto-deploy**: Configured\n\n### 3. Vercel Configuration вң…\n- `vercel.json` created\n- Build settings configured\n- Environment variables ready\n\n---\n\n## Next Step: Deploy!\n\n### Go to:\n**https://vercel.com/new**\n\n### Steps:\n1. Click \"Add New Project\"\n2. Import `xmad-control` from GitHub\n3. Click \"Deploy\"\n4. Get live URL: `https://xmad-control.vercel.app`\n\n---\n\n## Auto-Deploy Ready!\n\nAfter deploying, any push to GitHub will auto-deploy:\n```bash\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"Add new feature\"\ngit push  # Auto-deploys to Vercel! рҹҡҖ\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dashboard Features:\n- 4 Glass widgets (OpenClaw, Guardian, Memory, Network)\n- Status badges\n- Quick actions\n- Dark gradient background\n- NO emojis!\n- Small Lucide icons\n\n**Ready to deploy! Just connect to Vercel and click Deploy!** рҹҡҖ"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":3698,"output":314,"cacheRead":39296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43308,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773254994153}}
