{"type":"message","id":"13e80e99","parentId":"c4dd93e3","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:52:17.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Let me set up the full Vercel CI/CD with Infisical integration. Let me check your Infisical setup and configure everything:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b4345b0ba786473892437a9d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"infisical --version 2>&1 || echo \"Infisical not installed\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0a688eb9a95849e6b39c3b2d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"vercel --version 2>&1 || echo \"Vercel CLI not installed\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_77611b9ff6514028bf0e470c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"infisical --help 2>&1 | head -30"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_97ed4a68393d46c89c947585","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# рҹҡҖ Full Vercel + Infisical CI/CD Setup\n\n## Plan:\n\n### 1. Install CLI Tools\n- вң… Vercel CLI\n- вң… Infisical CLI\n\n### 2. Configure Infisical\n- Login to Infisical\n- Get project ID\n- Configure environment variables\n\n### 3. Configure Vercel\n- Link project to Vercel\n- Set up CI/CD\n- Connect Infisical for secrets\n\n### 4. Deploy\n- Push to GitHub\n- Vercel auto-deploys\n- Infisical injects secrets\n\n---\n\n**Starting full setup now!**","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/CICD_SETUP.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b1c3e1ef7892488a9dd1ee98","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel && npm i -g vercel@latest infisical@latest 2>&1 | tail -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":297,"output":318,"cacheRead":43264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43879,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773255133184}}
