{"type":"message","id":"7e34be8b","parentId":"61a48d9e","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:52:46.169Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good! Infisical is already installed. Vercel CLI is installing. Let me check and set up the project:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2b61480454cb4f48bafb4d20","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"rapid-seaslug","timeout":10000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_629ca90f18974673a23d89f0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"infisical status 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_db45af3a37814cb7b070320e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel && infisical init --help 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cb7b5e350c2144a6909774b4","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Infisical Configuration for XMAD Control\n\n## Project Setup\n\n### Step 1: Initialize Infisical\n```bash\ncd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel\ninfisical init\n```\n\n### Step 2: Link to Existing Project\n- Project ID: 3f265951-5e47-4460-88c1-ad9bee65b1ac (from platform-monorepo)\n- Or create new project for XMAD Control\n\n### Step 3: Configure Secrets\nAdd these secrets in Infisical:\n- `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` - Vercel URL\n- `OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL` - http://localhost:18789\n- `GUARDIAN_API_URL` - Local Guardian endpoint\n- `OPENCLAW_API_KEY` - SSOT key from Keychain\n\n### Step 4: Vercel Integration\n```bash\nvercel link\ninfisical run vercel pull\n```\n\n---\n\n**Starting setup...**","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/INFISICAL_SETUP.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_51a2fe45c6454546a30aabcc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel && infisical init 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":521,"output":376,"cacheRead":43776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44673,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"