{"type":"message","id":"fb376584","parentId":"b328f7aa","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:52:55.565Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_db45af3a37814cb7b070320e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Used to connect your local project with Infisical project\n\nUsage:\n  infisical init\n\nExamples:\ninfisical init\n\nFlags:\n  -h, --help   help for init\n\nGlobal Flags:\n      --domain string      Point the CLI to your Infisical instance (e.g., https://eu.infisical.com for EU Cloud, or https://your-instance.com for self-hosted). Can also set via INFISICAL_API_URL environment variable. Required for non-US Cloud users. (default \"https://app.infisical.com/api\")\n  -l, --log-level string   log level (trace, debug, info, warn, error, fatal)\n      --silent             Disable output of tip/info messages. Useful when running in scripts or CI/CD pipelines.\n      --telemetry          Infisical collects non-sensitive telemetry data to enhance features and improve user experience. Participation is voluntary (default true)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":264,"aggregated":"Used to connect your local project with Infisical project\n\nUsage:\n  infisical init\n\nExamples:\ninfisical init\n\nFlags:\n  -h, --help   help for init\n\nGlobal Flags:\n      --domain string      Point the CLI to your Infisical instance (e.g., https://eu.infisical.com for EU Cloud, or https://your-instance.com for self-hosted). Can also set via INFISICAL_API_URL environment variable. Required for non-US Cloud users. (default \"https://app.infisical.com/api\")\n  -l, --log-level string   log level (trace, debug, info, warn, error, fatal)\n      --silent             Disable output of tip/info messages. Useful when running in scripts or CI/CD pipelines.\n      --telemetry          Infisical collects non-sensitive telemetry data to enhance features and improve user experience. Participation is voluntary (default true)","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw