{"type":"message","id":"89f1058c","parentId":"0f179e91","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:55:23.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The repository isn't accessible. However, since you mentioned you have full Vercel admin access and Infisical ready, let me configure the current xmad-control project to use Infisical for environment variables:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ebb6ab37a96c458e86062a23","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Infisical Integration for XMAD Control\n\n## Setup Infisical for Environment Variables\n\n### Step 1: Login to Infisical\n```bash\ninfisical login\n```\n- Select: Infisical Cloud (US Region)\n- This will authenticate you\n\n### Step 2: Initialize Project\n```bash\ncd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel\ninfisical init\n```\n- This creates `.infisical` config\n- Links to your Infisical project\n\n### Step 3: Configure Secrets in Infisical Dashboard\nGo to: https://app.infisical.com\n\nCreate these secrets:\n- `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` - Your Vercel URL\n- `OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL` - http://localhost:18789\n- `GUARDIAN_API_URL` - http://localhost:XXXX\n\n### Step 4: Vercel Integration\n\nIn Vercel dashboard:\n1. Go to Project Settings вҶ’ Environment Variables\n2. Click \"Infisical\" integration\n3. Connect to your Infisical project\n4. Select which secrets to sync\n\n### Step 5: Deploy with Infisical\n```bash\n# Deploy with injected secrets\ninfisical run vercel --prod\n```\n\n---\n\n**This way, Vercel pulls secrets from Infisical automatically!**","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/INFISICAL_INTEGRATION.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3dcd99ea7a7044cdbd0c8aad","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# вң… Alternative: Use Your Existing Template\n\n## Question:\n\nDo you want to:\n\n### Option 1: Continue with current xmad-control project вң…\n- **Pros**: Clean new project, ready to deploy\n- **Cons**: Need to configure Infisical manually\n- **Status**: Building on Vercel now\n\n### Option 2: Copy to your existing template-v1\n- **Pros**: Already has Infisical + CI/CD configured\n- **Cons**: Need repository access to clone\n- **Status**: Can't access via GitHub (private?)\n\n## For Option 2:\n\nIf you can provide:\n1. Repository URL for template-v1\n2. Or access to clone it\n3. Or zip file of the template\n\nThen I can:\n1. Copy XMAD dashboard into template-v1\n2. Use your existing Infisical setup\n3. Deploy with everything pre-configured!\n\n---\n\n## For Now:\n\nCurrent xmad-control project is deploying to Vercel.\nOnce deployed, we can add Infisical integration.\n\n**Which approach do you prefer?**","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/OPTIONS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":203,"output":616,"cacheRead":63616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64435,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773255316936}}
