{"type":"message","id":"5c672518","parentId":"d9426457","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:58:06.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The repositories aren't accessible via GitHub. They're likely deployed to Vercel from a private repo. Let me use the platform-monorepo which you have access to, and I'll check the SSOT documentation to add Infisical integration:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2424d19207ff4b5db3cd01cf","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-center/SSOT_API_KEYS_GUIDE.md","limit":100}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2d1d8df0e64148dea7682152","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/platform-monorepo && ls -la .github/workflows/ 2>&1 | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d623fb8b2c6d4aee9b600065","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# рҹ“Ӣ Plan: Add Infisical SSOT to Current xmad-control\n\n## Since we can't clone the template, let's:\n\n### 1. Use the current xmad-control-vercel project\n### 2. Add Infisical integration following SSOT guide\n### 3. Configure CI/CD with Infisical secrets\n\n---\n\n## Steps:\n\n### 1. Create Infisical Configuration\n- `.infisical` directory\n- `infisical.json` config\n- Connect to your Infisical project\n\n### 2. Update GitHub Actions\n- Add Infisical step\n- Inject secrets at build time\n- Use SSOT keys from Keychain\n\n### 3. Configure Vercel\n- Add Infisical integration\n- Link environment variables\n- Auto-deploy with secrets\n\n---\n\n**Checking SSOT guide and platform-monorepo setup...**","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/INFISICAL_PLAN.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_def380e2d4c641ce95b4152e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/platform-monorepo && cat .github/workflows/ci.yml 2>/dev/null || cat .github/workflows/cd.yml 2>/dev/null || cat .gitlab-ci.yml | head -80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":175,"o