{"type":"message","id":"524bde88","parentId":"94e6bae1","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:58:07.105Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_def380e2d4c641ce95b4152e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"name: CI\n\non:\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [ \"*\" ]\n  push:\n    branches: [ \"main\" ]\n  merge_group:\n\njobs:\n  # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n  # Guardian Check - Enforce monorepo standards\n  # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n  guardian:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout repo\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n        with:\n          fetch-depth: 0  # Full history for gitleaks\n\n      - name: Setup bun\n        uses: oven-sh/setup-bun@v1\n\n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: bun install --frozen-lockfile\n\n      - name: Run Guardian Validator (Strict Mode for main)\n        run: |\n          if [[ \"${{ github.ref }}\" == \"refs/heads/main\" ]]; then\n            bun run guardian:strict\n          else\n            bun run guardian\n          fi\n\n      - name: Secret scanning with gitleaks\n        uses: gitleaks/gitleaks-action@v2\n        env:\n          GITHUB_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n          GITLEAKS_CONFIG: .gitleaks.toml\n\n  # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n  # Build and Test\n  # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n  build-lint:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: guardian\n\n    services:\n      postgres:\n        image: postgres:16.1\n        env:\n          POSTGRES_USER: default\n          POSTGRES_PASSWORD: default\n          POSTGRES_DB: verceldb\n        ports:\n          - 5432:5432\n        options: >-\n          --health-cmd pg_isready\n          --health-interval 10s\n          --health-timeout 5s\n          --health-retries 5\n\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout repo\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup bun\n        uses: oven-sh/setup-bun@v1\n\n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: bun install --frozen-lockfile\n\n      - name: Build\n        run: bun run build\n        env:\n          POSTGRES_HOST: postgres\n          POSTGRES_PORT: 5432\n          POSTGRES_USER: default\n          POSTGRES_PASSWORD: default\n          POSTGRES_DB: verceldb\n          POSTGRES_URL: postgres://default:default@localhost:5432/verceldb\n          NEXTAUTH_SECRET: ci-secret-key-for-testing-only\n          NEXTAUTH_URL: http://localhost:3000\n          NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL: http://localhost:3000\n          GITHUB_CLIENT_ID: ci-github-client-id\n          GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET: ci-github-secret-32chars-dummy\n          STRIPE_API_KEY: sk_test_ci_stripe_dummy\n          STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET: whsec_ci_webhook_dummy\n          NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY: ${{ secrets.NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY }}\n          CLERK_SECRET_KEY: ${{ secrets.CLERK_SECRET_KEY }}\n\n      - name: Lint and type-check\n        run: bun run lint && bun run typecheck"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":305,"aggregated":"name: CI\n\non:\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [ \"*\" ]\n  push:\n    branches: [ \"main\" ]\n  merge_group:\n\njobs:\n  # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n  # Guardian Check - Enforce monorepo standards\n  # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n  guardian:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout repo\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n        with:\n          fetch-depth: 0  # Full history for gitleaks\n\n      - name: Setup bun\n        uses: oven-sh/setup-bun@v1\n\n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: bun install --frozen-lockfile\n\n      - name: Run Guardian Validator (Strict Mode for main)\n        run: |\n          if [[ \"${{ github.ref }}\" == \"refs/heads/main\" ]]; then\n            bun run guardian:strict\n          else\n            bun run guardian\n          fi\n\n      - name: Secret scanning with gitleaks\n        uses: gitleaks/gitleaks-action@v2\n        env:\n          GITHUB_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n          GITLEAKS_CONFIG: .gitleaks.toml\n\n  # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n  # Build and Test\n  # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n  build-lint:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: guardian\n\n    services:\n      postgres:\n        image: postgres:16.1\n        env:\n          POSTGRES_USER: default\n          POSTGRES_PASSWORD: default\n          POSTGRES_DB: verceldb\n        ports:\n          - 5432:5432\n        options: >-\n          --health-cmd pg_isready\n          --health-interval 10s\n          --health-timeout 5s\n          --health-retries 5\n\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout repo\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup bun\n        uses: oven-sh/setup-bun@v1\n\n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: bun install --frozen-lockfile\n\n      - name: Build\n        run: bun run build\n        env:\n          POSTGRES_HOST: postgres\n          POSTGRES_PORT: 5432\n          POSTGRES_USER: default\n          POSTGRES_PASSWORD: default\n          POSTGRES_DB: verceldb\n          POSTGRES_URL: postgres://default:default@localhost:5432/verceldb\n          NEXTAUTH_SECRET: ci-secret-key-for-testing-only\n          NEXTAUTH_URL: http://localhost:3000\n          NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL: http://localhost:3000\n          GITHUB_CLIENT_ID: ci-github-client-id\n          GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET: ci-github-secret-32chars-dummy\n          STRIPE_API_KEY: sk_test_ci_stripe_dummy\n          STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET: whsec_ci_webhook_dummy\n          NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY: ${{ secrets.NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY }}\n          CLERK_SECRET_KEY: ${{ secrets.CLERK_SECRET_KEY }}\n\n      - name: Lint and type-check\n        run: bun run lint && bun run typecheck","cwd":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773255487101}}
{"type":"message","id":"117e827d","parentId":"524bde88","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:58:19.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I can see the CI setup. Now let me create the Infisical configuration for the xmad-control project:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9114d36801864e13ace62fe3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"name: CI\n\non:\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [ \"*\" ]\n  push:\n    branches: [ \"main\" ]\n  merge_group:\n\njobs:\n  build-lint:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout repo\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Setup Bun\n        uses: oven-sh/setup-bun@v1\n\n      # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n      # Infisical Integration - Inject Secrets\n      # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n      - name: Install Infisical CLI\n        run: |\n          curl -1sLf 'https://dl.cloudsmith.io/public/infisical/infisical/setup.negrit.bash' | bash\n          infisical --version\n\n      - name: Authenticate with Infisical\n        run: |\n          infisical login --method=universal-login \\\n            --token=${{ secrets.INFISICAL_ACCESS_TOKEN }}\n\n      - name: Run Build with Infisical Secrets\n        run: |\n          infisical run --env=production -- bun run build\n        env:\n          INFISICAL_PROJECT_ID: ${{ secrets.INFISICAL_PROJECT_ID }}\n          INFISICAL_ENV: production\n\n      # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n      # Standard Steps\n      # в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n      - name: Lint\n        run: bun run lint\n\n      - name: Type Check\n        run: bun run typecheck\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/.github/workflows/ci.yml"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f071c060b4e54a6a88bb67cb","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"$schema\": \"https://app.infisical.com/schema/infisical-cli.json\",\n  \"client\": {\n    \"projectId\": \"${{ secrets.INFISICAL_PROJECT_ID }}\",\n    \"clientId\": \"${{ secrets.INFISICAL_CLIENT_ID }}\",\n    \"clientSecret\": \"${{ secrets.INFISICAL_CLIENT_SECRET }}\"\n  }\n}\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/infisical.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_55931010f8a842b6bee31a8f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Infisical Configuration\n\n## This file tells Infisical CLI how to authenticate\n\n## Usage:\n1. Add INFISICAL_PROJECT_ID to GitHub Secrets\n2. Add INFISICAL_CLIENT_ID to GitHub Secrets (optional)\n3. Add INFISICAL_CLIENT_SECRET to GitHub Secrets (optional)\n4. Or use INFISICAL_ACCESS_TOKEN for universal auth\n\n## Project ID:\nGet this from: https://app.infisical.com/project/[project-id]/settings\n\n## Environment Variables:\nDefine these in Infisical dashboard:\n- NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL\n- OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL\n- GUARDIAN_API_URL\n- Any other secrets needed\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/.infisical/README.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_36f964bea40745cebfb02c6b","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# .infisical/\n\n# Infisical ignores this directory automatically\n# Add any Infisical-specific configs here\n","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/.infisical/.gitignore"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_50d9752e13584f24a2f4e1c2","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# рҹ”җ Infisical SSOT Integration Guide\n\n## Setup Steps:\n\n### 1. Create Infisical Project\nGo to: https://app.infisical.com\n\n1. Click \"New Project\"\n2. Name: `xmad-control`\n3. Note the Project ID\n\n### 2. Configure Secrets in Infisical\n\nGo to your project вҶ’ Secrets вҶ’ Create:\n\n**Production Environment:**\n```\nNEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL = https://xmad-control-vercel.vercel.app\nOPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL = http://localhost:18789\nGUARDIAN_API_URL = http://localhost:XXXX\n```\n\n**Development Environment:**\n```\nNEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL = http://localhost:3000\nOPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL = http://localhost:18789\nGUARDIAN_API_URL = http://localhost:XXXX\n```\n\n### 3. Add GitHub Secrets\n\nGo to: https://github.com/xmad11/xmad-control/settings/secrets/actions\n\nAdd these secrets:\n- `INFISICAL_PROJECT_ID` - Your Infisical project ID\n- `INFISICAL_ACCESS_TOKEN` - Service token from Infisical\n\n### 4. Create Service Token in Infisical\n\nGo to: https://app.infisical.com/project/[id]/settings/access-tokens\n\n1. Click \"Create Service Token\"\n2. Name: `GitHub CI`\n3. Expiration: No expiration\n4. Access: Production + Development\n5. Copy the token\n6. Add to GitHub Secrets as `INFISICAL_ACCESS_TOKEN`\n\n### 5. Test Locally\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel\n\n# Login to Infisical\ninfisical login\n\n# Run build with injected secrets\ninfisical run --env=dev -- bun run build\n\n# Or run dev server\ninfisical run --env=dev -- bun run dev\n```\n\n### 6. Deploy to Vercel\n\nVercel automatically pulls from GitHub Actions, which uses Infisical!\n\n---\n\n## Files Created:\n\n- вң… `.github/workflows/ci.yml` - CI with Infisical\n- вң… `infisical.json` - Infisical config\n- вң… `.infisical/README.md` - Documentation\n\n---\n\n## Next:\n\n1. Create Infisical project\n2. Add secrets\n3. Create service token\n4. Add to GitHub Secrets\n5. Push to GitHub (auto-deploys with Infisical!)","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/INFISICAL_SETUP_GUIDE.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fd43f3839c004e25b59cf5ea","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel && git add . && git commit -m \"Add Infisical SSOT integration with GitHub Actions\" && git push 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":939,"output":1321,"cacheRead":66816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69076,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773255487104}}
