{"type":"message","id":"75a34b88","parentId":"f07204c6","timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:58:31.705Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Infisical integration has been added and pushed! Now let me create a summary of what's configured:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_efa827e3ef594aa0a31d110d","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# вң… XMAD Control - Vercel + Infisical Complete!\n\n## Status: рҹ”„ DEPLOYING WITH INFISICAL SSOT\n\n---\n\n## What's Configured:\n\n### 1. GitHub Repository вң…\n- **URL**: https://github.com/xmad11/xmad-control\n- **CI/CD**: GitHub Actions with Infisical\n- **Auto-deploy**: Enabled\n\n### 2. Vercel Project вң…\n- **Project**: `xmad-control-vercel`\n- **Team**: `ahmad-s-projects-7e32bc62`\n- **Status**: Deploying\n- **URL**: https://xmad-control-vercel-ahmad-s-projects-7e32bc62.vercel.app\n\n### 3. Infisical Integration вң…\n- **Config**: `infisical.json` created\n- **CI Workflow**: `.github/workflows/ci.yml` with Infisical\n- **Documentation**: Setup guide included\n\n### 4. XMAD Dashboard вң…\n- **Path**: `app/xmad-dashboard/page.tsx`\n- **Components**: shadcn (Card, Button, Badge)\n- **Features**:\n  - 4 Glass widgets\n  - Status badges\n  - Quick actions\n  - Dark gradient background\n  - NO emojis!\n  - Small Lucide icons\n\n---\n\n## Next Steps to Complete Infisical Setup:\n\n### 1. Create Infisical Project\nGo to: https://app.infisical.com\n\n1. Click \"New Project\"\n2. Name: `xmad-control`\n3. Note the **Project ID**\n\n### 2. Add Secrets in Infisical\n\nIn your Infisical project вҶ’ Secrets:\n\n**Production:**\n```\nNEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL = https://xmad-control-vercel.vercel.app\nOPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL = http://localhost:18789\nGUARDIAN_API_URL = http://localhost:XXXX\n```\n\n**Development:**\n```\nNEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL = http://localhost:3000\nOPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL = http://localhost:18789\nGUARDIAN_API_URL = http://localhost:XXXX\n```\n\n### 3. Create Service Token\n\nIn Infisical вҶ’ Settings вҶ’ Access Tokens:\n\n1. Click \"Create Service Token\"\n2. Name: `GitHub CI`\n3. Access: Production + Development\n4. Copy the token\n\n### 4. Add to GitHub Secrets\n\nGo to: https://github.com/xmad11/xmad-control/settings/secrets/actions\n\nAdd:\n- `INFISICAL_PROJECT_ID` - Your project ID from step 1\n- `INFISICAL_ACCESS_TOKEN` - Service token from step 3\n\n### 5. Test Locally\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel\n\n# Login\ninfisical login\n\n# Run with secrets\ninfisical run --env=dev -- bun run dev\n```\n\n### 6. Deploy\n\nVercel will automatically use Infisical secrets via GitHub Actions!\n\n---\n\n## Deployment URLs:\n\n### GitHub:\nhttps://github.com/xmad11/xmad-control\n\n### Vercel Dashboard:\nhttps://vercel.com/ahmad-s-projects-7e32bc62/xmad-control-vercel\n\n### Live Site:\nhttps://xmad-control-vercel-ahmad-s-projects-7e32bc62.vercel.app/xmad-dashboard\n\n---\n\n## Auto-Deploy Workflow:\n\n```bash\n# Make changes\nvim app/xmad-dashboard/page.tsx\n\n# Commit\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"Update dashboard\"\n\n# Push (auto-deploys with Infisical secrets!)\ngit push\n```\n\nGitHub Actions will:\n1. Run Infisical CLI\n2. Inject secrets from Infisical\n3. Build the project\n4. Vercel deploys the build\n\n---\n\n## Files Created:\n\n### Dashboard:\n- `app/xmad-dashboard/page.tsx` - Main dashboard\n- `app/xmad-dashboard/globals.css` - Styles\n\n### Infisical:\n- `infisical.json` - Infisical config\n- `.infisical/README.md` - Documentation\n- `.github/workflows/ci.yml` - CI with Infisical\n\n### Documentation:\n- `INFISICAL_SETUP_GUIDE.md` - Complete setup guide\n- `FINAL_SUMMARY.md` - Project summary\n\n---\n\n## Success Metrics:\n\n- вң… GitHub repository created\n- вң… Vercel project linked\n- вң… Dashboard with glassmorphism UI\n- вң… Infisical CI/CD configured\n- вң… GitHub Actions workflow ready\n- вң… NO emojis (Lucide icons)\n- вң… Professional design\n- рҹ”„ Deploying to Vercel...\n- вҸі Waiting for Infisical setup\n\n---\n\n**Created**: 2026-03-11 22:57 GMT+4\n**By**: Nova (рҹ‘ұ)\n**For**: Ahmad Abdullah\n\n---\n\n## рҹҡҖ Almost There!\n\n1. Vercel is building now (check URL in ~2 min)\n2. Create Infisical project and add secrets\n3. Add Infisical tokens to GitHub Secrets\n4. Future deployments will automatically use Infisical SSOT!","path":"/Users/ahmadabdullah/Desktop/xmad-control-vercel/COMPLETE_SUMMARY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":398,"output":1152,"cacheRead":68992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70542,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773255501274}}
